In a quote given to Polygon on November 17, 2023, Clark praised the precision of the PS5 DualSense controller, likening the enhanced clarity it provides to the experience of putting on glasses and seeing the world come into sharp focus. This comparison underscores the controller's ability to significantly improve gameplay by offering a more accurate and immersive interaction with the game environment.

Additionally, Nicole Clark has shared insights on a video game, focusing on its puzzle elements and metagame aspects. Her commentary highlights the game's strategic depth and the importance of understanding the broader game mechanics beyond the immediate challenges presented in-game. This review or commentary by Clark indicates her appreciation for games that engage players on multiple levels, requiring not only in-game problem-solving but also a meta-level understanding of how various game systems interact.

Through these contributions, Nicole Clark demonstrates a keen interest in the intersection of technology and entertainment, particularly in how advancements in gaming hardware and software can enhance the overall gaming experience. Her perspectives are valuable for fellow gamers and industry professionals looking to understand the nuances of player engagement and satisfaction in the modern gaming landscape.

name: FADE AFTERNOON
description: Fading Afternoon is a video game developed by yeo, available on Windows PC, that explores the life of Seiji Maruyama, a former yakuza member, and how he spends his remaining time.[]

name: SEIJI MARUYAMA
description: Seiji Maruyama is a character in Fading Afternoon, a former yakuza member who has recently been released from prison and is trying to make his mark again while dealing with a limited time left.[]

name: JOSHUA RIVERA
description: Joshua Rivera is a person who provided a review or commentary on Fading Afternoon, a video game that deals with time and choices in the life of a former yakuza member.[]

name: SUIKA GAME
description: Suika Game is a video game developed by Aladdin X, available on Nintendo Switch, that combines elements of 2048, Tetris, and physics in a fruit drop game.[]

name: ALADDIN X
description: Aladdin X is the developer of Suika Game, a video game that has gained popularity for its engaging gameplay and social aspects.[]

name: NINTENDO SWITCH
description: The Nintendo Switch is a versatile hybrid video game console, known for its robust library of games that can be played either at home on a television screen or on the go as a portable device. This console, which is the successor to Wii Sports, boasts an abundance of titles with local multiplayer features, making it an excellent choice for game night with friends or casual play sessions. It offers a variety of multiplayer games, including sports, racing, and brawling games. Classic sports like bowling, golf, and tennis are featured, along with new additions such as volleyball and chambara. The console supports the 20-year series Mario Kart, with the latest edition adding new courses, and includes games like Scramble, where players operate a spaceship, and a paper-based game that requires teamwork to accomplish tasks. Additionally, Nintendo's fight-to-the-death brawler allows up to eight players to compete, and TMNT: Shredder’s Revenge is a beat-‘em-up brawler for TMNT fans, featuring the four Turtles, April O’Neil, Master Splinter, and Casey Jones. The Nintendo Switch also supports couch co-op games, such as Rayman Legends, Rocket League, Towerfall Ascension, Minecraft, Overcooked! All You Can Eat, Super Mario 3D World + Bowser's Fury, and Nintendo Switch Sports. It has seen an unprecedented run of success, with arguably the best entries in many of Nintendo's biggest franchises. Super Mario Bros. Wonder is set to be released on Oct. 20, 2023, on the Nintendo Switch, and Pikmin 4 can also be played on this platform, along with all previous Pikmin games that have been conveniently ported. The console is equipped with cute Joy-Con colors, a great pro controller, and themed peripherals for fans of all stripes. As a handheld device, the Nintendo Switch can be charged by a power bank with a capacity of 18 W through its USB-C charging port.

name: JL
description: JL is a person who provided a review or commentary on Suika Game, a video game that has become a go-to for time-killing and is noted for its social and streaming appeal.[]

name: LEAGUE OF LEGENDS SEASON 13
description: League of Legends Season 13 is a video game developed by Riot Games, available on Mac and Windows PC, that is noted for its balanced gameplay and the viability of almost every champion.[]

name: RIOT GAMES
description: Riot Games is the developer of League of Legends, a popular multiplayer online battle arena game, and its 13th season is highlighted for its balanced gameplay.[]

name: WORLD OF WARCRAFT CLASSIC
description: World of Warcraft Classic is a retro version of the popular MMORPG World of Warcraft, developed by Blizzard Entertainment. It is available on Mac and Windows PC. This year, interesting developments have occurred in the game, including the introduction of a permadeath mode called Hardcore and the Season of Discovery, which remixes and restructures the original WoW experience. These changes are aimed at keeping the game engaging for players who prefer the game as it was at launch [N. Carpenter, Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: BLIZZARD ENTERTAINMENT
description: Blizzard Entertainment, a renowned game developer, is actively engaged in the creation and enhancement of two major titles: Diablo 4 and World of Warcraft Classic. Diablo 4, known for blending action, role-playing, and a dark tone, has seen updates in season 2 to address player concerns, including making Nightmare Dungeons less grindy, improving the Renown system, and enhancing the functionality of mounts, as reported by Polygon on 2023-10-04. Meanwhile, World of Warcraft Classic, a massively multiplayer online game (MMO) that was launched in response to community demands, as noted by TechCrunch on 2023-10-30, continues to evolve with creative features to keep the game engaging for players who wish to experience the game as it was at launch. These features include the Hardcore permadeath mode and the Season of Discovery, both mentioned by N. Carpenter in Polygon on 2023-10-31. Blizzard Entertainment's commitment to listening to and acting on player feedback is evident in these updates, showcasing their dedication to enhancing the gaming experience for their community.

name: HARDCORE MODE
description: Hardcore is a permadeath mode introduced in World of Warcraft Classic by Blizzard Entertainment. This mode makes the game more dangerous and social, resurrecting the spirit of its 2004 servers [N. Carpenter, Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: SEASON OF DISCOVERY
description: The Season of Discovery is an event in World of Warcraft Classic that remixes and restructures the original WoW experience. It includes staggered level caps and shuffled class roles, potentially changing MMO design forever [N. Carpenter, Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: FIRE EMBLEM ENGAGE
description: Fire Emblem Engage, developed by Intelligent Systems and available on Nintendo Switch, is a turn-based tactics game that M. Mahardy from Polygon recommends as an excellent choice for gamers. This game is tailored for players who have a keen interest in combat stats, weapon loadouts, and team composition, providing a rich environment for strategic gameplay. Unlike some entries in the Fire Emblem series, Fire Emblem Engage places less emphasis on origin stories or political narratives, allowing players to immerse themselves in the tactical aspects of the game. A unique feature highlighted by Mahardy is the game's ability to let players observe character interactions on the battlefield, which can inspire creative fanfiction in the minds of its audience.

name: INTELLIGENT SYSTEMS
description: Intelligent Systems is the developer of Fire Emblem Engage, a turn-based tactics game that focuses on combat mechanics and team composition rather than narrative [M. Mahardy, Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: PIZZA TOWER
description: Pizza Tower, developed by Tour De Pizza, is a captivating video game available on Windows PC. The game's protagonist is Peppino Spaghetti, a chef embarking on an extraordinary quest. Peppino must ascend a towering structure, aptly named the Pizza Tower, to confront and vanquish Pizzaface, an enormous sentient pizza that poses an existential threat. The game's art style and absurd enemies draw inspiration from the Wario Land series, creating a unique and engaging experience for players. [Source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: TOUR DE PIZZA
description: Tour De Pizza, a creative game development studio, is renowned for crafting Pizza Tower, a whimsical video game that has garnered attention for its unique concept and gameplay. In Pizza Tower, players take on the role of Peppino Spaghetti, a chef on a mission to scale a towering pizza structure to confront a massive, sentient floating pizza. The game is celebrated for its full commitment to its quirky vision, successfully capturing the essence of the beloved Wario Land series, as noted by N. Carpenter and Polygon in their 2023-10-31 reviews. Tour De Pizza's dedication to bringing this imaginative world to life has made Pizza Tower a standout title in the realm of video games.

name: PEPPINO SPAGHETTI
description: Peppino Spaghetti is the main character in Pizza Tower, a chef who must race up the pizza tower to defeat Pizzaface. [Source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: PIZZAFACE
description: Pizzaface is an enormous floating sentient pizza in Pizza Tower, posing an existential threat that Peppino Spaghetti must defeat. [Source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: SUBPAR POOL
description: Subpar Pool is a physics puzzler video game developed by grapefrukt games, available on Android, iOS, Nintendo Switch, and Windows PC. It is described as dynamic minigolf on a pool table and is an ideal mobile game. [Source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: GRAPEFRUKT GAMES
description: grapefrukt games, aka Martin Jonasson, is a Swedish developer known for elegant classics such as Holedown, Twofold Inc., and Rymdkapsel, and is the developer of Subpar Pool. [Source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: AMNESIA: THE BUNKER
description: Amnesia: The Bunker is a video game developed by Frictional Games, available on PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Windows PC, Xbox One, and Xbox Series X. It is set in a sealed bunker during World War I and involves collecting fuel for the bunker’s generator while trying to find an exit. [Source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: FRICTIONAL GAMES
description: Frictional Games is a developer with a master’s grasp on interactive horror, known for the Amnesia series, including Amnesia: The Bunker. [Source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: M. MAHARDY
description: M. Mahardy, a distinguished writer for Polygon, is recognized for offering insightful reviews in the realm of video games. In 2023, Mahardy provided a detailed critique of Octopath Traveler 2, highlighting the game's unique narrative approach that skillfully challenges expectations while blending elements of comfort and subversion, a significant contribution to the JRPG genre. Additionally, Mahardy expressed appreciation for Mimimi Games, the developers behind The Cursed Crew, showcasing a keen interest in the works of innovative game studios. Mahardy's expertise in analyzing and conveying the intricacies of gaming experiences makes their reviews a valuable resource for both casual players and hardcore enthusiasts.

name: AMNESIA SERIES
description: The Amnesia series is a collection of horror video games known for its thrilling chases and tension-building moments. Amnesia: The Bunker, set in a sealed bunker from World War I, is considered one of Frictional's best games, where the player must find an exit while avoiding a monster attracted to sound and navigating through the bunker's complex structure. The game is as terrifying as any horror video game. [Source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: FRICITIONAL
description: Frictional is a game developer known for creating the Amnesia series, with Amnesia: The Bunker being one of their best works. [Source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: LIL GATOR GAME
description: Lil Gator Game is a video game developed by MegaWobble, available on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Windows PC, Xbox One, and Xbox Series X. It is described as having a similar feel to A Short Hike, offering a joyous, unstructured sense of play akin to a day in the park. The game is recommended for those looking for a relaxing and playful experience. [Source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: MEGAWOBBLE
description: MegaWobble is a game developer that created Lil Gator Game, a title that has gained a high ranking in the list of best video games of 2023. [Source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: STARFIELD
description: Starfield is a video game developed by Bethesda Game Studios and owned by Microsoft, which was launched exclusively on PC and Xbox in September 2023, and was playable on Game Pass from the day of its release. The game offers top-tier world-building, a customizable ship builder, and engaging combat, immersing players in a universe with over 1,000 planets. Although the number of planets is fewer than its competitor, No Man's Sky, Starfield's focus on infinite possibilities is highlighted by Clayton Ashley, as reported by Polygon on 2023-10-31. The game features galaxy-spanning faction quests and side quests that make the player feel like a captain in a Star Trek-like universe, with elements of good sci-fi for those willing to explore. ZeniMax workers, who helped ship the game, are entitled to a copy of Starfield as part of their unionization efforts.

name: BETHESDA GAME STUDIOS
description: Bethesda Game Studios is a game developer known for creating Starfield, a game that excels in world-building, ship customization, and combat. The game offers a variety of quests, including faction quests and side quests that enhance the player's experience. [Source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: NO MAN’S SKY
description: No Man’s Sky is a game that realizes the universe’s infinite number of planets, serving as a competitor to Starfield. It is mentioned in the context of Starfield’s marketing and the comparison of the number of planets [source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: BETHESDA
description: Bethesda is the developer of Starfield, a game that oversold the idea of a galaxy with over 1,000 planets. The company’s marketing led to a focus on the number of planets, overshadowing the game’s new game plus mode [source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: SYSTEM SHOCK
description: System Shock is a game developed by Nightdive Studios. It is a remake of the 1994 classic, updated with modern visuals while preserving the original game’s cyberpunk aesthetics and gameplay. The game requires players to use curiosity, caution, and cunning to navigate the halls of Citadel Station [source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: NIGHTDIVE STUDIOS
description: Nightdive Studios is the developer of the System Shock remake. The company managed to update the 1994 classic with modern visuals while preserving the original game’s aesthetics and gameplay, making it a thrilling experience [source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: STAR WARS JEDI: SURVIVOR
description: Star Wars Jedi: Survivor, developed by Respawn Entertainment, is a video game that serves as a sequel to Star Wars Jedi: Fallen Order. Building upon its predecessor, Jedi: Survivor offers a more action-packed beginning, enhanced aerial movements, and an array of lightsaber stances, ensuring a dynamic and engaging gameplay experience. Quality-of-life improvements, such as a fast travel system, have been implemented to streamline the game. Players can explore new locales filled with hidden collectibles and upgrades, interact with memorable characters, and even craft their own lightsabers. The game's narrative and character development are its core strengths, immersing players in the Star Wars universe and allowing them to feel the presence of the Force throughout their journey. [Source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: RESPAWN ENTERTAINMENT
description: Respawn Entertainment is the developer of Star Wars Jedi: Survivor, a sequel to Star Wars Jedi: Fallen Order. The company managed to create a game that is considered one of the best follow-ups in the entire Star Wars franchise [source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: STAR WARS JEDI: FALLEN ORDER
description: Star Wars Jedi: Fallen Order is the predecessor to Star Wars Jedi: Survivor, a video game that has been improved upon in various ways. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: THE NEW YORK TIMES
description: The New York Times, a renowned media company, has diversified its portfolio by acquiring the viral word game Wordle and transforming its Crossword section into a comprehensive gaming platform. This expansion showcases the company's ability to adapt and innovate, as evidenced by the launch of their new title, Connections, which has been well-received for its engaging content created by skilled puzzle writers and editors [Polygon, 2023-10-31]. Beyond gaming, The New York Times remains committed to delivering in-depth journalism, covering significant events such as the bankruptcy of FTX and the subsequent interview with its founder, Sam Bankman-Fried [The Verge, 2023-09-28]. The outlet also delved into the world of sports, reporting on allegations of sign-stealing and scouting by the Michigan football team, featuring insights from Purdue's coach Ryan Walters and Michigan's coach Jim Harbaugh [The New York Times, 2023-11-03]. Further, The New York Times scrutinized the controversy surrounding the College Football Playoff (CFP) selection process and its implications for college football, specifically highlighting the exclusion of Florida State from the CFP [The New York Times, 2023-12-03]. In the realm of entertainment, the newspaper conducted an interview with Britney Spears' lawyer, discussing the ongoing legal battles related to her conservatorship [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-18]. Additionally, The New York Times published an article praising the exceptional hockey skills of Connor Bedard, underscoring its broad coverage of various topics [The New York Times, 2023-11-17]. Through these diverse engagements, The New York Times demonstrates its commitment to providing comprehensive and insightful content across different sectors, maintaining its status as a leading source of information and entertainment.

name: CONNECTIONS
description: Connections is a video game developed by The New York Times, offering a grid of 16 words and challenging players to detect the common threads between four different sets of words. The game's logic ranges from simple to sneaky, and it includes a sense of accomplishment when all four sets are landed. The game is described as one of the year's best and is compared to BBC's Only Connect. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: HI-FI RUSH
description: Hi-Fi Rush, developed by Tango Gameworks, is an action-rhythm video game available on Windows PC and Xbox Series X. The game centers around the protagonist, Chai, who, following a workplace accident where an iPod is forcibly embedded into his chest, gains heightened sensitivity to sound and must adhere to the beat of the music. This unique narrative sets the stage for an engaging gameplay experience where players explore, climb, and engage in combat, all synchronized to the rhythm. Hi-Fi Rush is designed with accessibility in mind, gently guiding players back to the beat to maintain a sense of flow and accomplishment, making it enjoyable for gamers of all skill levels. The game is not only about survival but also features a crafting system for lightsabers, adding a creative and interactive element to the gameplay. Described as a joyful experience, Hi-Fi Rush combines elements of action, rhythm, and crafting to deliver a distinctive and entertaining gaming adventure.

name: TANGO GAMEWORKS
description: Tango Gameworks, a renowned game developer, is celebrated for creating Hi-Fi Rush, an innovative video game where players take on the role of Chai, a character determined to escape the clutches of a villainous corporation. The game uniquely blends action and rhythm, offering an engaging and immersive experience that captivates players with its dynamic gameplay and compelling storyline. As of 2023, Tango Gameworks continues to push the boundaries of interactive entertainment with Hi-Fi Rush, solidifying their reputation as a creative force in the gaming industry.

name: MATT PATCHES
description: Matt Patches, a notable figure in the realm of entertainment and technology, has shared his insights on both gaming and cinema. As of 2023, Patches has been recognized for his commentary on the video game Hi-Fi Rush, highlighting its accessibility and the exhilarating experience it offers to players. His appreciation for the game was published by Polygon on October 31, 2023. Additionally, Matt Patches has recommended the film Malignant, praising James Wan's direction, as noted in his review for Polygon on September 28, 2023. These contributions showcase Patches' diverse interests and expertise in analyzing and critiquing various forms of entertainment.

name: N. CLARK
description: N. Clark, a seasoned game reviewer for Polygon as of October 31, 2023, has shared insights on two distinct gaming experiences. In one review, Clark delves into Chants of Sennaar, praising the game for its straightforward mechanics, engaging translation puzzles, and the unique objective of climbing a tower while dynamically altering its structure. This highlights Clark's appreciation for games that blend simplicity with depth, offering players a rewarding challenge. In another critique, N. Clark focuses on Hi-Fi Rush, commending its fresh approach to the action-rhythm genre. The game's design, according to Clark, is masterful in fostering a sense of flow and accomplishment, making it an inviting choice for gamers seeking a harmonious blend of action and music. Through these reviews, N. Clark showcases a keen understanding of diverse gaming elements, from puzzle-solving to rhythm-based gameplay, and the ability to articulate the nuances that make each game a compelling experience.

name: MONSTER HUNTER NOW
description: "Monster Hunter Now, developed by Niantic, is a captivating video game available on both Android and iOS platforms. The game offers an enhanced combat system, streamlined matchmaking, a vast array of monsters to hunt, and comprehensive character development options. One of its unique features is the seamless integration of real-world elements, creating an immersive experience for players as they track monsters in their actual surroundings. During special events, such as Halloween, players can engage in themed hunts to collect exclusive items like the Jack-o’-Head armor and Pumpkin Tickets, adding an extra layer of excitement and variety to the gameplay."

name: NIANTIC
description: Niantic, a renowned developer in the technology and entertainment industry, is best known for creating Monster Hunter Now, a game that innovatively merges real-world technology with engaging combat and exploration mechanics. As confirmed by Niantic in 2023, any Kulu-Ya-Ku monsters in Monster Hunter Now that were tagged with paintballs during the Halloween event will continue to drop Pumpkin Tickets even after the event has ended, providing players with an extended opportunity to collect these special in-game items. This decision showcases Niantic's commitment to enhancing player experience and engagement beyond the typical event timelines.

name: MATT LEONE
description: Matt Leone is a person who reviewed Monster Hunter Now, praising the game's combat system, monster variety, and the integration of real-world elements. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: DIABLO 4
description:
Diablo 4, developed by Blizzard Entertainment and published in 2023, is an action-packed video game available on PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Windows PC, Xbox One, and Xbox Series X platforms. The game masterfully blends the action from Diablo 3, the RPG systems of Diablo 2, and the dark tone of the original Diablo, creating an immersive experience for players. It was first announced at BlizzCon 2019 and has since evolved with quality-of-life updates, particularly in season 2, which saw improvements to mounts, the Renown system, and gem acquisition, as reported by Polygon.

In Diablo 4, players can choose from various classes, including the Barbarian and the Sorcerer, to progress through the game using a multitude of builds and skills. The Barbarian class, the game's only pure melee class, involves complex math underlying its gameplay, even for the simple act of smashing enemies. Season 2 introduced the best Barbarian builds, enhancing the combat experience. The Sorcerer, on the other hand, is a pure caster class that wields elemental magic, allowing players to battle demons and other creatures in the realm of Sanctuary with a range of spells.

The game also features a Paragon Board system and various Legendary Powers and Unique items that can be used to augment character builds, providing a deep level of customization and strategy. Additionally, Diablo 4 includes endgame bosses, Nightmare Dungeons, and seasonal activities like Helltides and Blood Harvest, keeping the gameplay engaging and challenging for players across different seasons.

name: HITMAN FREELANCER
description: Hitman Freelancer is a video game that involves completing dangerous missions to defeat a crime syndicate, offering a thrilling experience when successfully exfiltrating after a mission [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: VENBA
description: Venba is a cooking video game developed by Visai Games, available on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Windows PC, Xbox One, and Xbox Series X. It focuses on an immigrant family that moved from India to Canada, with food playing a central role in the narrative [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: VISAIGAMES
description: Visai Games is the developer of the video game Venba, which is available on multiple platforms including Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Windows PC, Xbox One, and Xbox Series X [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: VIEWFINDER
description: Viewfinder is a video game developed by Sad Owl Studios, available on PlayStation 5 and Windows PC. It features a unique mechanic where photos of the environment can be pasted into the game world to manipulate it, creating bridges or revealing items. The game also has a narrative that explores the concept of perspective [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: SAD OWL STUDIOS
description: Sad Owl Studios is the developer of the video game Viewfinder, which is available on PlayStation 5 and Windows PC [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: HUMANITY
description: "Humanity is a video game that boasts a unique evolution in gameplay, starting as a classic puzzle game before seamlessly integrating elements of tower defense and shoot-'em-up genres, ultimately transforming into an intense all-out war scenario. Developed by an unspecified team, the game is celebrated for its modern art aesthetic that pays homage to early PlayStation games, showcasing impressive design feats. Players can experience the dynamic journey of Humanity on PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, and Windows PC platforms."

name: SAMIT SARKAR
description: Samit Sarkar is a person who provided a review of Hitman Freelancer, describing the game's experience and the satisfaction of completing missions [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: N. CARPENTER
description: N. Carpenter, a seasoned reviewer in the gaming industry, has shared insightful perspectives on two distinct games, Venba and Dave the Diver, both in a review published by Polygon on 2023-10-31. In the review of Venba, N. Carpenter praised the game for its remarkable ability to immerse players in the art of cooking, while also delving into the emotional depth of its narrative, making it a standout title in its genre. Moving on to Dave the Diver, the reviewer described the game as a masterful blend of absurdity and silliness, executed with a delicate balance that enhances its appeal. N. Carpenter further highlighted the game's compelling gameplay loop and the progression of its story, which contribute to its overall engaging experience. Through these reviews, N. Carpenter showcases a keen understanding of the nuances that make each game unique and captivating to its audience.

name: CA
description: CA is a person who reviewed Viewfinder, highlighting the game's unique perspective mechanic and its narrative that explores the concept of perspective [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: PARANORMASIGHT: THE SEVEN MYSTERIES OF HONJO
description: Paranormasight: The Seven Mysteries of Honjo is a video game developed by Square Enix. It is a mystery and horror game set in 1980s Japan, specifically the Tokyo neighborhood of Honjo, filled with shadows and lethal curses. The game is recommended for those interested in urban legends, spooky folklore, cults, and deadly rituals, and is available on Android, iOS, Nintendo Switch, and Windows PC [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: SQUARE ENIX
description: Square Enix, a renowned game developer and publisher, has made significant contributions to the gaming industry with mega-franchises such as Final Fantasy, Dragon Quest, and Kingdom Hearts. The company is celebrated for its ability to produce not only blockbuster titles but also surprising, interesting, and experimental games. One such example is Paranormasight: The Seven Mysteries of Honjo, a game that showcases Square Enix's innovative spirit. They are also behind the development of Final Fantasy 16, a mainline entry in the beloved Final Fantasy series, which was crafted by their Creative Business Unit III, the team responsible for the massively multiplayer online role-playing game (MMORPG) Final Fantasy 14. Demonstrating their commitment to quality and improvement, Square Enix is one of the developers of Octopath Traveler 2, where they have focused on enhancing the game's level design, narrative structure, and characterization, ensuring that the sequel is a more enjoyable and evolved version of the original.

name: THEATRHYTHM FINAL BAR LINE
description: Theatrhythm Final Bar Line is a rhythm game, described as the Avengers of rhythm games, and is an easy recommendation for those interested in the genre [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: ZERO ESCAPE
description: Zero Escape is a video game series that shares similarities with Paranormasight: The Seven Mysteries of Honjo in terms of genre and themes [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: DANGANRONPA
description: Danganronpa is a video game series that shares similarities with Paranormasight: The Seven Mysteries of Honjo in terms of genre and themes [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: PARANORMASIGHT
description: Paranormasight is a video game set in 1980s Japan, specifically the Tokyo neighborhood of Honjo, which is filled with shadows and lethal curses. It is recommended for those interested in urban legends, spooky folklore, cults, and deadly rituals, and is similar to series like Zero Escape and Danganronpa. The game runs well on console, PC, iOS, and Android. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: HONJO
description: Honjo is a neighborhood in Tokyo, Japan, where Paranormasight is set. It is described as being filled with shadows and lethal curses. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: TOKYO SKYTREE
description: Tokyo Skytree is a modern landmark in Tokyo, Japan. It is mentioned in contrast to the setting of Paranormasight, which is in the 1980s. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: MARVEL’S MIDNIGHT SUNS
description: Marvel’s Midnight Suns is a video game developed by Firaxis Games. It is a card-based strategy game featuring a customizable deck for each hero. The game is recommended for its clever combat and kooky cast of characters, including Captain Marvel, Magik, Blade, Wolverine, and Deadpool. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: FIRAXIS GAMES
description: Firaxis Games is the developer of Marvel’s Midnight Suns. They are known for creating games with high-stakes tactical battles, such as XCOM 2. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: CHRIS PLANTE
description: Chris Plante, a notable figure in the realm of technology and entertainment, is recognized for his insightful recommendations. As of 2023, Plante has been active in sharing his thoughts on various media, specifically within the horror genre, as mentioned in a Polygon article dated September 28, 2023. Not limiting his expertise to just horror movies, Plante also extends his recommendations to include video games, as evidenced in a subsequent Polygon article published on October 31, 2023. In this later piece, Plante, identified as the author, highlights the game Paranormasight alongside Marvel's Midnight Suns. He particularly emphasizes that Midnight Suns, despite potentially underwhelming in its initial hours, unfolds to reveal a depth of gameplay and clever combat mechanics that are worth experiencing. Plante's recommendations encourage audiences to look beyond surface impressions and engage with the full spectrum of what these titles have to offer.

name: MIDNIGHT SUNS
description: Midnight Suns is a video game that offers clever combat and a kooky cast of characters, including Deadpool DLC. It is worth the time, even for those who might be sick of Marvel, as it can win you over with its engaging gameplay. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: MARVEL
description: Marvel is a renowned entertainment company, primarily recognized as a publisher of comic books. The entity is celebrated for its creation of iconic characters, with Spider-Man being one of the most notable. Marvel's influence extends beyond the pages of comic books, as its characters and stories have been adapted into various forms of media, including video games. A recent example of this is the game "Spider-Man 2," which draws from Marvel's rich comic book universe. As of 2023, Marvel continues to be a significant player in the entertainment industry, captivating audiences with its superheroes and their adventures.

name: MADDY MYERS
description: Maddy Myers is a person who spent over 100 hours playing Midnight Suns and recommends giving the game a chance for its combat and humorous storylines, such as Wolverine attending Blade's book club. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: HONKAI: STAR RAIL
description: Honkai: Star Rail is a video game developed by Hoyoverse, designed as a solution for Genshin Impact burnout. It features slower-paced turn-based combat, the ability to auto-battle, and smaller maps, making it a perfect daily game without feeling exhausted. The characters are fun, flashy, and easy to latch onto. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: HOYOVERSE
description: Hoyoverse is a game developer known for creating Honkai: Star Rail, a game that serves as an alternative for players experiencing Genshin Impact burnout. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: GENSIN IMPACT
description: Genshin Impact is a video game that has caused burnout for some players due to its extensive content, including every character, grinding, 100% exploration, and completing every quest. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: CHANTS OF SENNAAR
description: Chants of Sennaar is a video game developed by Rundisc, where players climb a Tower of Babel-style structure and decipher the distinct language each group of people speaks. The game is rendered in a cel-shaded style and involves matching pictographic symbols to images in a dictionary-style book. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: RUNDISC
description: Rundisc is a game developer known for creating Chants of Sennaar, a game that involves language translation and cultural interactions in a cel-shaded isometric world. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: MIMIMI GAMES
description: Mimimi Games is a game development studio that has released The Cursed Crew, one of the best games of 2023, and is planning to close down after its release. The studio has been underappreciated throughout the last decade. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: SHADOW GAMBIT: THE CURSED CREW
description: Shadow Gambit: The Cursed Crew is a video game set in a tropical world of zombie pirates, religious fanatics, and talking ships. It is the final game released by Mimimi Games and is considered one of the best games of 2023. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: BLACK SALT GAMES
description: Black Salt Games is a game development studio that has released Dredge, a Lovecraftian horror game that masquerades as a simple fishing game. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: DREDGE
description: "DREDGE, developed by Black Salt Games, is a critically acclaimed video game that masterfully blends Lovecraftian horror with engaging gameplay elements, earning its title as one of the best games of 2023 according to Polygon. The game presents a dark parable about loss and obsession, captivating players with its narrative depth. Uniquely, DREDGE incorporates a fishing and boat building mechanic, where players can encounter a variety of mysterious sea creatures. The game's upgrade system, praised for its rewarding progression, enables players to catch better fish and construct a larger boat, fostering a sense of transformation and adventure as they delve deeper into the game's haunting world."

name: FINAL FANTASY 16
description: Final Fantasy 16 is a video game developed by Square Enix, featuring a Game of Thrones-like adventure. Players control Clive Rosfield, a young man protecting his brother Joshua, in a story filled with palace intrigue, sex, and war, with elements like mother crystals, Eikons, and Chocobos [source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: CLIVE ROSFIELD
description: Clive Rosfield is a character in Final Fantasy 16, a young man whose life's work is to protect his brother Joshua. His story takes a dramatic turn when he vows to destroy the monster that ruined his and his family's legacy [source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: CYBERPUNK 2077: PHANTOM LIBERTY
description: Cyberpunk 2077: Phantom Liberty is a video game developed by CD Projekt Red. It expands on the base game Cyberpunk 2077 with a new district in Night City and a spy-thriller storyline, enhancing the game's role-playing progression systems and enemy AI [source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: CD PROJEKT RED
description: CD PROJEKT RED, a notable game development company, has recently established unions within the past two years, reflecting a growing trend in the industry towards collective representation and worker rights. This progressive move comes alongside their dedication to creating immersive gaming experiences, as evidenced by their latest release, Cyberpunk 2077: Phantom Liberty. This expansion, an enhancement to the original Cyberpunk 2077 game, introduces fresh content and refines gameplay mechanics, aiming to captivate players with an enriched storyline and interactive environment. [source: Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: CYBERPUNK 2077
description: Cyberpunk 2077 is a video game that was initially released in 2020. It has undergone significant improvements through Phantom Liberty expansion and Patch 2.0, enhancing role-playing progression systems, enemy AI, and adding a new district to Night City with a spy-thriller storyline. The game is set in a neon-infused open world with futuristic heists, daunting choices, and striking characters. The improvements have justified the hype around the game, making it a more evolved version than its initial release. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: PHANTOM LIBERTY
description: Phantom Liberty is an expansion for Cyberpunk 2077 that adds a new district to the game's world, complete with its own spy-thriller storyline. It also includes improvements to the game's role-playing progression systems and enemy AI. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: CD PROJEKT
description: CD Projekt is the company behind Cyberpunk 2077. They released the game initially in 2020 and have since worked on improving it through expansions and patches. [Polygon, 2020-12-10]

name: DEAD SPACE
description: Dead Space is a survival horror video game developed by Motive Studio. The game is set on a deteriorating ship in outer space and follows the formula of Resident Evil 4 with a third-person-action focus. The remake of Dead Space has brought quality-of-life changes and underappreciated updates, making it hard to imagine going back to the original. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: MOTIVE STUDIO
description: Motive Studio is the developer of the Dead Space remake. They have updated the original game with quality-of-life changes and improvements, making the remake a paragon for sci-fi horror in a confined and claustrophobic setting. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: OCTOPATH TRAVELER 2
description: Octopath Traveler 2, a sequel to the first Octopath Traveler game, showcases significant enhancements over its predecessor, addressing criticisms regarding repetitive level design, monotonous narrative structure, and awkward character portrayals. This JRPG (Japanese Role-Playing Game) expertly challenges player expectations by presenting eight distinct playable characters, each with their own unique plot threads that weave together to create a rich and varied narrative experience. The game further improves upon the original with refined turn-based battles and expanded side quests, skillfully blending familiar comfort with innovative subversion to offer a fresh take on genre storytelling. Released in 2023, Octopath Traveler 2 demonstrates a masterful approach to game design, ensuring a captivating and engaging experience for both new and returning players.

name: ACQUIRE
description: Acquire is one of the developers of Octopath Traveler 2. They have contributed to the game's improvements, making it a more enjoyable and evolved version of the original. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: DAVE THE DIVER
description: Dave the Diver is a captivating video game that masterfully combines an array of engaging activities, including fishing, restaurant management, and farming. The game's protagonist, Dave, leads a dual life, diving into the mysterious Blue Hole during the day, where he encounters a rich and diverse cast of characters. By night, Dave transforms into a sushi restaurateur, requiring players to juggle the demands of running a successful eatery. Adding to the game's unique charm, it features a rhythm video game segment, further enhancing the interactive experience. Critics have described Dave the Diver as a delicate balancing act of absurdity and silliness, blending these elements with a surprising earnestness that creates a storyline both quirky and heartfelt. Released in 2023, the game has quickly gained attention for its innovative gameplay and memorable narrative, making it a standout title in the realm of video games.

name: RESIDENT EVIL 4 REMAKE
description: "RESIDENT EVIL 4 REMAKE, developed by Capcom, is a comprehensive reimagining of the iconic 2005 action-survival-horror game, Resident Evil 4. This remake sets a high standard for game remakes by featuring improved controls and more nuanced gameplay, while also introducing new elements and details that enhance the survival aspects of the game. Despite these enhancements, the remake preserves the camp and cheese that made the original game enduringly popular. RESIDENT EVIL 4 REMAKE is available on a variety of platforms, including PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Windows PC, and Xbox Series X, ensuring a wide accessibility for fans of the series and newcomers alike."

name: CAPCOM
description: CAPCOM, a renowned video game developer, has made significant strides in the gaming industry with its expertise in creating captivating and successful titles. Known for developing the Resident Evil series, CAPCOM has set the standard for game remakes, as exemplified by the Resident Evil 4 Remake, which showcases their mastery in controls and gameplay. Additionally, CAPCOM has demonstrated its versatility by hitting the gym and returning stronger than before with Street Fighter 6. This game features a robust, single-player, RPG-lite beat-'em-up mode called World Tour, further solidifying CAPCOM's reputation for delivering high-quality and engaging gaming experiences. As of 2023, CAPCOM continues to innovate and push the boundaries of what video games can offer, as noted by Polygon on October 31, 2023.

name: RESIDENT EVIL 2 REMAKE
description: Resident Evil 2 Remake is a video game developed by Capcom, which changed the perspective of its source material without sacrificing the focus on horror and survival

name: RESIDENT EVIL 3 REMAKE
description: Resident Evil 3 Remake is a video game developed by Capcom, which brought the design conceits of the original game to a modern audience, despite being forgettable

name: ARMORED CORE 6: FIRES OF RUBICON
description: Armored Core 6: Fires of Rubicon is a video game developed by FromSoftware, available on PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Windows PC, Xbox One, and Xbox Series X. It is described as a game where the giant robot you pilot feels the weight of a six-story building but moves as agile as a hummingbird, with an armory that could rival a small nation

name: STREET FIGHTER 6
description: Street Fighter 6 is a video game developed by Capcom, available on PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Windows PC, and Xbox Series X. It offers a robust single-player mode, solid online modes, and a cast of memorable new and returning World Warriors. The game features an innovative new control scheme called Modern Controls, which is easy to grasp and viable competitively. It also has finely honed one-on-one fighting mechanics, a well-populated social space called the Battle Hub, and a rock-solid online infrastructure. The game includes a compelling new roster of characters led by classics like Ryu, Zangief, and Chun-Li, and dazzling newcomers Marisa, Manon, and Kimberly. Street Fighter 6 is one of the best games of 2023, regardless of genre. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: WORLD TOUR MODE
description: World Tour mode is a robust, single-player, RPG-lite beat-’em-up mode in Street Fighter 6, similar to Sega’s Yakuza games. In this mode, players hit the streets of Metro City where everyone knows how to fight and relishes impromptu fisticuffs with strangers. It’s a matter of local pride. The streets of Metro City are part training grounds, part beginning of a silly, epic worldwide adventure where you learn the basics of Street Fighter 6. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: MODERN CONTROLS
description: Modern Controls is an innovative new control scheme in Street Fighter 6. While the six-button layout from the very first Street Fighter is still available, after multiple attempts at giving players a simplified control scheme, Capcom’s finally cracked it. Modern Controls are not only comparatively easy to grasp but are also pretty viable competitively. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: BATTLE HUB
description: Battle Hub is a well-populated social space in Street Fighter 6 where there’s a robust community of other Street Fighter fans to battle against on a daily basis. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: CHARACTERS
description: Characters in Street Fighter 6 include a compelling new roster led by classics like Ryu, Zangief, and Chun-Li, and dazzling newcomers Marisa, Manon, and Kimberly. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: PIKMIN 4
description: Pikmin 4 is a video game that is described as a whimsical joy to play, with Dandori Challenges and item collection that never becomes a drag or a grind. The game features a quasi real-world setting that makes the player see their own world differently, highlighting the special things to be found in tiny corners. The game is beautiful and is recommended as a good starting point for those who have never played a Pikmin game before, with all previous games conveniently ported to the Switch. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: NINTENDO EPD
description: Nintendo EPD is the developer of Pikmin 4, a game that has been described as a whimsical joy to play. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: SUPER MARIO BROS. WONDER
description:
Super Mario Bros. Wonder, released by Nintendo EPD in 2023, is a groundbreaking 2D platformer that marks the first side-scrolling addition to the Super Mario Bros. series since New Super Mario Bros. U in 2012. The game is celebrated for its inventiveness, offering a fresh take on the classic format while maintaining the irresistible charm that has defined the franchise. Wonder Flowers and Wonder Seeds are central to the game's unique mechanics, transforming the environment and gameplay into a musical, a quiz show, a race, or a hidden object game, breaking the established laws of Mario games and encouraging players to "break the machine."

The game's map is filled with secrets, nooks, and crannies to explore, providing a rich and engaging experience. It features detailed graphics, impressive character designs, and level details that showcase unapologetically wasteful creativity. Levels are filled with unique gimmicks, such as platforms that drop when stepped on, platforms with a countdown clock, and platforms made of batteries, which are used for a short time before being discarded, adding to the game's unpredictable nature.

Super Mario Bros. Wonder introduces a new badge system, allowing players to select special abilities and unlockable upgrades, and removes time limits, offering a more relaxed gameplay experience. Extra lives can be purchased with the game's currency, adding a new layer of strategy. The game maintains balance by layering on new challenges, ensuring that players are always engaged.

The game supports local multiplayer for up to four players, who can choose from classic characters like Mario, Luigi, Princess Peach, Princess Daisy, Toad, Toadette, and more. It also includes KO Arenas and Break Time levels, providing a range of gameplay experiences. The game is speculated to be the first "true new Mario game" since Super Mario World in 1990, making it a significant departure from recent 3D Super Mario titles.

Super Mario Bros. Wonder is praised for its collision between the traditional and the new, featuring six worlds and levels in the hub area. It is described as a game that taps into nostalgia while pushing the boundaries of what a Mario game can be. The game's character named Prince Florian provides conversation and tips, adding to the game's immersive experience. Overall, Super Mario Bros. Wonder is an entrancing experience for players, whether alone, with friends, or with strangers online, promising a bright future for the iconic plumber's

name: REMEDY ENTERTAINMENT
description: Remedy Entertainment, a renowned game development studio, has made significant strides in the realm of video games with the release of Alan Wake 2. This game, hailed as one of the best of the year by Polygon, showcases Remedy's expertise in crafting experiences that blur the lines between fear and the surreal, much like the unpredictable nature of dreams. Alan Wake 2 is described as a game that masterfully mimics the fluidity and lack of structure often found in dreams, transitioning seamlessly from terrifying scenarios to bizarre, almost comical situations. This unique approach to game design has not only garnered critical acclaim but also highlights Remedy Entertainment's innovative and creative vision in the gaming industry, as noted by JR on 2023-10-31.

name: PLAYSTATION 5
description: The PlayStation 5, a cutting-edge gaming console, serves as a premier platform for playing titles such as Alan Wake 2 and Marvel's Spider-Man 2. As of 2023, it is specifically noted that Alan Wake 2 is available on the PlayStation 5, providing gamers with an immersive experience, as reported by Polygon on October 31, 2023. Moreover, Marvel's Spider-Man 2 is exclusive to the PlayStation 5, showcasing the console's capabilities in delivering enhanced speed and fluidity in gameplay, as mentioned in the source text. This console is a go-to choice for fans of both action-adventure and superhero genres, offering them the opportunity to enjoy their favorite games with superior performance.

name: WINDOWS PC
description: Windows PC is one of the platforms where Alan Wake 2 can be played. [Polygon, 2023-10-31]

name: ALAN WAKE 2
description: Alan Wake 2, developed by Remedy Entertainment, is a captivating video game available on PlayStation 5, Windows PC, and Xbox Series X. The narrative revolves around a woman's harrowing journey through a dense, enigmatic forest as she searches for a body. This forest, with its perplexing geography, serves as a central character in the game, housing individuals who seem out of place and rooms that intriguingly transform with each visit. Alan Wake 2 delves into the realms of dreams and repetition, inviting players to explore the intricate process of deriving meaning from their experiences and the stories they encounter. As of 2023-10-31, the game offers a unique and immersive experience that challenges conventional storytelling in video games.

name: BALDUR’S GATE 3
description:
"Baldur's Gate 3, developed by Larian Studios, is a computer role-playing game that has made a significant impact in the realm of video games, available on PlayStation 5 and Windows PC. The game's release in August 2023 coincided with the resurgence of Dungeons & Dragons, capturing the essence of the tabletop game and translating it into a digital masterpiece. It has received widespread acclaim, transitioning from a niche interest to a mainstream sensation, thanks in part to two years of player feedback that Larian Studios incorporated into the game's development.

The game is set in the Forgotten Realms of Dungeons & Dragons, offering players a rich and immersive experience. It presents twelve classes to choose from, including Barbarian, Bard, Cleric, Druid, Fighter, Monk, Paladin, Ranger, Rogue, Sorcerer, Warlock, and Wizard, each with unique subclasses, feats, and builds. Players can gain Armor Proficiency with Medium Armor and shields, increase their Strength or Dexterity by 1, to a maximum of 20, learn a cantrip, and reduce the number they need to roll a Critical Hit while attacking by 1, with the effect stacking. Moreover, the game allows players to select different races and subraces, each with features that complement certain classes, such as extra movement or proficiency with specific weapons.

Baldur's Gate 3 has been instrumental in helping players, like Petrana Radulovic, understand the more intricate mechanics of Dungeons & Dragons, particularly combat. The game provides ample opportunities for creative problem solving and combat, enabling players to experiment with multiple classes when playing solo or managing a party. Players can encounter and interact with characters like Astarion, a vampire, early in the game, where dealing with his vampirism becomes a significant part of the gameplay. Other characters, such as Thaniel and Oliver, also feature prominently, adding depth to the narrative.

The game's story can be experienced through a custom character, allowing for a personalized journey. Players must complete quests to lift curses on the lands, such as the Shadow Curse, which can be broken by visiting the Last Light Inn in the second act of the game. Overall, Baldur's Gate 3 is a comprehensive and engaging role-playing game that has captivated players with its intricate mechanics, immersive story, and diverse character options."

name: LARIAN STUDIOS
description: Larian Studios is the developer of Baldur’s Gate 3, a game that has contributed to the renaissance of Dungeons & Dragons and received widespread acclaim after its launch in August. [2023-10-31]

name: DUNGEONS & DRAGONS
description: "Dungeons & Dragons, a tabletop role-playing game that has significantly influenced the board gaming renaissance, has experienced a resurgence in popularity, partly attributed to the growing interest in actual-play series such as Critical Role and Dimension 20. The game has recently been embroiled in controversy over its Open Game License (OGL) fiasco, which has sparked discussions and debates within the gaming community. Among its avid players are Mike Haracz and Petrana Radulovic, demonstrating the game's enduring appeal across different demographics. Mike Haracz is currently in the seventh year of a homebrew campaign, showcasing the game's potential for long-term engagement and creative storytelling. Petrana Radulovic, on the other hand, started playing Dungeons & Dragons in 2020, indicating the game's ability to attract new players even amidst its ongoing evolution and challenges."

name: CRITICAL ROLE
description: Critical Role is an actual-play series that has contributed to the renaissance of Dungeons & Dragons. [2023-10-31]

name: DIMENSION 20
description: Dimension 20 is an actual-play, improv-based TV show airing on Dropout, a streaming platform. The series has notably contributed to the resurgence of Dungeons & Dragons, showcasing the talents of improv comedians who get to explore narrative-driven storytelling in a format that differs from traditional stage performances. As of the platform's 5th anniversary announcement in September 2023, Dimension 20 has three seasons in its lineup, each season offering a unique and fun experience with specific subgenres, such as Secret of NIMH and Watership Down, which are referenced as examples of the show's creative range. This series provides a captivating blend of improvisation and role-playing, making it a standout program on Dropout.

name: NINTENDO
description:
Nintendo is a renowned Japanese video game company, celebrated for its creativity and innovation in the gaming industry. They are the masterminds behind the Super Mario Bros. franchise, which has captivated audiences since the release of Super Mario Bros. on the NES and SNES, and further revolutionized gaming with Super Mario 64, introducing 3D gameplay. In recent developments, Nintendo has released the Switch OLED, an updated version of their popular gaming console, featuring an improved screen while retaining the original hardware specifications. The company also offers subscription services that provide access to free digital titles, online multiplayer, and cloud-based saves, enhancing the gaming experience for its users.

Adding to their legacy, Nintendo is set to release Super Mario Bros. Wonder, a game that has sparked speculation as potentially being the first "true new Mario game" since Super Mario World in 1990. The development team behind Super Mario Bros. Wonder reportedly brainstormed over 2,000 ideas, demonstrating the company's commitment to delivering games that are rich in creativity and imagination. Rumors are circulating that Nintendo Switch's successor could be unveiled early next year, further solidifying Nintendo's position as a leading force in the evolution of gaming hardware and software.

name: INSOMNIA
description: Insomnia is a sleep disorder affecting millions of people in the UK, with studies showing women are 40% more likely to be affected than men after puberty, possibly due to hormonal differences such as menstruation, pregnancy, and menopause [Source: The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-01]

name: DR BROWNING
description: Dr Browning, a medical professional with a doctorate in insomnia, is a sleep therapist who passionately advocates for the effectiveness of Cognitive Behavioral Therapy for Insomnia (CBTI) as a long-term solution for treating insomnia. In an article published by The Independent - Life and Style on 2023-10-01, Dr Browning expresses frustration over the quick fixes often proposed in the field and highlights the exploitation of vulnerable insomniacs. Additionally, the expert comments on the introduction of the new drug Quviviq, providing insights into its potential impact on the treatment landscape for sleep disorders. Dr Browning emphasizes the importance of therapy over short-term fixes, aiming to empower insomniacs with sustainable strategies for managing their condition.

name: ROSE DAVIES-SMITH
description: Rosie Davies-Smith is a PR consultant who has spent over £600 on various insomnia treatments, including medications, teas, supplements, weighted blankets, and eye masks, finding true relief through therapy [Source: The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-01]

name: COGNITIVE BEHAVIOURAL THERAPY FOR INSOMNIA (CBTI)
description: CBTI is a therapy specifically designed to address insomnia by tackling the negative thoughts and worries that perpetuate the condition, described by Dr Browning as a "complete cure" [Source: The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-01]

name: QUVIVIQ
description: Quviviq, a groundbreaking medication for treating insomnia, has recently been approved by the NHS. Unlike traditional sleeping pills, Quviviq does not cause tolerance, making it a potentially more effective and sustainable solution for those struggling with sleep disorders. Dr. Browning has shared positive sentiments about Quviviq's potential, further highlighting its promising role in the field of sleep medicine. [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-01]

name: CBTI
description: CBTI (Cognitive Behavioral Therapy for Insomnia) is a treatment method that addresses the negative thoughts and worries that perpetuate insomnia, considered the gold standard across the world. [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-01]

name: NHS
description: The NHS (National Health Service) approved the new drug Quviviq for treating insomnia. [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-01]

name: PRIDE AND PREJUDICE
description: Pride and Prejudice is a book by Jane Austen that can be narrated in one's head as a way to deal with insomnia. [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-01]

name: APPLE TV+
description: Apple TV+ is a comprehensive streaming service that offers a diverse range of content to its global audience. As highlighted by Sporting News on 2023-10-07 and 2023-10-04, Apple TV+ is the exclusive platform for the MLS Season Pass, providing viewers with access to Major League Soccer matches, including the highly anticipated Chicago Fire vs. Inter Miami game. Additionally, The Independent - Life and Style reported on 2023-10-01 that Apple TV+ is home to the show 'Still Up', further enriching its entertainment offerings beyond sports. This service is a one-stop destination for both sports enthusiasts and entertainment seekers, making it a significant player in the streaming market.

name: STILL UP

name: ISRAEL-HAMAS WAR
description:
The Israel-Hamas war, a significant conflict that erupted in 2023, has had far-reaching implications both on the ground and in the digital sphere. In Tel Aviv, the real estate market and office space leasing have been potentially impacted by the unrest, as reported by Globes English | Israel Business Arena on December 3, 2023. The war has also led to a major protest event in the United States, with hundreds of demonstrators gathering outside the Capitol, as noted by Fortune on October 18, 2023, which underscores the global political challenges and intensifying concerns at home and abroad.

In response to the conflict, Meta, the parent company of various social media platforms, has taken proactive measures to address risks associated with the dissemination of information related to the Israel-Hamas war. According to TechCrunch on October 13, 2023, Meta has prioritized livestreaming checks and implemented hashtag blocking to render certain terms associated with the conflict non-searchable on its platforms. These actions were taken amidst the EU's concerns about illegal content and disinformation being spread on X, another platform, as part of the broader digital response to the war. Meta's policy adjustments and tool enhancements reflect the company's commitment to managing the complex dynamics of content moderation during times of international conflict.

name: LINDA YACCARINO
description:
Linda Yaccarino, the CEO of X, a prominent technology and social media platform, has been actively addressing significant community dynamics and content management issues. In response to the EU's warning regarding the proliferation of extremist content on the platform, Yaccarino assured that a leadership group had been convened to consider X's response, emphasizing the platform's commitment to safety and compliance. She reported that X had removed tens of thousands of pieces of content, thousands of posts, and hundreds of accounts linked to terrorist groups, violence, or extremism, demonstrating proactive measures taken to curb such activities [TechCrunch, 2023-10-13].

Contradicting earlier claims by Elon Musk, Yaccarino provided an update on the platform's activity levels, stating that X was seeing 500 million posts per day, a figure that underscores the platform's massive user engagement and the scale of content moderation challenges [TechCrunch, 2023-10-07]. This highlights the significant volume of content that X manages daily, necessitating robust systems and policies to ensure a safe and compliant community environment.

name: MUSK
description: Musk, a billionaire owner of X, has been making significant changes to the platform in 2023 with a focus on enhancing profitability. As part of these efforts, major layoffs were executed, affecting areas such as content moderation and human rights, according to TechCrunch on October 13, 2023. Additionally, Musk is the individual responsible for the decision to withdraw X from the EU's Code of Practice on online disinformation earlier in the year, further illustrating his strategic direction for the company. These actions reflect Musk's approach to managing X, balancing financial objectives with decisions that impact the platform's role in global information dissemination.

name: COMMUNITY NOTES FEATURE
description: Community Notes feature is a technology introduced by X that crowdsources additional context to add to questionable tweets as its main response to disinformation risks [TechCrunch, 2023-10-13]

name: ISRAELI MILITARY
description: In 2023, the Israeli Military, serving as the protective force of the state of Israel, reported a significant and tragic event. On October 13, TechCrunch published information stating that over 1,200 people were killed as a result of an attack by Hamas, a Palestinian militant group. This incident highlights the ongoing conflict and the severe impact it has on the region, as detailed by the Israeli Military's official reports.

This information underscores the critical role the GAZA MINISTRY OF HEALTH plays in addressing the health and safety concerns of the population amidst conflict, providing updates and reports on the impact of violence on the community.

name: OPENAI INC.
description: OpenAI, Inc. is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit that acts as the governing body for OpenAI, the AI startup behind ChatGPT, DALL-E 3, GPT-4, and other highly capable generative AI systems. The company has announced that Sam Altman has been fired from his position as CEO and board member due to issues with his communications with other board members. OpenAI's mission is to ensure that artificial general intelligence benefits all humanity, and the board remains fully committed to this mission. The company has appointed Mira Murati as the interim CEO and will begin a formal search for a permanent CEO immediately [source: TechCrunch, 2023-11-17]

name: GREG BROCKMAN
description: Greg Brockman, a co-founder of OpenAI, has had a dynamic tenure with the company. Initially serving as the chairman of the board, Brockman announced his resignation from the position amidst the board's decision to fire Sam Altman, a colleague and fellow co-founder. However, Brockman's role within OpenAI has evolved rather than diminished; he stepped down as chairman but remained as the company's president, reporting to the newly-appointed interim CEO, Mira Murati. This transition was speculated to be due to a disagreement on long-term strategy or Brockman's involvement in a major deal that the board did not favor. Despite his demotion and subsequent resignation from the presidency, there are persistent rumors suggesting that Brockman might return to OpenAI in some capacity. In the meantime, Brockman is also considering a move to Microsoft to lead a new AI research team, indicating his continued interest and influence in the AI sector. His potential return to OpenAI or move to Microsoft highlights the fluid nature of leadership in the tech industry and Brockman's significant role in shaping AI research and development.

As highlighted by OpenAI, AGI is not merely an academic pursuit but a practical goal with significant economic implications. It is envisioned to surpass human capabilities in most economically valuable work, making it a cornerstone in OpenAI's mission. This advanced form of AI, as described in TechCrunch articles dated 2023-11-17 and 2023-11-18, is central to discussions about the future of technology and its potential to transform various industries by automating complex tasks that currently require human intelligence.

name: TAYLOR SWIFT
description:
Taylor Swift, a 33-year-old Grammy-winning singer-songwriter, has been in a confirmed relationship with NFL player Travis Kelce since summer 2023. Swift, known for her Easter egg-filled hints and references in her music and public appearances, first sparked rumors of their relationship when Kelce attempted to give her a friendship bracelet with his number on it during one of her Eras Tour shows. She confirmed their relationship in July 2023, and has since attended multiple Kansas City Chiefs games, including a game against the New York Jets on 1 October 2023, and a game against the Green Bay Packers on 3 December 2023, which became the most-watched Sunday NFL show since the Super Bowl LVII in February 2023. Swift's presence at these games has led to increased viewership and engagement with NFL games among her massive fan base of 103.7992 million Swifties worldwide.

Swift, who has faced significant challenges in her career, including the loss of the master recordings of her first six studio albums and personal attacks, has re-recorded her music catalogue, releasing four "Taylor's Version" albums. She continues to perform for her fans, even under difficult circumstances, and her ongoing concert tour, The Eras Tour, has been turned into a concert film. The average cost of a ticket for the North American leg of her tour was $3,801, a significant increase from her 2018 Reputation Stadium Tour. Swift sold over $100 million of tickets for her concert movie as of 2023-10-10.

Swift's live performances are often compared to those of BTS and Beyoncé, and her concert experiences are appreciated by fans. She recently commented on a viral TikTok video of three young fans struggling to open one of her CDs, expressing amazement at the video. Swift also mentioned her relationship with Kelce in her "Karma" lyrics during her Eras Tour show in Buenos Aires, Argentina, on 3 November 2023, where Kelce was in attendance.

Swift and Kelce have been seen together at sports events and on a date in New York City after the season 49 premiere of Saturday Night Live. A source claimed to Yahoo Entertainment that Swift and Kelce "have talked about kids" within the next year. Swift attended a Chiefs game on September

name: TRAVIS KELCE
description:
Travis Kelce, a 34-year-old tight end for the Kansas City Chiefs in the National Football League, has been in a relationship with Taylor Swift since the summer of 2023. Their romance began after Kelce attempted to give Swift his phone number by presenting her with a friendship bracelet at one of her Eras Tour shows, which he attended in Kansas City and later in Buenos Aires, Argentina, where Swift acknowledged their relationship in her "Karma" lyrics. Kelce, a sports personality and Taylor Swift's boyfriend, has been seen with her at various events, including a date in New York City while she was re-recording her 1989 tracks there. He has also expressed his admiration for Swift's skills as a musician and how being around her has been mind-blowing, despite the public attention their relationship has attracted.

Kelce, known for his ability to exploit defenses and potentially score multiple times in a game, is a key target for opposing teams, as evidenced in a fantasy football analysis by Sporting News. He has hosted "Saturday Night Live" in March, showcasing his storytelling skills. During a game against the New York Jets on October 1, 2023, Kelce commented on the NFL's coverage of Taylor Swift, and he later addressed her attendance at his games on his podcast, New Heights with Jason and Travis Kelce, noting the excitement it brought to Chiefs Kingdom and the memorable nature of the games. Amid their ongoing romance, Kelce's remarks about starting his own family resurfaced, sparking controversy.

In addition to the media attention surrounding his relationship with Swift, Kelce has also faced backlash for previous comments he made about women, referring to them as "breeders." Despite this, he is proud of his relationship with Swift and is not letting the media scrutiny affect it. Kelce has attempted to delete some of his tweets before they went viral, including one about a squirrel and bread that went viral due to a spelling mistake. The relationship has had a significant impact on Kelce's personal brand, leading to increased jersey sales and Instagram followers.

Travis Kelce, a professional athlete, is not only a football star but also a podcast host alongside his brother Jason Kelce. Their podcast, New Heights, has been the platform where Kelce has shared personal insights and experiences, including his interactions with Taylor Swift and the dynamics of their relationship.
