name: LIFESTYLE EDIT NEWSLETTER
description: The Lifestyle Edit Newsletter is a free weekly publication offered by The Independent, designed to keep its subscribers informed about the latest trends in fashion and beyond. This newsletter, which requires a valid email address for sign-up, is not merely a source of fashion updates but also explores trends in various other lifestyle areas, ensuring that readers are well-equipped to stay ahead in multiple facets of modern living. As a comprehensive guide, Lifestyle Edit provides insights into a wide range of interests, making it a valuable resource for anyone looking to keep abreast of current styles and lifestyle shifts. The newsletter has been consistently published by The Independent throughout late 2023, as evidenced by the dates of the sources provided, ranging from October 16 to December 12.

name: KANSAS CITY CHIEFS
description: The Kansas City Chiefs, a professional American football team based in Kansas City, Missouri, and members of the National Football League (NFL), have been making headlines for their impressive performance and strategic gameplay. As of the 2023 season, the Chiefs are ranked 2nd with a record of 7-2, having benefited from the Baltimore Ravens' loss, which allowed them to regain the AFC's top seed and secure home-field advantage. Patrick Mahomes, a significant player, leads the team, which is also known for its strong defensive capabilities. They have successfully limited their opponents' rushing plays to 12-plus yards and have only allowed one rushing touchdown to a running back this season. The Chiefs have faced various opponents, including the New York Jets in Week 4 and the Green Bay Packers in a prime-time game, showcasing their competitive edge. However, they did suffer a loss to the Broncos, which was an unexpected outcome. Travis Kelce, a talented tight end, is a key player for the Kansas City Chiefs. The team has also gained attention from celebrity fans, with Taylor Swift attending multiple games of the Chiefs during the 2023 season, further highlighting the team's popularity and influence in the sports and entertainment world.

name: NFL
description: The National Football League (NFL), a major American sports organization, is a professional American football league comprising 32 teams, equally divided between the National Football Conference (NFC) and the American Football Conference (AFC). The NFL organizes various games, including 'Sunday Night Football' matches between Kansas City and the Packers, as well as Kansas City and the Jets, and 'Monday Night Football' games featuring the Raiders against the Lions, and the Bears versus the Vikings. Notable teams in the league include the Cowboys, 49ers, Buffalo Bills, Cincinnati Bengals, Bears, and Panthers. Travis Kelce, a tight end for the Chiefs, is a significant figure in the NFL, and his rumored relationship with Taylor Swift has expanded the league's audience and increased interest and viewership, as seen in the game between the Chiefs and New York Jets on December 3, 2023. The NFL hosts annual awards for achievements by players and coaches, with longshot candidates for awards such as MVP, OPOY, DPOY, Coach of the Year, and Comeback POY discussed in terms of betting odds and considerations. The league is the most popular odds market for betting in the US, surpassing the NBA in terms of betting interest, and NFL betting sites offer a wide variety of bet types, including many prop bet opportunities. The NFL has defended its actions of changing social media bios to reflect Taylor Swift's lyrics, considering it a pop cultural moment. The league has grown from its inception in 1920 to a $18 billion business today, aiming for a $27 billion target by 2027 under Commissioner Roger Goodell's leadership, with strategies to dominate the world sporting scene. The NFL's master plan includes a potential shift towards global recognition, expanding its reach beyond American shores. Teams' strategic use of timeouts is also a topic of discussion, with only 14 instances since 2020 where teams have used all their first-half timeouts above four minutes.

name: ERAS TOUR
description: The Eras Tour is a concert series embarked upon by the renowned singer Taylor Swift, scheduled to run until November 2024. Each concert in the tour is an extensive showcase, lasting over 180 minutes, during which Swift performs more than 40 songs, drawing from at least nine of her albums. The tour is characterized by its elaborate production, featuring 16 costume changes per show. To prepare for this demanding tour, Swift engaged in rigorous training, which included singing the entire set list while running on a treadmill, undergoing a three-month dance training program, and taking rest days after a series of performances. Notably, during one of the shows in Buenos Aires, Argentina, on 3 November 2023, NFL player Travis Kelce attended and attempted to give Swift his number by presenting her with a friendship bracelet, an incident that garnered attention from The Independent - Life and Style in 2023.

name: BUENOS AIRES, ARGENTINA
description: Buenos Aires, Argentina, is the location where Taylor Swift's Eras Tour show took place on 3 November 2023, where Travis Kelce was in attendance. [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-12-06]

name: WSJ MAGAZINE
description: WSJ Magazine, a distinguished publication in the realm of lifestyle and culture, featured an exclusive interview with the renowned football player Travis Kelce in December 2023. During the conversation, Kelce candidly discussed his relationship with Taylor Swift, the celebrated singer-songwriter, and expressed his profound admiration for her exceptional skills as a musician. The admiration for Swift's musical prowess was a recurring theme in Kelce's discussions with WSJ Magazine, as evidenced by his comments in an earlier interview on November 25, 2023, where he also praised her talents. Through these interviews, WSJ Magazine provided its readers with unique insights into the personal life and interests of Travis Kelce, highlighting the intersection of sports and entertainment.

name: KICK
description: Kick is a burgeoning streaming platform that has been making waves in the technology and entertainment communities, particularly for its more favorable revenue splits compared to established platforms like Twitch and YouTube. This young platform offers a 95/5 revenue split to its streamers, which has attracted a growing number of content creators, including Kelly, who now earns over $1,000 per month with 145 subscribers. Despite facing controversies, such as ties to a crypto gambling site and a scandal involving a sex worker that raised safety concerns, especially among women, Kick has maintained a focus on gaming and creative content. The platform addressed the incident in a public post, emphasizing the importance of community and public safety in content creation. They are committed to reviewing and refining their policies, though specific details may not be disclosed for privacy and confidentiality reasons. In response to the controversy, Kick took action by removing Denino from the front page and featured category. While Kick's presence at TwitchCon 2023, with its nearby gaming lounge, was initially perceived as a haunting presence, it did not negatively impact the positive atmosphere of the event. The platform's light moderation approach, however, has been a point of contention, leading to discord among Twitch's community and causing some streamers to consider leaving for Kick's seemingly more lucrative and supportive environment.

description: Bree is a Kick streamer who does not feel safe returning to Twitch due to the harassment she faced on that platform. She acknowledges that Kick's decision not to ban Denino does hurt, but she understands the business perspective with contracts involved. name: BOB
description: Bob, also recognized by his online alias BobDuckNWeave, is a content creator and streamer who recently announced his departure from the platform Kick amidst a significant controversy. The incident, involving a sex worker, led Bob to criticize Kick's "non-response" and lack of action, as reported by TechCrunch on September 30, 2023. Disappointed with the platform's policies and moderation, Bob joined a chorus of other streamers who vowed to leave Kick, acknowledging the series of controversies that have marred its short existence. His decision to disassociate himself from the platform was a clear statement of his stance on the importance of ethical conduct and responsible community management in the digital entertainment space.

name: TWITCH
description:
Twitch, initially launched in 2011 as Justin.tv, is a leading live streaming platform that primarily caters to gamers and young adults, with over 70% of its viewers falling between the ages of 18 and 34 in 2022. The platform has evolved from a focus on gaming content to include lifestyle, beauty, and sports, reflecting the changing dynamics of the internet and the gaming industry. Twitch hosts annual conventions, TwitchCon, in both Europe and North America, which have seen improvements in crowd management and layout, although the choice of Las Vegas as a location in 2023 was met with criticism due to its emphasis on drinking and gambling, which is incompatible with much of Twitch's usership.

The platform has faced community backlash over policy changes that affected creators' monetization, including the end of a 70/30 subscription revenue split and restrictions on embedded ads and sponsored content. Twitch has since introduced the Partner Plus program, which offers a higher revenue share but has steep requirements that exclude the majority of Twitch Partners. The company has also been working on improving the ad experience by allowing ad breaks to be synchronized with content and involving moderators and the community in adjusting those breaks. Twitch is part of Amazon, the third largest and fastest growing advertising business in the world, which provides a unique opportunity for expanding the reach of advertisers to a broader set of potential partners.

Despite its popularity, Twitch has been a source of concern for some streamers, including Bree, a Kick streamer who felt unsafe due to harassment, and Bob, another creator who mentioned leaving Kick. Many streamers, including those transitioning from Kick, find that Twitch alone does not provide enough income to pay their bills. Twitch's decision to cut the premium 70/30 revenue deal for select streamers in favor of its ad revenue program has angered many creators.

Twitch is not supported for livestreaming from Meta's smart glasses, although it remains a popular choice among content creators. The platform has launched the Sports Accelerator Program to support sports content creators wanting to engage in sports talk, such as podcasts, talk shows, reaction streams, sidecasts, watch-alongs, and more, through live workshops and by providing opportunities to network and expand their viewership. Twitch serves the needs of advertisers and streamers by offering both performance-based and brand awareness models. The company is addressing discord within its community and competition from other platforms like YouTube and

name: RACHEL
description:
Rachel, the wife of Jordan Poyer, is a multifaceted personality known for her significant influence and diverse talents. She is grateful for Jordan's discovery of ayahuasca, which transformed him into a more appreciative and loving husband and father. This change in Jordan has also positively impacted their family life. Rachel boasts a strong online presence with over 4 million followers on Instagram, where she shares glimpses of her life and interests. She has expanded her digital footprint to include an OnlyFans page and has ventured into the business world with her own line of skincare products.

In addition to her social media endeavors, Rachel is a streamer and content creator on YouTube, where she shares cooking videos, showcasing her culinary skills and engaging with her audience. Despite the opportunities provided by Kick, a platform that caters to smaller creators, Rachel made the decision to leave due to the platform's objectification of people, demonstrating her commitment to personal values and the well-being of her community.

One memorable evening, Rachel returned home and was tidying up the kitchen when she was captivated by ethereal, haunting sounds emanating from the outside balcony upstairs. The music, a testament to Jordan's artistic growth, was a far cry from what the old Jordan Poyer could have produced, further highlighting the profound impact of his personal transformation on their lives together.

description: Darren Waller, a 31-year-old tight end (TE) with 7 years of experience, is a key player for the New York Giants. As of 2023-10-12, projections from CBSSports.com anticipated Waller to score 10.2 points in the upcoming game against the Buffalo Bills, ranking him 7th among tight ends. description: The New York Mets, a Major League Baseball (MLB) team, had an unsuccessful season in 2023, failing to secure a playoff spot despite being one of the highest spenders in the league, a fact that drew significant scrutiny. As the year came to a close, the team found itself in need of a new manager due to pentagonal vacancies, a situation that has left the organization in a state of flux. Amidst these challenges, the New York Mets were also considered a potential destination for Yoshinobu Yamamoto, a talented player whose acquisition could potentially bolster the team's roster and help them improve their performance in the upcoming seasons. [Essentially Sports, 2023-10-30]

description: The Los Angeles Angels, a professional baseball team in the Major League Baseball (MLB), have experienced a challenging year in 2023, marked by the potential departure of star players Shohei Ohtani and Mike Trout, as noted by Essentially Sports on November 18, 2023. Despite Mike Trout's persistence in staying with the team since the beginning, the Angels find themselves in a precarious situation. As of October 30, 2023, the team is in search of a new manager following the rejection of Phil Nevin's 2024 club option. Compounding their issues, the Angels are grappling with a below-par farm system and a playoff drought that has stretched over nine seasons, further clouding their future prospects amidst the uncertainty surrounding Ohtani's and Trout's status with the team.

name: HOUSTON ASTROS
description: The Houston Astros, a professional baseball team playing at Minute Maid Park, have a storied history marked by both triumph and controversy. They experienced a memorable moment in the 2005 NLDS when Chris Burke hit a walk-off home run. The team notably won the 2017 World Series, however, their victory was overshadowed by a cheating scandal that involved using trash cans to signal pitch types and stealing signs from opposing teams, which was later uncovered by an MLB investigation. Under the management of Dusty Baker, the Astros secured another World Series win in 2022 and two pennants. As of the end of 2023, the team is in search of a new manager following Baker's retirement.

Despite the gravity of the situation, the league decided against revoking the Astros' 2017 World Series win, deeming the process of determining the impact of the cheating on the outcome of games as "difficult and impractical." In response to such issues, MLB has been proactive in handing out warnings against sign stealing to maintain the integrity of the sport. Additionally, MLB betting sites have been a point of interest, offering a variety of prop bets centered on individual player statistics such as home runs, RBI, and strikeouts, reflecting the fans' enthusiasm and the league's popularity. The fans' expectations for teams to display great vigor and ferocity further underscore the competitive nature of the league.

name: INTER MIAMI
description: Inter Miami, a professional soccer team in Major League Soccer (MLS), has been at the center of significant developments in 2023. The club, coached by Gerardo Martino, experienced a notable leap in ticket prices for the 2024 season, following the high-profile arrival of Lionel Messi, as reported by Sporting News on October 4, 2023. However, despite the excitement surrounding Messi's presence, Inter Miami's performance on the field has been inconsistent. The team faced FC Cincinnati in a critical match that ultimately resulted in their elimination from the MLS playoff race, as they missed early chances and were unable to overcome the deficit, despite Messi's efforts, according to Sporting News on October 7, 2023. Earlier, on October 4, 2023, Inter Miami struggled without Messi in a 4-1 loss to the Chicago Fire, which significantly diminished their playoff hopes. The team's list of substitutes included Dos Santos, McVey, Sailor, Ulloa, J. Mota, D. Ruiz, Sunderland, and Stefanelli, indicating depth in their squad. Additionally, Inter Miami dealt with a computer glitch that caused incorrect season ticket renewal prices to be sent to supporters, further highlighting the team's off-field challenges. The premium ticket for the 2024 season was priced at $2,898, reflecting the substantial increase in season ticket prices. Rumors also circulated about Messi potentially playing on loan with Barcelona after Inter Miami's failure to qualify for the MLS playoffs, as mentioned by Sporting News Argentina on October 12, 2023. The match against FC Cincinnati was set to be significant, as it could have impacted Messi's MLS playoffs, but unfortunately, it did not lead to the desired outcome for Inter Miami.

name: FC CINCINNATI
description: FC Cincinnati, a professional soccer team competing in Major League Soccer (MLS), made significant headlines in 2023. Despite a midweek defeat, the team showcased remarkable resilience and went on to clinch the Supporters' Shield as the regular season champion. This achievement was particularly notable given the competitive nature of the league. In a pivotal match against Inter Miami, FC Cincinnati secured a 1-0 victory, thanks to a decisive 78th-minute goal by Alvaro Barreal. This win not only highlighted the team's skill but also contributed to Inter Miami's elimination from the MLS playoff race, intensifying the stakes of the game. Barreal, a key player who leads the team in minutes played, was rested midweek, demonstrating the team's strategic depth. The starting lineup for the Inter Miami match featured notable players such as Celentano in goalkeeping, Arias, Hagglund, Miazga, and Murphy in defense, Barreal, Nwobodo, and Acosta in midfield, and Moreno, Vazquez, and Santos in the forward positions. On the bench, ready to make an impact, were Kann as a substitute goalkeeper, Kubo, Mosquera, Angulo, Badji, Pinto, Halsey, Valenzuela, and Boupendza. The team's pursuit of the Golden Boot award, given to the league's top scorer, was an additional motivation driving their performance on the field.

name: LIONEL MESSI
description:
Lionel Messi, one of the most talented and legendary soccer players of all time, recently joined Inter Miami, a move that sparked a craze among fans eager to witness his prowess on the field. However, his time with the club has been marred by an injury, which caused him to miss several crucial matches, including the games against Chicago Fire and FC Cincinnati. Despite initial hopes that Messi would return for the match against FC Cincinnati, as suggested by Argentine journalist Gaston Edul, his actual participation was unclear. The absence of Messi significantly impacted Inter Miami's performance, contributing to their status as underdogs and ultimately leading to their elimination from the MLS playoff race, as the team was at the bottom of the Eastern Conference when he joined.

Messi's international career also faced a minor controversy when Antonio Sanabria spat on him during a match. Nevertheless, Messi's skills were on full display as he hit the post directly from a corner and also twice during Argentina's match against Paraguay on October 12, 2023. For that particular game, Messi was expected to start on the bench, with Nicolas Otamendi wearing the captain's armband until Messi's entry into the pitch. Despite these challenges, Messi's reputation as a professional soccer player whose presence can dramatically influence the outcome of matches remains intact, making his return to the field a highly anticipated event.

name: PREMIER LEAGUE
description:
The Premier League is a top-tier professional football league in England, recognized as a significant platform in the world of sports. It is a football league where teams like Manchester United, Chelsea, Liverpool, Aston Villa, Everton, and Manchester City are prominent participants. Manchester United and Chelsea are two of only seven teams to have won the modern Premier League, showcasing their competitive edge and historical success in the league. These two teams have also seen the most drawn matches in the league, with 19 of these draws featuring goals for both teams, highlighting the intense rivalry and evenly matched gameplay between them.

However, the league is not without its controversies. Everton has been penalized with a 10-point deduction for financial rule breaches, a decision that has sparked protests from Everton fans. Similarly, Manchester City is facing serious charges, with the Premier League accusing them of 115 financial breaches, indicating the strict financial regulations and governance within the league.

The Premier League is not just a battleground for these teams but also a stage for individual brilliance. A recent game featured a Norwegian player scoring his 13th goal, demonstrating the league's ability to foster and showcase talent. Despite the challenges and controversies, the Premier League remains a highly competitive and entertaining professional football league in England, attracting global attention and talent.

name: MLS
description: MLS, or Major League Soccer, is a professional sports league in the United States that features teams such as Inter Miami and the Chicago Fire. In a significant move, MLS inked a major media rights deal with Apple, which has resulted in almost all of its games being streamed exclusively on Apple TV, effectively placing them behind a paywall. This strategic partnership reflects the growing popularity of the league, which has also seen an increase in betting activities, including a rise in the number of prop bets at sportsbooks across the nation. As of 2024, Inter Miami, one of the competing clubs in MLS, has notably increased its ticket prices, setting them significantly higher than those of other clubs within the league, as reported by Sporting News on October 4, 2023. These developments underscore the dynamic and evolving nature of MLS, both in terms of media accessibility and financial strategies.

name: COINBASE
description:
Coinbase, a prominent player in the fintech industry and the fourth-largest global crypto exchange by daily volume, has experienced significant fluctuations in its stock value amidst a turbulent year for the cryptocurrency market. As reported by Alex for TechCrunch on 2023-12-09, the company's value has been pushed higher by investors betting on the rebound of consumer trading of equity and crypto. This optimism is reflected in the stock's rally, with a more than 60% increase in the same month that saw the founders of FTX and Binance brace for potential legal consequences, as noted by Cnbc | World Business News Leader on 2023-11-30.

Coinbase, which went public in 2021, has demonstrated resilience in the face of the so-called crypto winter, unlike many of its competitors. Its shares have seen a remarkable climb of over 250% in the first 11 months of 2023, showcasing the company's strong position in the market. With a market cap of close to $30 billion, Coinbase's share price has seen a 20% increase since Binance's settlement, although it experienced a 2.4% drop to $124.72 on Thursday, as reported by Cnbc | World Business News Leader on 2023-11-30, which temporarily erased some of the recent gains.

Despite its market success, Coinbase is not without challenges. The company is currently engaged in legal battles with the SEC, which adds an element of uncertainty to its future trajectory. Nevertheless, Coinbase's performance in 2023 has been characterized by significant growth and investor confidence, positioning it as a key entity in the evolving landscape of cryptocurrency and fintech.

name: BRIAN ARMSTRONG
description:
Brian Armstrong, the CEO of Coinbase, a leading cryptocurrency exchange, has made significant comments regarding the state of the crypto industry and Coinbase's strategic direction amidst regulatory challenges. According to CNBC, a world-renowned business news leader as of November 30, 2023, Armstrong observed that the Binance settlement, a pivotal event in the crypto space, has enabled the industry to progress beyond a series of scandals. He emphasized that regulatory clarity is crucial for attracting more investment, particularly from institutional investors, suggesting a positive outlook for the sector's growth and stability.

In the same report, Armstrong also expressed criticism towards the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC), indicating that the regulatory environment in the U.S. is a concern for Coinbase. As a result, the company is exploring opportunities to increase its investments outside of the U.S., a move that reflects the broader strategy of navigating through regulatory complexities to ensure sustainable business expansion. This decision underscores the importance of global diversification in the cryptocurrency industry, as companies like Coinbase seek more favorable regulatory climates to foster innovation and growth.

name: U.S. SECURITIES AND EXCHANGE COMMISSION
description: The U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission is a government agency that regulates securities and exchanges. It has been criticized by Brian Armstrong, the CEO of Coinbase. [Cnbc | World Business News Leader, 2023-11-30]

name: SAM BANKMAN-FRIED
description:
Sam Bankman-Fried, also known as SBF, is the founder and former CEO of FTX, a now-defunct cryptocurrency exchange, and Alameda Research, a cryptocurrency trading firm. Despite his initial lack of knowledge about cryptocurrency, he started Alameda Research in 2017 during a crypto bull run. Bankman-Fried owned a significant portion of both companies, with 90 percent of Alameda and 65 percent of FTX, and had the ultimate decision-making power in case of disagreements. He lived in a $35 million penthouse in the Bahamas with many FTX employees and was in a personal relationship with Caroline Ellison, the former CEO of Alameda Research, which began in the fall of 2018.

Bankman-Fried is currently on trial for seven counts of criminal charges, including wire fraud, conspiracy to commit money laundering, and conspiracy to misuse customer funds. His actions have affected the lives of those closest to him, including co-conspirators and family members. He is accused of misusing billions of dollars in FTX customer deposits for personal gain, including real estate purchases, investments, and political contributions. He also allegedly created special features in FTX's code to allow Alameda unlimited access to FTX funds, effectively giving Alameda an infinite line of credit. During the trial, he has been repeatedly scolded by Judge Lewis Kaplan for not answering questions and has occasionally interrupted his counsel Mark Cohen.

In November 2022, Bankman-Fried tweeted that FTX was fine and had enough assets to cover all client holdings, but this was not true. He directed Gary Wang to send customer funds to Bahamanian regulators and stall US lawyers. He claims to have learned about Alameda's $8 billion liability in October 2022 by looking at a computer database and was surprised by this information. He managed the relationship between Alameda Research and FTX, providing funds from FTX to Alameda without collateral or written terms. He testified about handling support tickets himself and the lack of a risk team, which he now considers a "big mistake." He also mentioned the "risk engine" of FTX and its issues in 2020.

Bankman-Fried's defense argues that he acted in good faith and did not defraud anyone, emphasizing his willingness to give up personal wealth to make customers whole. However, he has been found guilty of seven criminal fraud counts tied to the

name: FTX
description:
FTX, co-founded by Sam Bankman-Fried (SBF) and Gary Wang in 2019, was once a prominent and rapidly growing cryptocurrency exchange, boasting a peak valuation of $32 billion and trades up to $15 billion per day. Its success was attributed to its "risk engine," which was designed to prevent significant losses from being distributed among customers. However, the company's risk management system was compromised by a code feature called "allow_negative," which permitted Alameda Research, a related entity, to spend and withdraw unlimited amounts of money without collateral or written terms. This feature, created at the direction of SBF, allowed Alameda to use FTX customer deposits, leading to the misappropriation of customer funds for personal use and the launch of a $2 billion venture fund, FTX Ventures, in January 2022.

FTX's collapse in December 2022, triggered by Alameda's misuse of customer funds, resulted in a multi-billion-dollar deficiency and a catastrophic feedback loop that could have created losses in the "trillions of dollars." The company filed for bankruptcy on November 11th, 2022, causing a significant problem for the industry's reputation and leading to other companies also filing for bankruptcy. The collapse led to criminal charges against SBF and civil penalties from the Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) and the Commodity Futures Trading Commission (CFTC). SBF, who owned 17% of the company and had ultimate decision-making power, is currently on trial for fraud and money laundering. The trial involves a detailed code review, and it has been revealed that SBF was not entirely sure about the processes happening within the company, which was managed by teams.

Despite the legal and financial turmoil, FTX allowed Bahamian customers to withdraw their assets, making them fully whole, as per SBF's decision. However, the Securities and Exchange Commission alleges that FTX was a fraud "from the start," with a multi-billion-dollar deficiency caused by SBF's own misappropriation of customer funds. The company operated without a chief risk officer, which became a critical issue when the crypto market crashed. Mark Cohen has argued that FTX was not a Ponzi scheme but a very innovative, successful company with reasonable business practices between Alameda and FTX.

FTX's bankruptcy and the subsequent legal proceedings have cast a shadow over the crypto industry, with SBF's potential

name: BINANCE
description:
Binance, the world's largest cryptocurrency exchange by volume, has been at the forefront of the digital asset industry, boasting over $65 billion in assets on its platform. Founded by Changpeng Zhao, the company has faced significant legal challenges in 2023. Zhao, also known as the CEO, was informed about the theft of FTX customer funds by Carlton Ellison, which led Binance to start withdrawing its remaining $2.1 billion equivalent of cash in BUSD and FTT after the exposure of FTX's financial issues. In the same year, Binance's market share fell from over 60% in February to under 50% in September, possibly due to regulatory pressures and the company's legal troubles.

Binance.US, its American sister company, has also been embroiled in legal issues, including a suit by the U.S. CFTC for allegedly breaking trading and derivatives rules, and charges related to anti-money laundering. Despite these challenges, Binance claims to see a climbing percentage of institutional user transactions, indicating a shift in its customer base.

In November 2023, Binance's founder, Changpeng Zhao, pleaded guilty to violations of the Bank Secrecy Act and U.S. economic sanctions, bracing for potential prison time. This development coincided with a period when Coinbase's stock rallied more than 60%, highlighting the contrasting fortunes of the two major players in the cryptocurrency exchange market.

Following the Justice Department's announcement of a $4.3 billion settlement, Binance experienced a $1 billion customer withdrawal and a 25% drop in liquidity. Zhao appeared in court, stating that his presence was to protect users and ensure the company's longevity amidst the legal turmoil. Binance had also been involved in a deal to buy crypto broker Voyager Digital's assets, which was later terminated due to regulatory concerns.

name: CHANGPENG ZHAO
description: Changpeng Zhao, widely recognized as the founder and CEO of Binance, a leading global cryptocurrency exchange, has been at the center of significant developments in the digital asset industry. In October 2023, Zhao was informed about the theft of FTX customer funds by Carlton Ellison, an event that shook the crypto community and highlighted the need for robust security measures. However, Zhao's legal challenges did not end there. By November 30, 2023, he had pleaded guilty to serious charges including violations of the Bank Secrecy Act for failing to implement an effective anti-money laundering program and for willfully violating U.S. economic sanctions. This admission of guilt has set the stage for his sentencing, which is scheduled for February 2024, as reported by CNBC, a world leader in business news. These events underscore the complex legal landscape that cryptocurrency exchanges like Binance must navigate, and the personal and professional repercussions for their leaders when compliance is not strictly adhered to.

name: JUSTICE DEPARTMENT
description: The Justice Department, a prominent government organization, has been actively involved in significant legal and regulatory matters in both the tech and cryptocurrency sectors. In a recent development, the Justice Department announced a substantial $4.3 billion settlement with Binance, one of the world's largest cryptocurrency exchanges. This announcement, made on 2023-11-30 and covered by CNBC | World Business News Leader, led to a notable increase in customer withdrawals from Binance, subsequently causing a drop in the exchange's liquidity. Additionally, the Justice Department has taken a stance on competition within the tech industry, arguing that Google's dominant position in the search engine market has resulted in the company having minimal incentive to innovate and improve its products. This dual focus on tech giants and cryptocurrency platforms highlights the Department's role in overseeing and regulating major players across various sectors to ensure fair practices and competition.

name: SECURITIES AND EXCHANGE COMMISSION (SEC)
description: The Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC), a government regulatory body, has been actively involved in addressing significant issues within the cryptocurrency industry. The SEC has alleged that FTX, a major cryptocurrency exchange, was operating as a fraud from its inception, with a multi-billion-dollar deficiency that was caused by the misappropriation of customer funds by its founder, Sam Bankman-Fried. This serious accusation highlights the SEC's role in overseeing and enforcing regulations to protect investors and maintain fair and orderly markets. Additionally, the SEC has found itself embroiled in legal disputes with other prominent players in the crypto space, including Binance and Coinbase. However, it is noteworthy that the SEC was notably absent from the Binance settlement, indicating a complex and evolving landscape of regulatory engagement within the cryptocurrency sector.

name: ANALYSTS
description: Analysts, as referenced in the provided descriptions, have been active in providing insights on various market dynamics. Firstly, they have commented on the market's reaction to weak US data, noting that the potential for a more accommodative Federal Reserve policy has generated excitement, which seemed to offset the negative impact of Apple's stock performance, as reported by The Sydney Morning Herald on 2023-11-05. In another context, Analysts have taken a neutral stance on Coinbase's stock, setting an $80 price target, as highlighted by Cnbc | World Business News Leader on 2023-11-30. These Analysts play a crucial role in interpreting market movements and providing guidance on investment decisions, particularly in the technology and cryptocurrency sectors.

name: ETF MARKETS
description: The ETF markets are seen as more transparent, efficient, and lower cost to execute, with potential for migration to ETFs for cheaper exposure and trading, driving Coinbase to lower fees [Cnbc | World Business News Leader, 2023-11-30]

name: FORMER SEC ENFORCEMENT CHIEF
description: The former SEC enforcement chief commented on the 'casualness' in crypto compliance in a watch segment [Cnbc | World Business News Leader, 2023-11-30]

name: SBF
description: Sam Bankman-Fried, commonly known as SBF, is a former entrepreneur who co-founded and served as the CEO of FTX, a now-bankrupt cryptocurrency exchange. At the height of his career, SBF became the richest individual under 30, with a net worth of $22.5 billion, and expressed ambitions to save humanity from extinction. However, his reputation has since been marred by allegations of orchestrating the collapse of FTX, leading to a high-profile trial where he faces seven counts of fraud and conspiracy, as well as charges of money laundering. Details about his political dealings, including attempts to buy off political figures, are being revealed in Michael Lewis's book "Going Infinite." SBF has also made television appearances and engaged in marketing deals with sports icons, demonstrating his wide-ranging influence and activities within the tech and entertainment sectors prior to the legal troubles. This case is one of the most significant within the crypto space, highlighting the complex dynamics and potential risks associated with the industry.

name: MICHAEL LEWIS
description: Michael Lewis, a notable author, has been intricately involved in chronicling the activities of Sam Bankman-Fried (SBF), a key figure in the tech and finance world. Lewis met with SBF over 100 times, gathering insights that he later recounted, providing the public with a behind-the-scenes look at SBF's life. This includes details about SBF's first television appearance and his interactions with political figures. In a significant move, Lewis chose the first day of SBF's trial to debut his book "Going Infinite," which delves deeper into SBF's political dealings, offering readers a comprehensive understanding of SBF's influence and strategies in the political arena. The information is sourced from TechCrunch, with updates on October 2nd and 7th, 2023.

name: TOM BRADY
description: Tom Brady, a retired NFL player renowned for his illustrious career, has recently been in the news for reasons beyond the football field. Amidst the cheating allegations surrounding the Houston Astros, Brady's successor made a mocking statement about not being a fan of the team, drawing attention to the sports community's reactions to the scandal. Additionally, Brady has taken on a new role as a sports icon in the realm of technology and finance. In a significant move, he was paid a staggering $55 million by FTX, a leading cryptocurrency exchange, to lend legitimacy and an air of success to the company. This partnership highlights Brady's influence extending beyond sports, as he continues to make waves in the tech and entertainment sectors post-retirement.

name: STEPH CURRY
description: Steph Curry is a sports icon who was paid $35 million by FTX to lend legitimacy and edge to the company. [Source: TechCrunch, 2023-10-02]

name: ANNA WINTOUR
description: Anna Wintour is a fashion doyenne who reached out to SBF to ask him to sponsor the Met Costume Ball. [Source: TechCrunch, 2023-10-02]

name: MITCH MCCONNELL
description: Mitch McConnell is a political figure who SBF met with to discuss funding political candidates looking to offset Trump’s influence in the Republican Party. [Source: TechCrunch, 2023-10-02]

name: DONALD TRUMP
description: Donald Trump, the former President of the United States, is a significant figure in American politics, currently standing as the Republican frontrunner for the 2024 election. Despite facing legal challenges, including four indictments in the last six months for various offenses and a lawsuit by Letitia James, Trump's wealth is on the rise due to a ground lease on a property he owns, set to increase to $US30 million from about $US2.6 million based on current rent values. Trump has been found to have committed fraud by Judge Arthur Engoron in a civil lawsuit brought by New York's attorney general, for massively overvaluing his assets and exaggerating his net worth on paperwork used in making deals and securing financing. In the realm of policy, Trump criticized electric vehicles (EVs) as too expensive, lacking range, and potentially harmful to the environment and American jobs in a speech in suburban Detroit. He is also known for his strong support of Jim Jordan, particularly during the Jan. 6 Capitol attack, for which he awarded Jordan a Medal of Freedom days after the incident. Trump's 2020 election defeat led to the storming of the Capitol by armed right-wing extremists, and his campaign rally was reportedly sabotaged by TikTok users and K-pop fans. Interestingly, SBF reportedly offered Trump $5 billion to not run for president again. Trump shares the same birthday as Vincent Namatjira, and the two are featured in the painting Vincent & Donald (Happy Birthday). Trump has also claimed that he would be able to resolve the Ukraine war "in one day" if he was reelected. The Epoch Times supported Trump's 2020 election campaign through advertising and publishing articles that echoed his claims about the election.

name: STEAM DECK OLED
description:
The Steam Deck OLED is Valve's latest iteration of their handheld gaming device, unveiled as a mid-cycle refresh with significant enhancements over the original model. This device boasts an improved 7.4-inch OLED screen, the first HDR OLED screen on any gaming portable, offering native support for HDR, faster frame rates, and a peak brightness of 1,000 nits for HDR content and 600 nits for SDR. The screen's wider color gamut and faster display, with a 90 Hz refresh rate, provide a smoother, brighter gaming experience. The Steam Deck OLED is marginally lighter and cooler to the touch, thanks to enhanced thermals and a slightly larger fan, making it less top-heavy and more comfortable to hold during gaming sessions.

Battery life has been significantly extended, with tests showing the device lasting four hours and 23 minutes before dying, and a stress test involving playing Elden Ring with everything maxed out lasting two hours and 20 minutes. The improvements in battery life are estimated to be 30-50% better than the original Steam Deck, allowing for a more portable gaming experience. The device also includes a reworked power supply with a longer 2.5m cable, capable of charging the device from 20 to 80 percent in as little as 45 minutes.

Internally, the Steam Deck OLED features a die-shrunk version of the custom AMD APU found in the original Steam Deck, with the same CPU and GPU but more efficient. The thumbsticks are 1mm taller, and the touch pads' haptics are slightly sharper, enhancing the gaming experience. The device supports Wi-Fi 6E and Bluetooth 5.3, with a new antenna array for better simultaneous use of both, ensuring a stable and fast connection for online gaming and wireless accessories.

The Steam Deck OLED is available in three models with increased storage capacity: 1 TB, 512 GB, and 256 GB options. The 1 TB model is a special edition with a translucent shell, available for a limited time in the U.S. and Canada for $679. More than 10,000 titles on Steam fall under the playable or verified labels for the device, making it a versatile gaming platform. Despite its improvements, the Steam Deck OLED maintains the same large form factor as its predecessor and does not support variable refresh rates (VRR).

name: VALVE
description: Valve, a renowned company in the gaming industry, is celebrated for its expertise in developing both gaming hardware and software. Among its notable creations is the Steam Deck, a handheld gaming console that has captured the attention of gamers worldwide. In a recent announcement, Valve unveiled the Steam Deck OLED, a mid-cycle refresh of the original device, which boasts significant enhancements. The new model features an OLED screen, delivering superior display quality, and an improved battery that offers 30 to 50 percent longer life and faster charging, achieving a charge from 20 percent to 80 percent in just 45 minutes. Valve opted to integrate these upgrades into the existing chassis, rather than redesigning the device around smaller hardware, which also resulted in better heat management and Wi-Fi capabilities. Additionally, Valve has released a SteamOS update that enables players to utilize HDR and VRR on external displays, further enriching the gaming experience. The company's commitment to continuous improvement is evident, as it has been regularly updating the hardware of the original Steam Deck. Valve's strategic decisions, such as the arbitrary choice made two decades ago with Steam, have also become a point of interest in the Epic v. Google trial, highlighting the company's long-standing influence in the gaming and digital distribution sectors. With plans to develop successive generations of handhelds as long as the demand for handheld gaming remains robust, Valve is poised to remain a key player in the gaming hardware market.

name: OLED SCREEN
description: The OLED screen is a key upgrade in the Steam Deck OLED, featuring a wider P3 color gamut, pure blacks, and a peak brightness of 1,000 nits, compared to the original max of 400 nits. It supports higher-contrast colors and provides a more polished frame for retro aspect ratios. The screen does not support variable refresh rates (VRR) but now tops out at 90Hz, while the original could only hit 60Hz. [Engadget, 2023-11-09]

name: CUSTOM AMD APU
description: The Steam Deck OLED has a die-shrunk version of the custom AMD APU found in the original Steam Deck, with the same CPU and GPU but more efficient. This technology is used by Valve to improve the efficiency of the device without changing the performance targets. [Engadget, 2023-11-09]

name: BATTERY LIFE
description: The battery life of the Ray-Ban Meta smart glasses, an essential attribute for users, ranges from three to six hours based on how the glasses are used, as reported by The Verge on October 20, 2023. This variability in battery duration highlights the impact of different functionalities and usage patterns on the device's power consumption, allowing users to manage their expectations and usage accordingly.

name: WI-FI 6E
description: Wi-Fi 6E is a wireless technology supported by the Steam Deck OLED, enhancing its connectivity capabilities. This technology is designed to provide faster download speeds, which is particularly beneficial for users with compatible routers. By leveraging Wi-Fi 6E, the Steam Deck OLED ensures a more efficient and seamless wireless experience, optimizing performance for gaming and other entertainment activities.

name: BLUETOOTH 5.3
description: Bluetooth 5.3 is a wireless connectivity technology that is supported by the Steam Deck OLED, enhancing its functionality. This latest iteration of Bluetooth technology allows for better performance when using both Wi-Fi and Bluetooth simultaneously, providing an improved user experience in terms of connectivity and device management. The Steam Deck OLED, a high-end gaming console, benefits from Bluetooth 5.3 by offering seamless wireless connection options for accessories and peripherals, making it a versatile choice for gamers who value both performance and convenience. As of 2023, the integration of Bluetooth 5.3 into the Steam Deck OLED has been highlighted by Engadget on November 9th, showcasing the device's commitment to staying at the forefront of technological advancements in the gaming industry.

name: ENGADGET
description: Engadget is a seasoned media organization, established in 2004, that specializes in testing, reviewing, and reporting on consumer technology products. They offer comprehensive coverage and analysis of tech news, including updates on significant events such as Apple's Scary Fast event and the best deals during Amazon Prime Day and Black Friday. Engadget's content is enriched with affiliate links, which allow them to earn a commission from purchases made through those links, providing a revenue stream that supports their operations. Their evaluation process is based on stringent criteria and guidelines, ensuring that the reviews and guides they publish are insightful and reliable. Engadget has featured a variety of products in their best picks guides, including the Logitech G Pro X Superlight mouse, Samsung Pro Plus microSD card, Backbone One gamepad, Crucial MX500 internal drive, and the Steam Deck OLED, which they praised for its improved battery life, heat management, and Wi-Fi capabilities. They also published an article on the K.O. II, discussing its features and limitations, and provided a guide on the best Black Friday headphone deals, showcasing their expertise in headphones and wireless earbuds. Recently, Engadget tested nine of the best VPN services available and selected five top picks, further demonstrating their commitment to providing detailed and up-to-date information on technology products.

name: ANTHONY JOSHUA
description: Anthony Joshua, a global star and professional boxer from the United Kingdom, has faced significant mental challenges following title losses to Usyk and an upset loss to Andy Ruiz Jr. in 2019. Despite these setbacks, Joshua has demonstrated resilience, attending a darkness retreat to help improve his mental state. With a record of 27-3-0, he recently delivered a convincing victory against Otto Wallin, showcasing his jabbing skills and moving forward with confidence, proving that his best days may not be behind him. Anthony Joshua is scheduled to fight on the undercard of the Day of Reckoning event, where he is expected to work hard against his opponent in a match that could potentially result in another loss. His name has also been mentioned in relation to Deontay Wilder's potential fight, further highlighting his status in the boxing world.

name: DEONTAY WILDER
description: Deontay Wilder, a former heavyweight boxing champion, has undergone a significant transformation following his attendance at an Ayahuasca retreat in South America. This spiritual rebirth has led to a noticeable change in his demeanor, making him happier and more relaxed. Despite his recent losses in the trilogy against Tyson Fury, Wilder's career and personal growth continue to be topics of interest in the boxing world. His chances of facing another prominent boxer, Anthony Joshua, were unfortunately thwarted by Joseph Parker, adding another layer to his career narrative. [CBSSports.com, 2023-12-23; The Roar | Sports Writers Blog, 2023-12-23]

name: TYSON FURY
description: Tyson Fury, a professional heavyweight boxer, has made significant waves in the boxing world. Notably, he concluded his trilogy with Deontay Wilder on a high note, securing victories in the final two fights, contributing to his 2-0-1 record against Wilder. Demonstrating his expertise and sportsmanship, Fury has been offering guidance to fellow boxer Joseph Parker for an upcoming fight. Looking ahead, Tyson Fury is set to face Oleksandr Usyk in a highly anticipated bout on February 17 in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia. This event could potentially include Jai Opetaia's next fight on the undercard, adding to the excitement of the evening. As of December 23, 2023, these details have been confirmed by reputable sources such as CBSSports.com and The Roar | Sports Writers Blog, providing a comprehensive snapshot of Tyson Fury's recent and future engagements in the boxing arena.

name: ANDY RUIZ JR.
description: Andy Ruiz Jr. is a boxer who upset Anthony Joshua in 2019, leading to Joshua's mental struggles. [CBSSports.com, 2023-12-23]

name: USYK
description: USYK, a professional boxer, has made a significant mark in the boxing world by defeating Anthony Joshua in a pair of title fights, as reported by CBSSports.com on December 23, 2023. These victories not only showcased USYK's superior skills and strategic prowess in the ring but also highlighted the technical disadvantages faced by Anthony Joshua in their encounters. Through these two remarkable wins, USYK has solidified his position as a formidable force in the sport of boxing.

name: SAUDI ARABIA
description: Saudi Arabia, a country known for its strategic investments, has set its sights on the world of combat sports. As reported by CBSSports.com on December 23, 2023, Saudi Arabia has made a substantial financial commitment to the potential heavyweight boxing match between Anthony Joshua and Deontay Wilder. This investment is part of a broader initiative to position the country as a new global hub for big-time combat sports events. By channeling significant resources into the sector, Saudi Arabia aims to attract major international fights and events, solidifying its reputation as a key player in the entertainment and sports industry.

name: JOEY JOYCE
description: Joe Joyce is a boxer who defeated Joseph Parker in 2022, damaging Parker's reputation. [CBSSports.com, 2023-12-23]

name: ANDY LEE
description: Andy Lee is Joseph Parker's head trainer who has been working with Parker in the camp of Tyson Fury. [CBSSports.com, 2023-12-23]

name: JOSEPH PARKER
description: Joseph Parker, a professional Kiwi heavyweight boxer, has made significant waves in the boxing world with notable victories over Ruiz, Hughie Fury, and Derek Chisora. In a remarkable turn of events, Parker stunned the boxing community by defeating former champion Deontay Wilder, effectively derailing Wilder's plans for a highly anticipated match against Anthony Joshua. As of 2023, Parker is actively preparing for his next fight, and he has been receiving strategic advice from none other than Tyson Fury and Andy Lee, two esteemed figures in the sport. This preparation suggests that Parker is committed to continuing his successful career and further establishing himself as a formidable force in professional boxing.

name: DAY OF RECKONING
description: Day of Reckoning is a boxing event scheduled for December 23, 2023, at the Kingdom Arena in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia. It features fights between recognized names in the heavyweight division. [CBSSports.com, 2023-12-23]

name: DAZN PPV
description: DAZN PPV is a subscription-based pay-per-view platform that provides access to exclusive events, such as the Day of Reckoning. As of December 23, 2023, the service charges $39.99 for viewing access to such events, according to CBSSports.com. This platform enables subscribers to watch high-profile entertainment and sports events on a pay-per-view basis, making it an ideal choice for fans who wish to engage with specific, premium content without committing to a full subscription package.

name: DMITRY BIVOL
description: Dmitry Bivol is a professional boxer recognized as the 2022 fighter of the year, and is featured in Saturday's super card [CBSSports.com, 2023-12-23]

name: HELENIUS
description: Helenius is a professional boxer who lost to Anthony Joshua, with Joshua delivering a perfect knockout blow that showcased his power and natural finishing skills [CBSSports.com, 2023-12-23]

name: WALLIN
description: Wallin is a professional boxer who is expected to face a competitive fight against Deontay Wilder, with the possibility of winning only if he does so in a dominant fashion [CBSSports.com, 2023-12-23]

name: PARKER
description: Parker, a 31-year-old professional boxer, has recently made headlines in the boxing world. Despite being a former heavyweight champion who impressively dominated Deontay Wilder in a recent fight as reported by The Roar | Sports Writers Blog on 2023-12-23, CBSSports.com on the same day suggests that Parker might face a competitive challenge against Wilder. The analysis indicates that while Parker possesses significant skills and experience, he may lack the finishing power to match Wilder's aggressive style, adding an intriguing layer to their upcoming bout. This contrast in perspectives highlights the dynamic nature of professional boxing, where past victories and current capabilities are continuously scrutinized and debated.

name: HULU
description: Hulu, a comprehensive streaming service, offers a vast selection of content including horror films and popular shows such as The Bear and Only Murders in the Building. As of 2023, the platform has been making headlines for its special deals and subscription plans. In late September 2023, Polygon reported on Hulu's curated collection of horror films, making it a go-to destination for fans of the genre. Later, in November, The Verge and Engadget covered an enticing Black Friday deal for new and returning subscribers who hadn't paid for the service in at least a month. This deal provided an annual subscription to Hulu's ad-supported plan for $12, equating to $1 per month, which is an 85% discount off the standard monthly price. The offer was available until November 28th at 11:59 PM PT. Additionally, Hulu is known for streaming the film Sputnik. However, it's worth noting that some of the service's shows might be geoblocked in certain countries, affecting global accessibility.

name: MAX
description: MAX is a streaming platform that offers a diverse collection of content, including a notable selection of horror movies for its audience to enjoy. Among the titles available on MAX, "Malignant" stands out as a featured film, providing viewers with access to this particular horror genre piece. As of September 28, 2023, Polygon has reported on MAX's library, highlighting its commitment to catering to horror movie enthusiasts.

name: PARAMOUNT PLUS
description: Paramount Plus is a comprehensive streaming platform, offering a wide array of content to cater to diverse viewer preferences. Known for providing access to horror movies, the service also boasts a rich collection of popular TV shows such as The Good Fight and Star Trek: Strange New Worlds. Additionally, classic film enthusiasts can enjoy watching Sunset Boulevard on the platform. With its broad spectrum of programming, Paramount Plus aims to be a one-stop destination for entertainment, ensuring that there is something for everyone within its streaming library.

name: ENCOUNTERS OF THE SPOOKY KIND
description: Encounters of the Spooky Kind is a horror movie directed by Sammo Hung, featuring Sammo Hung, Chung Fat, and Dick Wei in the cast, and is available for streaming on the Criterion Channel [Polygon, 2023-09-28]

name: SAMMO HUNG
description: Sammo Hung is a director, choreographer, and actor who directed, co-wrote, choreographed the action, and starred in Encounters of the Spooky Kind, showcasing his skills as a martial artist and comedian [Polygon, 2023-09-28]

name: CRITERION CHANNEL

name: HEREDITARY
description: Hereditary is a horror movie that is elegantly creepy and becomes terrifying, offering a mishmash of family drama, supernatural elements, and resentments [Polygon, 2023-09-28]

name: THE HOST
description: The Host is a monster thriller directed by Bong Joon-ho, following a father's quest to rescue his daughter kidnapped by a mutated fish monster in the Han River, serving as commentary on U.S. intervention, ecological disasters, and more [Polygon, 2023-09-28]

name: BONG JOON-HO
description: Bong Joon-ho is the director of The Host, a follow-up to his successful serial killer drama Memories of Murder [Polygon, 2023-09-28]

name: HOUSE
description: House is a bizarre and visually inventive ghost story directed by Nobuhiko Obayashi, following a group of school girls on vacation at a haunted mansion in Japan [Polygon, 2023-09-28]

name: NOBUHIKO OBAYASHI
description: Nobuhiko Obayashi is the director of House, a unique and weirdly excellent horror movie [Polygon, 2023-09-28]

name: IN THE MOUTH OF MADNESS
description: In the Mouth of Madness is a horror movie directed by John Carpenter, where the plots of a horror novelist's books and monsters seem to invade the real world [Polygon, 2023-09-28]

name: JOHN CARPENTER
description: John Carpenter is the director of In the Mouth of Madness, a wild and unhinged horror film [Polygon, 2023-09-28]

name: THE BEST HORROR MOVIES YOU CAN WATCH RIGHT NOW
MALIGNANT
description: Malignant is a horror film directed by James Wan, featuring Annabelle Wallis, Maddie Hasson, and George Young. It is available to watch on Max. [Polygon, 2023-09-28]

name: JAMES WAN
description: James Wan is a film director known for his work on The Conjuring and Insidious franchises, as well as blockbuster films like Furious 7 and Aquaman. He directed Malignant, a high-emotion giallo horror film. [Polygon, 2023-09-28]

name: ANNABELLE WALLIS
description: Annabelle Wallis is an actor who plays the role of Madison in Malignant, a pregnant woman dealing with domestic abuse, a killer, and psychotic episodes. [Polygon, 2023-09-28]

name: MADDIE HASSON
description: Maddie Hasson is an actor who is part of the cast of Malignant. [Polygon, 2023-09-28]

name: THE MIST
description: The Mist is a horror film directed by Frank Darabont, starring Thomas Jane, Marcia Gay Harden, and Laurie Holden. It can be watched through digital rental or purchase. [Polygon, 2023-09-28]

name: FRANK DARABONT
description: Frank Darabont is a film director who directed The Mist, his third adaptation of a Stephen King story. [Polygon, 2023-09-28]

name: THOMAS JANE
description: Thomas Jane is an actor known for his role in The Expanse and stars in The Mist as a Hollywood poster artist living in Maine. [Polygon, 2023-09-28]

name: REC
description: [REC] is a found-footage horror movie that uses the format to enhance its creeping dread and tension, leading up to a terrifying finale. The movie is praised for its effective use of the genre to create a suspenseful atmosphere.[]

name: SPUTNIK
description: Sputnik is a 2020 Russian sci-fi horror film directed by Egor Abramenko. Set during the Cold War in 1983, it follows Tatyana, a young psychiatrist, who is recruited to treat Konstantin, a cosmonaut who survived a mysterious satellite crash. Tatyana discovers that Konstantin is hosting an alien organism, and she must decide between studying the creature and saving Konstantin. The film explores themes of duty, survival, and the consequences of one's actions.[]

name: EGOR ABRAMENKO
description: Egor Abramenko is the director of Sputnik, a 2020 Russian sci-fi horror film. His debut film is noted for its compelling use of the "trolley problem" thought experiment to dramatic emotional effect.[]

name: OKSANA AKINSHINA
description: Oksana Akinshina is an actress who plays Tatyana, the uncompromising young psychiatrist in Sputnik. She delivers a convincing and compelling performance, showcasing her character's struggle between duty and compassion.[]

name: FEDOR BONDARCHUK
description: Fedor Bondarchuk is an actor involved in the cast of Sputnik, although his specific role is not mentioned in the text.[]

name: PYOTR FYODOROV
description: Pyotr Fyodorov is an actor who portrays Konstantin, the wounded cosmonaut and lone survivor of a mysterious satellite crash in Sputnik. His performance is described as sympathetically complex and implicitly sinister at times.[]

name: TATYANA
description: Tatyana is a character in Sputnik, an uncompromising young psychiatrist who must confront the alien organism inside Konstantin and make hard decisions about her duty and the potential threat to humanity.[]

name: KONSTANTIN
description: Konstantin is a character in Sputnik, a cosmonaut and the lone survivor of a mysterious satellite crash. His body is now the host to an alien organism, and he is torn between his duty to his country and his emotional obligation to a loved one.[]

name: UNFRIENDED
description: Unfriended is a 2014 supernatural horror film viewed entirely from the perspective of a computer desktop, centering around a Skype call between high school students joined by an unknown presence known as “billie227.” The mysterious stranger reveals terrifying secrets and kills the friends one by one [Polygon, 2023-09-28]

name: US
description:
The United States (US), a country with significant global influence, has been actively engaged in various international and domestic affairs. In the realm of international relations, the US has been mentioned in discussions regarding the funding of tent camps for refugees in the Sinai Peninsula, demonstrating its involvement in humanitarian efforts. Additionally, the country has designated Hamas as a terrorist group, reflecting its stance on global security issues. The US shares a strategic partnership with Egypt, a relationship that has been reaffirmed by President Joe Biden, indicating the importance of bilateral cooperation in the region.

On the domestic front, the US is the setting for a legal case against Google, where it is required to prove that the tech giant broke the law to achieve its dominant market status. This highlights the ongoing scrutiny of large technology companies within the US legal system.

Furthermore, under President Biden's administration, the US approved $8 billion in military aid, as reported by H.S. in Globes English | Israel Business Arena on 2023-10-12. This aid is intended to help address the deficit caused by the war, showcasing the US's commitment to supporting allies and maintaining global stability.

In the entertainment sector, "Us" is a 2019 psychological slasher film directed by Jordan Peele, featuring a star-studded cast including Lupita Nyong'o, Winston Duke, and Elisabeth Moss. The movie, which follows the Wilson family's harrowing encounter with their doppelgängers called Tethered, has been praised for its mix of slasher thrills and intricate world-building, as noted by Polygon on 2023-09-28. Despite the various uses of "US" in different contexts, the entity in question consistently refers to the United States, highlighting its multifaceted role in both global politics and domestic legal and entertainment industries.

name: JORDAN PEELE
description: Jordan Peele is a director known for his horror films, including Us, which is considered a fantastic horror movie with a great cast and atmosphere [Polygon, 2023-09-28]

name: ELISABETH MOSS
description: Elisabeth Moss is an actor who appears in Us in a brief but loathsome role as one of the family’s friends, delivering an extraordinarily off-kilter performance that adds to the movie's unsettling vibe [Polygon, 2023-09-28]

name: SKYPE
description: Skype is a technology used in Unfriended as a central plot device, where a group of high school students are joined by an unknown presence during a call [Polygon, 2023-09-28]

name: THE BEST HORROR MOVIES
description: The best horror movies are a collection of films recommended for viewing, as suggested in an article by Polygon published on 2023-09-28

name: AG
description: AG, an insightful individual with a keen eye for horror cinema, has been highlighted in Polygon's coverage of the genre. On 2023-09-28, AG's thought-provoking quote about the reflections one encounters in the mirror was featured in an article discussing the nuances of horror movies. Continuing to share expertise, AG reviewed the film "Talk to Me" on 2023-10-07, commending its impeccable premise, the actor's brilliant performance, and the film's stylish, shocking horror elements. AG's contributions to Polygon's horror movie discourse showcase a deep understanding and appreciation for the genre, making their insights valuable to fellow horror enthusiasts.

name: LITHIUM-ION BATTERIES
description: Lithium-ion batteries are a technology that has grown due to the demand for rechargeable batteries in personal electronics and electric vehicles markets. They are relatively inexpensive and environmentally friendly compared to fossil fuels but have the risk of burning or explosion due to thermal runaway [Source: Advanced Science News, 2023-09-26]

name: RECHARGEABLE ZINC IODINE BATTERIES
description: Rechargeable zinc iodine batteries are a potential substitute for lithium-ion batteries, offering advantages in safety, cost, and environmental friendliness. However, they suffer from lower energy output, zinc dendrite growth, and anode corrosion, which can lead to reduced efficiency and short-circuiting [Source: Advanced Science News, 2023-09-26]

name: NANYANG TECHNOLOGICAL UNIVERSITY
description: Nanyang Technological University (NTU) is an educational institution where researchers, including Professor Hongjin Fan, are working on improving the stability and safety of rechargeable zinc ion batteries using hydrogel electrolytes [Source: Advanced Science News, 2023-09-26]

name: HONGJIN FAN
description: Hongjin Fan is a professor at the School of Physical and Mathematical Sciences at Nanyang Technological University. He and his co-authors have published a paper in Advanced Materials, focusing on the design of hydrogel electrolytes for rechargeable zinc ion batteries [Source: Advanced Science News, 2023-09-26]

name: HYDROGEL ELECTROLYTES
description: Hydrogel electrolytes are a three-dimensional network structure capable of storing large amounts of water, designed to address challenges in rechargeable zinc ion batteries by ensuring even accumulation of zinc on the anode side and mitigating the "shuttle effect" [Source: Advanced Science News, 2023-09-26]

name: ZINC IODINE BATTERIES
description: Zinc iodine batteries are a type of rechargeable battery technology that uses zinc and iodine as active materials. The technology is being modified with hydrogel to improve the even deposition of zinc on the anode side and accelerate the iodine conversion reaction on the cathode side, mitigating the "shuttle effect" and improving cycling stability and anode corrosion [Advanced Science News, 2023-09-26]

name: HYDROGEL
description: Hydrogel is a material used to modify zinc iodine batteries. It has different functional groups that make it zincophilic and iodophilic, which helps in the even deposition of zinc and the immobilization of polyiodides, respectively. The hydrogel electrolyte also accelerates redox reactions and limits the growth of dendrites due to its mechanical strength [Advanced Science News, 2023-09-26]

name: FAN
description: Fan is a researcher who explained the purpose and effects of hydrogel modification in zinc iodine batteries. He also acknowledged the challenges in bringing the battery to the mass market, including the need for further improvement in ion conductivity and stability of hydrogel electrolytes, compatibility with other battery components, and large-scale, cost-effective production methods [Advanced Science News, 2023-09-26]

name: COMMERCIAL LITHIUM-ION BATTERIES
description: Commercial lithium-ion batteries are a type of battery technology that is currently available in the market. They have higher mass and volume energy density compared to zinc iodine batteries [Advanced Science News, 2023-09-26]

name: THE WHITE COMPANY

Among its Christmas range, The White Company features exquisite decorations, captivating scents, and cozy homeware, ensuring that every space is perfectly ready for celebrations. Complementing these offerings, The White Company also provides nightwear and Christmas trees, making it a one-stop destination for all holiday needs.

name: GOLF BETTING
description: GOLF BETTING is a specialized domain within the broader landscape of sports betting, focusing on professional golf tournaments. This includes prestigious events such as those on the PGA Tour and the DP World Tour, as well as other notable competitions like The Match and the Ryder Cup. The betting options in GOLF BETTING are diverse and cater to various preferences and strategies. Common bets include predicting the outright winner, betting against the field, head-to-head matchups, each-way bets, and top 10 or top 20 finishes. Additionally, enthusiasts can place bets on the first-round leader, group matchups, the nationality of the winner, and engaging prop bets. In recent times, live golf betting has gained significant traction, enabling fans to wager on every shot and hole in real-time. The advent of sports betting apps and the integration of live streaming services have revolutionized the experience, making GOLF BETTING more accessible and thrilling for bettors. As of 2023-10-13, these trends and betting options are highlighted by Sporting News, reflecting the current state and excitement within the golf betting community.

name: DRAFTKINGS SPORTSBOOK
description:
DraftKings Sportsbook is a premier and well-known online sports betting platform in the United States, recognized for its intuitive sportsbook and betting app. It offers an extensive array of betting options across various sports markets, including Major League Baseball with game lines, player props, and futures bets, as well as NBA bets covering the MVP award and Rookie of the Year award. The platform is also popular for golf betting, providing odds and props for PGA Tour events and major championships, such as tournament winners, top 5, 10, and 20 finishes, and matchup betting, with the added feature of live betting on individual holes and shots during tournaments.

DraftKings Sportsbook is known for its ease of use and features such as live betting options and a diverse prop betting selection, making it one of the most prominent sports betting apps in the country. It has applied for a license to expand its operations into Vermont, further demonstrating its reach and ambition in the sports betting industry.

For new players, DraftKings Sportsbook provides a competitive and generous welcome offer. This multi-part welcome bonus includes a $50 Bonus Bet for depositing $5, $150 in Bonus Bets for making a $5 wager, and a 20% deposit match bonus worth up to $1,000 in Bonus Bets. Additionally, newcomers can receive a promo with a total promotional value of up to $1,200, enhancing the appeal for those looking to join the platform. The company's focus on providing a seamless and engaging betting experience, coupled with its attractive promotional offers, positions DraftKings Sportsbook as a leading choice for sports enthusiasts seeking to place bets on their favorite teams and players.

name: FANDUEL SPORTSBOOK
description: FanDuel Sportsbook is a widely recognized and popular online sports betting platform across the United States, known for its competitive odds and generous promotions. It is particularly favored within the NBA betting community for its expansive selection of player and game props, including NBA Rookie of the Year, MVP, and a same-game parlay feature that allows users to combine moneylines, totals, and props for a personalized betting experience. New players can claim a welcome offer, typically $150 in bonus bets, and existing customers enjoy attractive promotions and odds boosts. FanDuel Sportsbook is also a top destination for MLB enthusiasts, offering daily betting options with staple bets such as run lines and totals, as well as dozens of player props and futures bets. Additionally, it is a great app for golf betting, providing a wide range of markets and props for PGA Tour events, major championships, and international golf events like the DP World Tour and the Ryder Cup. Some of its golf odds and props include top-20 finishes, head-to-head matchups, and first-round leaders. The platform has applied for a license to launch in Vermont, demonstrating its commitment to expanding its reach. FanDuel Sportsbook is celebrated for its user-friendly interface and is considered one of the best sports betting apps in the industry, with a massive following. It offers an Early Sign Up Special for an extra $100 in Bonus Bets and a unique feature where new sign-ups can make an initial $5 wager and get back $200 in Bonus Bets. Despite listing Parker as a big underdog in his fight against Wilder, FanDuel Sportsbook continues to be a must-visit for finding the best prices on bets across various sports.

name: BETMGM SPORTSBOOK
description:
BetMGM Sportsbook, often hailed as the "King of Sportsbooks," is a prominent and reliable entity in the gambling industry, recognized for its competitive odds across all bet types, including futures bets and NBA Rookie of the Year award predictions. This sports betting platform extends its services to a wide array of premier sports, offering an extensive betting portfolio that particularly caters to MLB fans with traditional bet types, such as moneylines, run lines, and totals, alongside a rich selection of player and team prop bets and futures bets. Additionally, BetMGM Sportsbook is a go-to destination for golf enthusiasts, providing diverse markets and props for PGA Tour events and major championships, including live betting options akin to DraftKings and FanDuel.

New users are welcomed with a generous "First Bet Offer," which can amount to $1,500 in Bonus Bets if the initial wager is unsuccessful. The structure of the refund varies for bets over $50, with the amount split into five Bonus Bets. It's imperative to note that the Bonus Bet(s) must be utilized within seven days, and the winnings do not include the bet amount back. BetMGM Sportsbook ensures a smooth betting experience by offering a variety of deposit and withdrawal methods, 24/7 customer service, and an intuitive betting app that includes features like "edit my bet" and "easy parlay" options.

BetMGM Sportsbook is expanding its reach, having applied for a license to launch in Vermont, further solidifying its position as a leading sportsbook in numerous states where sports betting is legal. Its commitment to providing consistently competitive lines and odds, coupled with a plethora of sports betting promotions and odds boosts, makes it a valuable choice for bettors seeking better prices on their wagers.
