name: PARENTING
description: Parenting is an activity that traditionally involves caring for one's children, but in modern times, it has expanded to include the care of aging parents, often referred to as "parenting" one's parents. This phenomenon is particularly prevalent among the sandwich generation, who are simultaneously caring for their children and their elderly parents [The Guardian, 2023-10-10]

name: SANDWICH GENERATION
description: The sandwich generation refers to individuals who are simultaneously caring for their children and their aging parents, often experiencing the complexity of technology and its impact on both ends of the age spectrum [The Guardian, 2023-10-10]

name: DR EAMON LAIRD
description: Dr Eamon Laird is a researcher in health and aging at Limerick University. He supports the idea of encouraging older parents to engage with new challenges and technology, which can help build and maintain new brain connections and improve overall health [The Guardian, 2023-10-10]

name: UNIVERSITY OF TEXAS
description: The University of Texas conducted a study involving over 200 elderly adults, finding that those who engaged with technology had better cognition and memory than those who did not. This study suggests that digital engagement can protect the brain [The Guardian, 2023-10-10]

name: AMMY
description: Ammy is a person whose mother recently joined Instagram, which helped her expand her grey matter and stay in touch with her grandchildren [The Guardian, 2023-10-10]

name: EAMON LAIRD
description: Dr Eamon Laird is a health and ageing researcher who found that a daily walk could cut the risk of depression in older adults by up to 43% [The Guardian, 2023-10-10]

name: INSTAGRAM
description: Instagram, a product of Meta and designated as a Very Large Online Platform (VLOP) under the EU's Digital Services Act (DSA), is a social media platform that significantly occupies young people's screen time, with some users spending up to three hours daily on the app. It has been leveraged by Believe to drive global engagement around artists and their music, such as Iñigo and the song Si No Estás. Artists also have the opportunity to create Reels as part of the entry process for AfroFuture's "Rising Star Challenge." However, Instagram faces criticism for tracking and profiling users for ad targeting without their consent, as reported by TechCrunch in 2023. Internal studies and communications reveal the presence of under-13 users who are subjected to bullying on the platform. Additionally, Instagram has been accused of censorship and bias, particularly in relation to content about Palestine, even when it does not support Hamas. Users have reported restrictions on their accounts for 24 hours due to reports on their Palestine travel videos, and more recently, accusations of "shadowbanning" Stories about Palestine have surfaced. In the context of the Israel-Hamas war, certain hashtags were blocked, and livestreaming checks were prioritized. Despite these issues, Instagram continues to be a place where people like Ammy's 84-year-old mother can stay connected with their loved ones, and where celebrities like Sarah Michelle Gellar share personal experiences, such as her son's Roblox account being hacked. The platform's monetization tactics for livestreaming content, however, are considered less effective than those of Twitch.

name: SUSAN SAUNDERS
description: Susan Saunders is a health coach who advises on caring for parents with dementia and recommends investigating all available research trials [The Guardian, 2023-10-10]

name: DEMENTIA RESEARCH
description: Dementia Research is a nationwide register that matches volunteers to research programmes, recommended by Susan Saunders for those with parents in the early stages of dementia [The Guardian, 2023-10-10]

name: VITAMIN D AND B12 SUPPLEMENTS
description: Vitamin D and B12 supplements are recommended by Dr Eamon Laird to moderate the chance of depression in older people [The Guardian, 2023-10-10]

name: MULTIVITAMIN FOR OLDER PEOPLE
description: An inexpensive multivitamin formulated specifically for older people improved cognition, memory, and focus, according to a recent study from Columbia University [The Guardian, 2023-10-10]

name: NATIONAL FOOTBALL LEAGUE (NFL)
description: The National Football League (NFL) is a professional American football league that covered Taylor Swift's attendance at the Kansas City Chiefs game against the New York Jets on 1 October 2023. The league's focus on Swift contributed to high ratings for the game [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-04]

name: JASON KELCE
description: Jason Kelce, a star player for the Philadelphia Eagles and brother of Travis Kelce, is deeply involved in the world of sports and entertainment. He co-hosts the podcast "New Heights" with his sibling Travis, where they engage in candid discussions about various topics. In February 2023, Jason humorously addressed their mother's apparent preference for Travis on the podcast, providing a glimpse into their familial dynamics [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-30]. Later, the duo discussed the NFL's coverage of Taylor Swift's performance during a game, intertwining their love for football with pop culture [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-04]. Jason was also part of a live television segment that dissected rumors surrounding Travis and Taylor Swift's potential relationship, showcasing his role in the public discourse around his brother's personal life [CBSSports.com, 2023-10-12]. Additionally, the podcast featured a segment where Travis talked about his efforts to delete old tweets, with Jason's input adding to the conversation [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-11-25]. Jason shares three children with his wife Kylie Kelce, balancing his professional life with his family responsibilities. Through "New Heights," Jason and Travis offer their audience a unique blend of sports insights, personal anecdotes, and entertainment news, making them a dynamic duo in the podcasting world.

name: NEW HEIGHTS WITH JASON AND TRAVIS KELCE
description: New Heights with Jason and Travis Kelce is a podcast where the two brothers, both professional football players, discuss various topics including the NFL's coverage of Taylor Swift during a recent game [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-04]

name: NASCAR
description: NASCAR, the National Association for Stock Car Auto Racing, is a prominent motorsport organization in the United States that sanctions a variety of racing series, such as the Cup Series and the Truck Series. Kyle Larson, a notable driver in NASCAR, has expressed hope that the High Limits Racing Sprint Car Series will gain significant national popularity. Larson's optimism comes amidst a period of change for NASCAR, as the organization recently secured a $7.7 billion media rights deal with Fox Sports, NBC, Amazon, and Warner Bros. Discovery. This deal, representing a 40% increase over their current agreement, was made in response to declining cable viewership and to explore streaming options, addressing the challenges of reduced cable subscribers and the need for additional funding for racing teams. The deal's potential to improve accessibility for fans, despite concerns about potential backlash, is seen as a positive step by Larson. Dale Earnhardt Jr, a former NASCAR racer, and Ryan Blaney, the recent Cup Series champion, are among the notable figures in the NASCAR community. Additionally, Ben Rhodes celebrated his second championship win in the Truck Series. NASCAR's influence extends beyond the racetrack, impacting car-buying decisions, particularly for Ford F-150 trucks and Mustangs, as reported by Essentially Sports on 2023-11-06.

name: FOX SPORTS
description: Fox Sports is a media company that is part of NASCAR's new media rights deal. [Essentially Sports, 2023-12-01]

name: NBC
description: NBC, a prominent U.S. broadcast network, has been the carrier of "Sunday Night Football" since 2006 and is committed to airing the NFL segment through at least 2033, as reported by Sporting News on 2023-11-05. The network broadcast the Kansas City Chiefs vs. Green Bay Packers game on Sunday, December 4, 2023, as confirmed by @SNFonNBC on 2023-12-04 and Sporting News on 2023-12-03. Additionally, NBC aired the Bills vs. Bengals game and is set to broadcast the Vikings vs. Broncos game nationally, with the latter also being available for streaming on Fubo and DAZN, as per Sporting News on 2023-11-19. Beyond NFL coverage, NBC is part of NASCAR's new media rights deal, as mentioned by Essentially Sports on 2023-12-01, further solidifying its role as a key player in sports broadcasting. Viewers can access NBC's programming through various platforms, including Fubo, which carries the network and contributes to the extensive football coverage available to audiences.

name: WARNER BROS. DISCOVERY
description: Warner Bros. Discovery, a prominent media company, has strategically positioned itself within NASCAR's media landscape through a significant rights deal. As part of this agreement, the company leverages its streaming service, MAX, and its cable channel, TNT, to simulcast NASCAR races, ensuring a wide reach and accessibility for racing enthusiasts. This dual-platform approach highlights Warner Bros. Discovery's commitment to delivering high-quality content across various media formats, solidifying its role as a key player in the broadcasting of NASCAR events.

name: ADAM STERN
description: Adam Stern, a seasoned journalist with Sports Business Journal, has been actively analyzing and discussing the nuances of NASCAR's recent media rights deal. On the Dirty Mo Live podcast, Stern shared comprehensive insights, highlighting both the implications and potential drawbacks of this deal. He emphasized concerns over how the deal might affect ratings and the accessibility of NASCAR for its fanbase, suggesting that these aspects need careful consideration to maintain the sport's popularity and engagement. Through his expertise, Stern provides a balanced perspective on the deal's impact, offering valuable commentary for stakeholders and fans alike.

name: NEXT GEN CARS
description: Next Gen cars are a type of vehicle introduced by NASCAR, which have led to increased costs for Cup Series teams and other competitions, contributing to the financial struggles of the teams. [Essentially Sports, 2023-12-01]

name: CUP SERIES TEAMS
description: Cup Series teams are part of NASCAR's top-level competition and have been experiencing financial difficulties, especially since the introduction of the Next Gen cars. They have been pressuring NASCAR to secure more funding. [Essentially Sports, 2023-12-01]

name: MULTI-BILLION DOLLAR MEDIA RIGHTS DEAL
description: NASCAR has signed a multi-billion dollar media rights deal, which is expected to bring more money to the table and potentially improve the league's financial stability [Essentially Sports, 2023-12-01]

name: KYLE LARSON
description: Kyle Larson, the 2021 Cup Series champion, is a professional stock car racing driver deeply rooted in the NASCAR community. Currently in the prime of his career, Larson not only competes in NASCAR but also owns the High Limits Racing Sprint Car Series, demonstrating his commitment to the racing business. The series has been successful and profitable for drivers and teams, aiming to increase purses for weekend shows and potentially elevate national interest in sprint car racing. Larson's involvement in sprint car racing extends beyond ownership, as he actively participates in events like the Lernerville race, where he led for a significant portion before experiencing a loss of control, reminiscent of an incident in Texas. Despite not securing a win in every race, Larson's contributions to the sport are substantial. He is optimistic about NASCAR's future, particularly in light of the multi-billion dollar media rights deal, viewing it as a positive move for the industry. Larson's dedication to both NASCAR and sprint car racing showcases his passion for the sport and his desire to see it thrive at all levels.

name: LIZZIE MCGUIRE
description: Lizzie McGuire is a TV show that features Isabella the pop star, a character who embodies the dream-like premise that many shows fail to execute effectively

name: HARPER’S ISLAND
description: Harper’s Island is a 2009 TV show set on a small Pacific Northwest island with a deadly legacy, where the main character Abby returns for her best friend Henry’s wedding, only to find the island’s serial killing history resurfacing

name: ABBY
description: Abby is the main character in Harper’s Island who lost her mom in a serial killing almost a decade ago and returns to the island for her best friend Henry’s wedding

name: HENRY
description: Henry is Abby’s best friend in Harper’s Island who is getting married, leading to Abby’s return to the island

name: ELAINE CASSIDY
description: Elaine Cassidy is an actress who plays the role of Abby in Harper’s Island

name: CHRISTOPHER GORHAM
description: Christopher Gorham is an actor who plays the role of Henry in Harper’s Island

name: ZOSHA MILLMAN
description: Zosha Millman is a writer who praises Harper’s Island for its ability to sustain a levelheaded approach to an absurd serial killing scenario, making it a fun and twisty slasher TV show

name: AMERICAN HORROR STORY: NYC
description: American Horror Story: NYC is a season of the American Horror Story series that opens with a serial killer on the prowl and explores the horror of the queer community’s powerlessness in the face of the AIDS crisis

name: RYAN MURPHY
description: Ryan Murphy is the creator of American Horror Story who effectively builds an overwhelming, inescapable sense of dread in the NYC season

name: JEFFREY DAHMER
description: Jeffrey Dahmer is a real-life serial killer whose uncanny resemblance is portrayed by a character in American Horror Story: NYC

name: NICOLAS WINDING REFN
description: Nicolas Winding Refn is the director of the 2016 horror movie The Neon Demon, known for his distinct visual style and nightmarish portrayal of the modeling industry in Los Angeles [Polygon, 2023-10-10]

name: THE NEON DEMON
description: The Neon Demon is a 2016 horror movie directed by Nicolas Winding Refn, featuring Elle Fanning as Jesse, a young model in Los Angeles who becomes the center of a grim and dangerous world [Polygon, 2023-10-10]

name: ELLE FANNING
description: Elle Fanning stars as Jesse in The Neon Demon, a young model navigating the treacherous landscape of the modeling industry in Los Angeles [Polygon, 2023-10-10]

name: JENA MALONE
description: Jena Malone plays Ruby, a makeup artist who takes Jesse under her wing in the movie The Neon Demon [Polygon, 2023-10-10]

name: PROJECT WOLF HUNTING
description: "Project Wolf Hunting is a Korean monster movie, released in 2023, that masterfully blends the thrilling elements of Con Air, the intense action of Predator, and the eerie atmosphere of The Last Voyage of the Demeter. The film takes place on a cargo ship, where a monstrous creature and a group of dangerous criminals are the central antagonists. Known for its graphic and gory violence, Project Wolf Hunting has been recognized as one of the goriest movies in recent times, with the director proudly disclosing the use of 2.5 tons of fake blood during the filming process. This excessive use of fake blood contributes to the movie's aim of providing a bloody good time for its audience. Moreover, the film boasts an exceptional sound design that elevates the monster's presence, making its movements sound metallic and otherworldly, thus enhancing the creature's portrayal as something beyond human comprehension."

name: KURONEKO
description: Kuroneko is a 1968 supernatural horror film directed by Kaneto Shindo, set in the Sengoku period of Japanese history. The film centers on the story of two women, a mother and her daughter-in-law, who are raped and murdered by samurai. Their spirits forge a pact with the demons of the underworld, resurrecting them to seek vengeance on any samurai who cross their paths. The death toll rises, and a young samurai is enlisted to fend off the spirits, unaware of their origins or their tragic connection to his past.[]

name: ONIBABA
description: Onibaba is a 1964 film directed by Kaneto Shindo, which was featured in a 2021 Halloween countdown.[]

name: KIYOMI KURODA
description: Kiyomi Kuroda is the cinematographer for Kuroneko, known for employing minimalism and intense contrast of light and shadow to create sequences that feel otherworldly.[]

name: A WOUNDED FAWN
description: A Wounded Fawn is a 2022 horror movie that takes inspiration from Greek mythology. The film follows a museum curator who goes on a date with a serial killer and discovers a statue, The Wrath of Erinyes, in his home that shouldn't be there. The movie is shot on 35mm and is visually stunning, even before the action starts.[]

name: TRAVIS STEVENS
description: Travis Stevens is the director of A Wounded Fawn, known for his work on Jakob's Wife. He melds Greek mythic imagery with an unconventional serial killer narrative in A Wounded Fawn.[]

name: KINDLE SCRIBE
description: The Kindle Scribe, introduced by Amazon, stands out as the company's largest e-reader to date, boasting a 10.2-inch display with a high resolution of 300 dpi and a long-lasting battery. This device is unique among Kindle models for its innovative note-taking capabilities, which are facilitated by the use of a stylus, allowing users to write on the screen as they would on a regular notebook. Despite these features, initial testing revealed that the note-taking functionalities were somewhat lacking, a shortcoming that Amazon is addressing through ongoing software improvements delivered via free over-the-air (OTA) updates. The Kindle Scribe has received an 8/10 rating from WIRED, which recommends it for its size and note-taking abilities. However, the review also points out a significant limitation: users are unable to write in the margins of books, a feature that is notably absent, especially considering the device's premium price point. These insights, gathered from Amelia Holowaty Krales at The Verge (2023-10-16) and WIRED (2023-10-10), provide a comprehensive overview of the Kindle Scribe's features, performance, and areas for improvement.

name: PREMIUM PEN
description: The Premium Pen is an accessory for the Kindle Scribe that includes a shortcut button and a built-in eraser. It is available in a bundle with the 16GB Kindle Scribe, a folio cover, and a power adapter at a discounted price. [Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge, 2023-10-16]

name: FOLIO COVER
description: The folio cover is an accessory for the Kindle Scribe that is included in the Essentials Bundle. It is available in three fabric options. [Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge, 2023-10-16]

name: BASIC PEN STYLUS
description: The Basic Pen stylus is included in Amazon's base Essentials Bundle for the Kindle Scribe. [Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge, 2023-10-16]

name: OTA SOFTWARE UPDATES
description: Amazon is using free OTA software updates to improve the note-taking capabilities of the Kindle Scribe. [Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge, 2023-10-16]

name: CHERRY PARK
description: Cherry Park is the director of product marketing at Discord, who discussed the company's plans for custom experiences and app portability with Engadget. [Engadget, 2023-10-19]

name: NITRO SUBSCRIBERS
description: Nitro subscribers are a group of Discord users who will have the opportunity to test new features before they become available to the public. [Engadget, 2023-10-19]

name: APP PORTABILITY
description: App portability is a technology that Discord is considering to improve the user experience by allowing custom experiences to be accessible across different devices. [Engadget, 2023-10-19]

name: TEEN SAFETY
description: Teen safety is a concept that Discord is addressing by implementing content filters and automated warnings to protect its younger users. [Engadget, 2023-10-19]

name: HYDROGELS
description: Hydrogels are a technology that can be mixed into soil with seeds to help plants retain water. They can also be used in a hydrogel-based device to capture water vapor from the air and produce drinking water. [Science News For Students, 2023-11-03]

name: SMARTFARM
description: SmartFarm is a device that collects water from the air, allowing plants to grow without being watered. It could be used to grow crops in dry places. [Science News For Students, 2023-11-03]

name: MIT TEAM
description: The MIT team is designing a hydrogel-based device that will produce drinking water by capturing water vapor from the air and releasing it as moisture when heated by the sun. The device also contains a material that can be cooled without using electricity. [Science News For Students, 2023-11-03]

name: DÍAZ-MARÍN
description: Díaz-Marín is a person who explains how the hydrogel-based device designed by the MIT team works and highlights the potential of hydrogels to provide new sources of drinking water in dry places. [Science News For Students, 2023-11-03]

name: HURLER
description: The hurler is a person who throws the ball in the game, mentioned in the context of a play where the ball is thrown to Reed for a 44-yard gain [Sporting News, 2023-09-28]

name: MICHIGAN STATE
description: Michigan State is a university that has hired Jonathan Smith as its next football coach. The school made the announcement on Saturday, 2023-11-25, as reported by CBSSports.com

name: JONATHAN SMITH
description: Jonathan Smith, 44, is the new football coach at Michigan State. He spent the past six seasons as the coach at Oregon State, guiding the Beavers to 18 wins over the past two seasons, including a 10-3 mark and No. 17 finish in the AP Top 25 during the 2022 campaign, which earned him Pac-12 Coach of the Year honors. Smith was among the initial pool of candidates linked to the Michigan State opening after the Spartans fired fourth-year coach Mel Tucker with cause midseason amid sexual harassment allegations. Smith exits Oregon State with a 34-35 overall mark as coach, including a 1-1 record in bowl games, as he now joins the Big Ten coaching ranks. Smith, a former quarterback for the Beavers from 1998-2001, guided Oregon State to seven victories in 2021 after the program went 9-22 during his first three years. The 2022 season marked the Beavers' first 10-win season since 2006 and highest AP Top 25 finish. CBSSports.com, 2023-11-25

name: OREGON STATE
description: Oregon State is a university where Jonathan Smith spent the past six seasons as the football coach. He guided the Beavers to 18 wins over the past two seasons, including a 10-3 mark and No. 17 finish in the AP Top 25 during the 2022 campaign, which earned him Pac-12 Coach of the Year honors. CBSSports.com, 2023-11-25

name: MEL TUCKER
description: Mel Tucker is the former football coach at Michigan State who was fired midseason amid sexual harassment allegations. CBSSports.com, 2023-11-25

name: ALAN HALLER
description: Alan Haller is the athletic director at Michigan State who announced the hire of Jonathan Smith as the next football coach. CBSSports.com, 2023-11-25

name: THE BEARS
description: The Bears are a sports team that nearly won the game against Cleveland with a Hail Mary pass, a play that requires a miracle to succeed, on December 17, 2023 [Sporting News, 2023-12-17]

name: CLEVELAND
description: Cleveland is a city with a sports team that won an improbable game against Chicago with a 20-17 victory on December 17, 2023 [Sporting News, 2023-12-17]

name: DARNELL MOONEY
description: Darnell Mooney is a sports player for the Bears who nearly caught the Hail Mary pass that would have won the game against Cleveland on December 17, 2023 [Sporting News, 2023-12-17]

name: D'ANTHONY BELL
description: D'Anthony Bell is a sports player for Cleveland who caught the ball after it deflected off Darnell Mooney's hands, sealing the Browns' 20-17 win on December 17, 2023 [Sporting News, 2023-12-17]

name: DAVID NJOKU
description: David Njoku, a talented tight end for the Cleveland Browns, made a significant impact during the 2023 NFL season. On November 30, 2023, he scored a crucial touchdown against the Seattle Seahawks in Week 8, showcasing his skills and contributing to his team's success. Later in the season, on December 17, 2023, Njoku experienced a mix of shock and relief when a Hail Mary pass, which could have potentially secured a win for the Chicago Bears against his team, failed to do so. This event was widely reported by Sporting News, highlighting the high-stakes nature of the game and Njoku's emotional response to the outcome. Throughout the season, Njoku proved to be a key player for the Cleveland Browns, demonstrating his prowess on the field and his ability to handle pressure situations.

name: JOE FLACCO
description: Joe Flacco, a veteran sports player, serves as the quarterback for the Cleveland Browns. On December 17, 2023, Flacco demonstrated his strategic prowess by driving the Browns to the go-ahead score before the Hail Mary play, maintaining a cautious approach until the game's conclusion, as reported by Sporting News. Earlier in the month, on December 1st, 2023, CBSSports.com announced Flacco's appointment as the starter for the Browns' Week 13 game against the Rams, stepping in due to Dorian Thompson-Robinson's absence caused by a concussion. Flacco's playing style is characterized by his inclination to attempt deep passes and his focus on a primary receiver, a strategy that has become a notable aspect of his performance since joining the Browns, as observed on November 30th, 2023, by CBSSports.com.

name: MICHELIN UPTIS
description: Michelin Uptis is a non-pneumatic tire technology that uses modern composites instead of air pressure, providing a mix of stiffness and flex with significantly more durability. Michelin claims it could reduce tire replacements by 20 percent [The Verge, 2023-11-17]

name: JASON ROANHOUSE
description: Jason Roanhouse is the VP of North American Bandag operations at Bridgestone Mobility Solutions, a company that has saved 300 million tires from being thrown out through retreading, equivalent to roughly 4 billion gallons of oil [The Verge, 2023-11-17]

name: BRIDGESTONE MOBILITY SOLUTIONS
description: Bridgestone Mobility Solutions is a company that offers retreading services for tires, saving millions of tires from disposal and reducing the environmental impact [The Verge, 2023-11-17]

name: RECYCLING
description: Recycling is a process that can be applied to tires, but reuse through retreading is considered a better environmental practice [The Verge, 2023-11-17]

name: TIRE WEAR
description: Tire wear is a natural process that occurs over time and use, leading to the need for tire replacement. Modern tires have longer wear life, with 80,000-mile wear warranties becoming relatively common [The Verge, 2023-11-17]

name: TIRE POLLUTION
description: Tire pollution is an environmental issue caused by the disposal of worn-out tires, with 250 million tires scrapped every year in North America [The Verge, 2023-11-17]

name: GOODYEAR RECHARGE
description: Goodyear ReCharge is a concept tire with a biodegradable tread that can be recharged by inserting refillable capsules with seasonal compounds. It is a purely conceptual design that might never be produced [The Verge, 2023-11-17]

name: GOODYEAR
description: Goodyear is a company that produces tires and has introduced conceptual designs for tires with refillable capsules containing seasonal compounds, which may never be produced as such, but indicate ongoing research into future tire technology [The Verge, 2023-11-17]

name: HELSEL
description: Helsel is an individual associated with Goodyear who confesses that the company's conceptual tire designs are purely conceptual and might never be produced, but highlights the non-pneumatic nature and advanced sensors as indicative of ongoing research into future tires [The Verge, 2023-11-17]

name: BRIDGESTONE
description: Bridgestone is a company that produces tires and has introduced a concept called a "Wireless In-Wheel Tire" at the Japan Mobility Show, which turns every tire into an inductive charging pad for electric vehicles (EVs) [The Verge, 2023-11-17]

name: JAPAN MOBILITY SHOW
description: The Japan Mobility Show is an event where Bridgestone showcased its "Wireless In-Wheel Tire" concept, which is designed to increase the viability of electric vehicles by enabling wireless charging through the tires [The Verge, 2023-11-17]

name: WIRELESS IN-WHEEL TIRE
description: The Wireless In-Wheel Tire is a concept technology introduced by Bridgestone that turns every tire into an inductive charging pad for electric vehicles, addressing the issue of maintaining strong charging rates while the car is in motion [The Verge, 2023-11-17]

name: BEEPER MINI
description: Beeper Mini, a messaging app, serves as a bridge for Android users to send and receive iMessage texts, effectively overcoming the green bubble limitation. This product, which also facilitates iMessage access on a Mac, employs reverse-engineering to achieve interoperability with Apple's services. Despite facing challenges, including Apple's efforts to shut it down as noted in a TechCrunch article on 2023-12-11, Beeper Mini has managed to bounce back from issues with messages not being sent or received after an app update. A known bug, the "2FA submission error," was resolved by an uninstall/reinstall procedure. Currently, the app is free due to recent chaotic events and includes end-to-end encryption, enhancing user privacy. However, phone number registration is not yet functional, necessitating users to sign in with an Apple ID. This has led to an Apple prompt warning users that their ID is being used to sign in with a device near Los Angeles, CA, a glitch that is being addressed. Beeper Mini is committed to building trust by undergoing a third-party audit and sharing its codebase with a mutually agreed upon security research firm. Additionally, the company has published open-source code for over 50 projects on GitHub. The updated version of Beeper Mini, featuring new capabilities such as chats opening at the last unread message and an enhanced video player, is available for sideloading on beeper.com/update, although this method is considered riskier than downloading from the Play Store. The app update is now live on Google Play, offering users a safer alternative for installation.

name: MIGICOVSKY
description: Migicovsky is the spokesperson for Beeper who told TechCrunch that he can’t share anything on the topic of Beeper Mini’s security beyond what’s already in the blog post. He also mentioned that the company wants Apple to agree on the third-party security research firm for an audit.

name: 2FA SUBMISSION ERROR
description: The "2FA submission error" is an error message that appeared after updating the Beeper Mini app. This issue was fixed by uninstalling and reinstalling the app, as reported in the TechCrunch article published on 2023-12-11

name: DEVICE ADDED TO YOUR ACCOUNT
description: A message stating "Device Added to Your Account. A Mac now has access to iMessage" appeared on our iPhone after setting up the new Beeper Mini, offering a hint as to Beeper's fix for enabling iMessage access on a Mac, as reported in the TechCrunch article published on 2023-12-11

name: XBOX
description:
Xbox, a renowned brand of gaming consoles and controllers developed by Microsoft, has established itself as a significant player in the gaming industry. The Xbox Series S, one of its models, occasionally sells at a price point lower than that of the Scuf Instinct Pro, making it an attractive choice for budget-conscious gamers. The standard Xbox controller is widely regarded as the optimal choice for most Xbox gamers, embodying the essence of four generations of first-party controllers. It is celebrated for its affordability, wireless capabilities, and flexibility in battery options, with the added convenience of being able to function as a wired accessory via a USB-C cable. The controller's hardware, featuring tight sticks, buttons, triggers, and a sunken dish-shaped D-pad, is highly praised for its precision and responsiveness. Gamers can choose from a variety of colors or even customize their controllers through Microsoft's Xbox Design Lab, with prices ranging from $69.99 to $99.94.

Beyond hardware, Xbox offers a gaming platform that includes subscription services, granting gamers access to free digital titles, online multiplayer, and cloud-based saves, enhancing the gaming experience and providing value beyond the initial console purchase. Microsoft has secured exclusive rights to stream Activision Blizzard games for 15 years, further enriching the platform's content offerings. Initially, Xbox was more walled garden-like, akin to PlayStation, but it has evolved to become more open to social cross-platform features, fostering a more inclusive and interconnected gaming community.

name: POWERA ENHANCED WIRED CONTROLLER
description: PowerA Enhanced Wired Controller is a budget-minded wired controller for Xbox and PC, connecting via Micro USB and featuring two customizable buttons on its rear. It is available in many different colors and licensed designs, with a full retail price of $37.99, but some color schemes can be as low as around $25. [The Verge, 2023-11-21]

name: POWERA FUSION PRO 3
description: The PowerA Fusion Pro 3 is a wired controller that serves as an affordable alternative to premium controllers like the Xbox Elite Series 2, featuring four rear buttons, trigger lockouts, rubberized grips, swappable sticks, friction rings, and a compact zip-up case. It is significantly lighter than its predecessor and costs $79.99 [The Verge, 2023-11-21]

name: XBOX ELITE SERIES 2
description: The Xbox Elite Series 2, a pro-grade controller from Microsoft, stands out in the gaming community for its premium design and deep customization options. Priced at $179.99, occasionally dropping to $140, it is more than twice as expensive as a regular Xbox controller, reflecting its high-end status. The controller is made from premium materials, featuring a built-in rechargeable battery, a metal D-pad, and four removable paddles on the rear. It offers hair-trigger locks and rear paddle buttons, which can provide a competitive edge in gaming, although these features may require adjustment and might not suit all players. The Elite Series 2 allows users to tailor its layout to suit their play style with swappable D-pads and analog sticks. Despite its exceptional build quality and extra buttons, the controller has faced criticism for lackluster quality control, leading Microsoft to extend the warranty from 90 days to a year in late 2020. This extension addresses the issue of users experiencing multiple replacements under warranty, demonstrating Microsoft's commitment to customer satisfaction. The Xbox Elite Series 2 is often mentioned in comparison with other high-end controllers, such as the DualSense Edge, highlighting its position in the market as a top-tier gaming accessory.

name: HAIR-TRIGGER LOCKS
description: Hair-trigger locks are a feature of the Xbox Elite Series 2 controller that allows for faster shots in shooter games by reducing the trigger pull distance. [The Verge, 2023-11-21]

name: REAR PADDLE BUTTONS
description: Rear paddle buttons on the Xbox Elite Series 2 controller allow for additional control options without taking your thumb off the right stick for aiming. [The Verge, 2023-11-21]

name: ELITE SERIES 2 CORE
description: The Elite Series 2 Core is a stripped-down version of the Xbox Elite Series 2 controller, available in white-and-black, red-and-black, or blue-and-black finishes. It does not include rear paddles, accessory charging case, or extra stick toppers and D-pad. [The Verge, 2023-11-21]

name: ACCESSORIES PACK
description: The $59.99 accessories pack for the Xbox Elite Series 2 Core includes rear paddles, accessory charging case, and extra stick toppers and D-pad, turning it into a standard Elite Series 2. [The Verge, 2023-11-21]

name: ELITE SERIES 2
description: The Elite Series 2 is a controller for Xbox that has a warranty ranging from 90 days to a year, introduced in late 2020 to address concerns. It offers a hair trigger feature that can make gameplay feel worth it when used effectively[]

name: SCUF INSTINCT PRO
description: The Scuf Instinct Pro is a premium, customizable wireless Xbox controller with a starting price of $199.99, making it the most expensive option. It features a magnetic faceplate, textured rubber grips, four rear rocker buttons, and hair triggers, which are highly responsive and satisfying to use[]

name: SCUF
description: Scuf is a company that produces customizable gaming controllers with colorful accents and magnetically swappable faceplates, as mentioned in a review by The Verge on 2023-11-21

name: NACON REVOLUTION X
description: The Nacon Revolution X is a customizable gaming controller with deep customization options, including mappable rear buttons, software customization, and adjustable analog sticks. It is wired and connects via USB-C. The controller is described by The Verge on 2023-11-21 as having premium features and being worthy of an award for terrible naming

name: DOLBY ATMOS FOR HEADPHONES APP
description: Dolby Atmos for Headphones app is software that comes with a license for the Nacon Revolution X controller, allowing for audio customization. The Verge mentioned this in their review on 2023-11-21

name: RECON CONTROLLER
description: The Recon controller is a wired gaming controller that lacks fancy features like hair triggers and swappable thumbsticks. It has a plastic build that feels cheap, but the rubbery grips provide a comfortable feel. The sticks, triggers, and additional rear buttons are tight and snappy. It has a learning curve but is fairly priced and includes extra buttons and helpful audio functions, making it a great choice for shooter games. The D-pad is similar to the standard Xbox Wireless Controller but is inferior in comparison. [Source: The Verge, 2023-11-21]

name: XBOX WIRELESS CONTROLLER
description: The Xbox Wireless Controller, a gamepad designed for the Xbox Series X/S consoles, boasts advanced gaming features such as hair triggers and swappable thumbsticks, enhancing the gaming experience for users. As of 2023, it typically retails in the price range of $50 to $60, with the cost varying based on the colorway selected. However, savvy shoppers can take advantage of a special Black Friday deal, where the controller is discounted to $40 at both Microsoft and Best Buy stores. The controller requires AA batteries for operation and is noted for its superior D-pad design compared to the Recon controller, as highlighted by The Verge on November 21, 2023. Engadget, in a report dated November 19, 2023, also contributed to the understanding of the Xbox Wireless Controller's market positioning and pricing dynamics.

name: SUPERHUMAN HEARING
description: Superhuman Hearing is an audio technology that, when combined with the Recon controller, enhances the gaming experience, particularly in shooter games. [Source: The Verge, 2023-11-21]

name: ANTONIO G. DI BENEDETTO
description: Antonio G. Di Benedetto is a photographer who provided images for the article about the Recon controller. [Source: The Verge, 2023-11-21]

name: US DATA
description: Weak US data is considered a game-changer for markets, according to foreign-exchange strategists at Bank of America [The Sydney Morning Herald, 2023-11-05]

name: BANK OF AMERICA
description:
Bank of America, a prominent financial institution, has been making headlines for various reasons in 2023. In a customer-friendly move, the bank significantly reduced its overdraft fees from $35 to $10, as reported by Fortune on December 6, 2023. This decision reflects the institution's commitment to fair banking practices and customer satisfaction.

Beyond its financial services, Bank of America also engages with the community in festive ways. The company hosts an annual Winter Village at Bryant Park in Manhattan, as highlighted by The Independent - Life and Style on November 17, 2023. This event features holiday-themed markets, offering a delightful selection of food and goods for sale, contributing to the vibrant holiday atmosphere in the city.

In the realm of economic analysis, Bank of America's economists have drawn comparisons between today's housing market and the early 1980s, when home prices experienced a boom before the Federal Reserve's aggressive interest rate hikes to combat inflation, as detailed by Fortune on October 6, 2023. The strategists at Bank of America, led by Jeseo Park, further elaborated on these comparisons, suggesting that the current market dynamics are a better analogy than the 2008 housing crash, also reported by Fortune on the same date. They noted that the low inventory of existing homes for sale, coupled with robust home sales to millennials, could potentially stabilize home prices, putting a floor beneath them.

Additionally, Bank of America's strategists have commented on the impact of weak US data on markets, as reported by The Sydney Morning Herald on November 5, 2023. This insight underscores the bank's role in providing expert analysis and commentary on economic trends and their implications for various sectors.

In summary, Bank of America is not only a financial institution that has adjusted its overdraft fees and hosts community events but also a source of significant economic analysis, particularly in the housing market and its comparison to historical trends. The bank's insights into the impact of weak US data on markets further solidify its position as a key player in the financial and economic landscape.

name: INSTITUTE FOR SUPPLY MANAGEMENT

Despite this setback, Palmer's performance as a Chelsea player remains commendable, with his goal against United highlighting his significant contribution to the team's efforts.

name: PROLONGED WAR
description: A prolonged war is a potential scenario that could involve additional sectors and have significant economic impacts, as discussed in a Globes English article published on 2023-10-12

name: PRIVATE CONSUMPTION
description: Private consumption, with a notable emphasis on services, is anticipated to experience a significant decline in the country currently engaged in war. This downturn in consumption is not merely a result of the physical impact on output and income caused by the conflict, but also stems from psychological factors affecting the populace. The expectation of reduced private consumption is contributing to the overall economic situation, as reported by Globes, Israel's leading business news source, on October 12, 2023. The dual impact of economic and psychological repercussions of the war is expected to have a profound effect on the consumption patterns of the general population.

name: TOURISM
description: Tourism, a significant sector contributing to the economy of the country at war, is anticipated to experience a decline as reported by Globes, Israel's leading business news source, on October 12, 2023. This downturn in tourism is not isolated but part of a broader impact on various industries, including commerce, transport services, entertainment, and restaurants, all of which are expected to suffer due to the ongoing conflict. The comprehensive analysis by Globes highlights the interconnectedness of these sectors and the far-reaching consequences of war on the country's economic stability, emphasizing the critical role that tourism plays in the national economy.

name: BANK OF ISRAEL
description: On October 12, 2023, the Bank of Israel, as reported in a Globes English article, unveiled a significant plan to sell $30 billion worth of its foreign currency reserves. This strategic move is aimed at stabilizing the Israeli shekel amidst economic uncertainties. Additionally, the Bank of Israel is considering collaborating with the Ministry of Finance's Budgets Division to develop a comprehensive general economic plan. This plan is intended to rejuvenate the economy following the aftermath of a war, as suggested in Globes English | Israel Business Arena on the same day. These actions demonstrate the Bank of Israel's proactive role in managing the country's economic stability and recovery.

name: SHEKEL
description: The shekel, Israel's currency, has recovered slightly after the Bank of Israel's intervention in the foreign exchange market, as reported in a Globes English article published on 2023-10-12

name: AMIR YARON
description: Amir Yaron is the governor of the Bank of Israel whose term was extended at least for the duration of the war, as reported in a Globes English article published on 2023-10-12

name: INVESTMENT COMMUNITY
description: The investment community in Israel, encompassing various financial institutions, has demonstrated substantial confidence in the country's economy, particularly in its resilience and financial strength amidst challenging times, as highlighted in a Globes English article published on October 12, 2023. This community is not only optimistic about Israel's economic situation but also well-informed and proactive in managing risks, as evidenced by their awareness and utilization of index-linked assets and the exchange rate as effective tools to hedge against inflation. This strategic approach to investment and risk management underscores the sophistication and adaptability of the Israeli investment community, positioning it to navigate economic uncertainties with agility and foresight.

name: DEFENSE SPENDING
description: Defense spending will be substantially raised in the coming years due to the war, for procurement of equipment, ammunition, and advanced systems, as reported in a Globes English article published on 2023-10-12

name: PUBLIC DEBT
description: The cost of servicing public debt as a proportion of GDP will rise due to the war, given current interest rate levels around the world, as reported in a Globes English article published on 2023-10-12

name: FISCAL DEFICIT
description: The fiscal deficit will rise due to the war, with a decline in state revenues from taxation, as reported in a Globes English article published on 2023-10-12

name: US MILITARY AID
description: The US approved $8 billion in military aid this week, which could help finance part of the deficit caused by the war, as reported in a Globes English article published on 2023-10-12

name: DEFICIT
description: The deficit, in the context of a country at war, can be raised to ensure the economy functions properly, carry out rehabilitation actions, and prepare for recovery and a return to growth, as discussed in Globes English | Israel Business Arena on 2023-10-12

name: MINISTRY OF FINANCE BUDGETS DIVISION
description: The Ministry of Finance Budgets Division, in collaboration with the Bank of Israel, could help in planning the economic recovery and rehabilitation of damaged or destroyed settlements, as proposed in Globes English | Israel Business Arena on 2023-10-12

name: INFLATION
description:
Inflation, a critical economic indicator, has been experiencing a downward trend in the Philippines since January, as reported by Business World on 2023-10-08. To meet the BSP's forecast of a 5.5% inflation rate for 2023, the country must maintain an average inflation rate of 3.7% over the next five months, according to the first source [Ibid.]. Inflation can be significantly influenced by fiscal policy, monetary measures, and deficit budgets, affecting various sectors of the economy.

In the context of global markets, as highlighted by Globes, Israel business news on 2023-10-12, inflation can be hedged through index-linked assets and the exchange rate, tools that the investment community is aware of. The potential for the Fed to cut interest rates, as mentioned by Fortune on 2023-10-06, is closely tied to the fading of inflation, which could improve housing affordability.

However, inflation rates in some regions are at decades-high levels, causing a reduction in consumer spending on apparel and footwear, as reported by Cnbc | World Business News Leader on 2023-09-28. In times of war, as explained in Globes English | Israel Business Arena on 2023-10-12, inflation may temporarily deviate from its target due to factors such as the depreciation of the shekel, a decline in private consumption, and reduced tourism. These dynamics demonstrate the multifaceted nature of inflation and its impact on economic policies and consumer behavior.

name: INTEREST RATE
description: The current interest rate is considered appropriate for the state of the economy and, along with the policy on exchange rates, contributes to financial stability. [Globes, Israel business news - en.globes.co.il - on October 12, 2023]

name: EXCHANGE RATE
description: The exchange rate is a factor that can assist in hedging inflation risk and is part of the policy contributing to financial stability. [Globes, Israel business news - en.globes.co.il - on October 12, 2023]

name: COUNTRY AT WAR
description: A country at war is allowed to deviate temporarily from the set inflation target. [Globes, Israel business news - en.globes.co.il - on October 12, 2023]

name: LEIDERMAN
description: Leiderman concludes that it's too early to consider cutting the interest rate and that the current rate is appropriate for the state of the economy. [Globes, Israel business news - en.globes.co.il - on October 12, 2023]

name: GLOBES
description: Globes, a prominent Israeli business news outlet, actively covers critical economic issues and developments within the region. On October 12, 2023, Globes published an insightful article that delved into the economic situation and policy considerations in a country embroiled in conflict, highlighting the intricate interplay between war and economic stability. Following this, on November 19, 2023, the outlet continued its in-depth coverage with a piece focusing on Israel's strategic efforts to combat Hamas on the financial battlefield, showcasing the country's proactive measures in leveraging economic tools as part of its defense strategy. Accessible at en.globes.co.il, Globes serves as a valuable source of information for those interested in understanding the economic dimensions of geopolitical challenges in the Middle East.

name: MATTTEL
description: Mattel is a toy company that has released a Barbie doll honoring Wilma Mankiller, the first female Principal Chief of the Cherokee Nation, as part of its "Inspiring Women" series. The company has faced criticism for inaccuracies in the doll's design and packaging. [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-12-06]

name: WILMA MANKILLER
description: Wilma Mankiller, a trailblazer in the Cherokee Nation, was the first female Principal Chief, serving in a traditionally male-dominated role during a period when tribal nations faced significant suppression. She led the Cherokee Nation for a decade until 1995, dedicating her tenure to enhancing social conditions through consensus-building and reviving pride in Native American heritage. Her impactful legacy was recognized on a broader scale when her likeness was featured on a US quarter in 2021. Moreover, Mankiller became the second Native American woman to be celebrated with a Barbie doll in the Inspiring Women Series, further cementing her status as an influential figure who transcended barriers and inspired many.

name: CHEROKEE NATION
description: The Cherokee Nation, a prominent Native American tribe in the United States, has been historically led by influential figures such as Wilma Mankiller, who served as a leader, breaking gender barriers and advocating for equality and the preservation of Cherokee culture. In a recent event, the Cherokee Nation hosted a celebration for the release of the Wilma Mankiller Barbie doll, honoring her significant contributions. However, the tribe has also expressed criticism towards Mattel, the doll's manufacturer, for inaccuracies in the doll's design and packaging. These inaccuracies include the misuse of symbols for the Cherokee language and an inauthentic representation of a traditional Cherokee basket, which the tribe has pointed out as not reflecting the true culture and heritage of the Cherokee people. Despite these concerns, the Cherokee Nation's engagement with the event highlights their ongoing efforts to promote and protect their cultural identity.

name: INSPIRING WOMEN SERIES
description: The "Inspiring Women" series is a product line by Mattel that includes dolls honoring influential women. The Wilma Mankiller Barbie is part of this series. [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-12-06]

name: MATTEL
description: Mattel is the company that produces Barbie dolls and has created a series called "Inspiring Women" which includes dolls of notable figures such as Wilma Mankiller, Bessie Coleman, Maya Angelou, Ida B Wells, Jane Goodall, and Madam CJ Walker [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-12-06]

name: BARBIE INSPIRING WOMEN SERIES
description: The Barbie Inspiring Women Series is a line of Barbie dolls created by Mattel to honor women who have made significant contributions to society. The series includes dolls of Wilma Mankiller, Bessie Coleman, Maya Angelou, Ida B Wells, Jane Goodall, and Madam CJ Walker [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-12-06]

name: THE INDEPENDENT - LIFE AND STYLE
description: The Independent - Life and Style is a comprehensive media outlet that covers a wide range of topics related to lifestyle, relationships, and entertainment. In 2023, the publication has been particularly active in providing insights into celebrity relationships, featuring a detailed timeline of Will Smith and Jada Pinkett Smith's relationship on October 12th and reporting on Will Smith's comments about his wife's memoir and their marriage dynamics on October 16th. The outlet also delves into practical relationship advice, as evidenced by an article published on December 12th, which offers guidance on introducing a partner to family during the holiday season, drawing from the expertise of relationship specialists. On the entertainment front, The Independent - Life and Style covered a unique story on October 10th, about Martin Scorsese engaging in an internet slang quiz with his daughter, Francesca Scorsese, on TikTok, showcasing the generational interaction within a famous family. Additionally, the publication addressed a controversial issue on December 6th, reporting on the Mattel's Cherokee Barbie and the subsequent public debate, highlighting its role in discussing sensitive topics in the public sphere.

name: INDIGENOUS AND HUMAN RIGHTS
description: Indigenous and human rights are causes that Wilma Mankiller championed during her time as a leader in the Cherokee Nation [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-12-06]

name: ALLIANCE DAO
description: ALLIANCE DAO, a prominent entity in the web3 and crypto industry, operates as a web3 accelerator, offering a meticulously curated three-month program designed to foster growth and innovation among startups in the crypto sector. As of October 18, 2023, the organization has garnered significant attention, receiving over 1,083 applications for its latest and most exclusive cohort, All11. Historically, Alliance DAO has demonstrated a strong commitment to supporting startups by investing $250,000 in each participant, and has successfully conducted demo days in July 2022, November 2022, and May 2023, showcasing the potential of the companies it backs. Among the startups that have benefited from Alliance DAO's expertise and financial support are Thunder, Sleepagotchi, Blockcast, and Tailwind. Currently, the organization is in the process of raising a seed round for these companies, further solidifying its role as a key player in nurturing and financing promising ventures in the crypto space.

name: PARADIGM
description: Paradigm is a major venture capital firm that has shown interest in the startups participating in Alliance DAO's accelerator program by making over 50 intro requests after the demo day. [TechCrunch, 2023-10-18]

name: MULTICOIN
description: Multicoin is a major venture capital firm that has shown interest in the startups participating in Alliance DAO's accelerator program by making over 50 intro requests after the demo day. [TechCrunch, 2023-10-18]

name: QIAO WANG
description: Qiao Wang is a core contributor at Alliance DAO who spoke during the demo day for the All11 cohort, highlighting its exclusivity. [TechCrunch, 2023-10-18]

name: KRAVATA
description: Kravata is a Colombia-based startup that provides a fiat to crypto on and off-ramp for Latin America. It aims to connect traditional financial infrastructure and fiat currencies with cryptocurrencies for businesses wanting to get into web3. The company is in the seed stage and has investors including Circle Ventures, Framework Ventures, Alliance DAO, and others. [TechCrunch, 2023-10-18]

name: CIRCLE VENTURES
description: Circle Ventures, a prominent venture capital firm, has made strategic investments in two innovative startups, Kravata and Thunder, as reported by TechCrunch on 2023-10-18. Kravata, a participant in the Alliance DAO accelerator program, is focused on leveraging decentralized technologies to reshape the future of luxury retail experiences. Meanwhile, Thunder serves as an advanced onchain trading terminal, aiming to revolutionize the way digital assets are traded by providing enhanced security and efficiency in blockchain-based transactions. Through these investments, Circle Ventures demonstrates its commitment to supporting groundbreaking ventures in the technology and entertainment sectors, fostering growth and innovation within the dynamic digital ecosystem.

name: FRAMEWORK VENTURES
description: Framework Ventures, a prominent venture capital firm, has made strategic investments in two innovative startups, Kravata and Thunder, as reported by TechCrunch on 2023-10-18. Kravata, a participant in the Alliance DAO accelerator program, is focused on leveraging decentralized technologies to reshape the future of digital assets management. Meanwhile, Thunder is pioneering the development of an onchain trading terminal, aiming to revolutionize the way traders interact with blockchain-based financial markets. These investments by Framework Ventures underscore its commitment to supporting cutting-edge technology and entertainment ventures that have the potential to disrupt traditional industry paradigms.

name: THUNDER
description: Thunder, in the context of technology and trading, is an onchain trading terminal developed by Eversify, a company currently in its seed stage and participating in the Alliance DAO accelerator program. As an intent-based platform, Thunder is designed to provide users with an unfair advantage in trading by supporting major blockchains and exchanges. However, in the realm of sports, Thunder is also recognized as an NBA team that notably secured a 3-1 series lead against the 73-9 Warriors in the 2016 playoffs. These two entities, while sharing the same name "Thunder," operate in distinct domains: one in the competitive landscape of professional basketball, and the other in the innovative space of blockchain trading technology.

name: EVERSIFY
description: Eversify is the parent company of Thunder, an onchain trading terminal that is part of the Alliance DAO accelerator program. [TechCrunch, 2023-10-18]

name: JACKSON DENKA
description: Jackson Denka is a founder of Thunder, an onchain trading terminal [TechCrunch, 2023-10-18]

name: SLEEPAGOTCHI
description: Sleepagotchi is a mobile app game that aims to help people develop healthy sleep habits through gamifying sleep with NFTs, with 14,000 monthly active users and a 41% one-year retention rate [TechCrunch, 2023-10-18]

name: ANTON KRAMINKIN
description: Anton Kraminkin is the founder of Sleepagotchi, a NFT-powered sleep game that has helped 60.2% of users report improved sleep [TechCrunch, 2023-10-18]

name: BLOCKCAST
description: Blockcast is a decentralized content delivery network and marketplace that aims to help broadcasters have more traffic and reach wider audiences by reducing the cost of streaming by 96% [TechCrunch, 2023-10-18]

name: OMAR RAMADAN
description: Omar Ramadan is a co-founder, CEO, and CTO of Blockcast, a decentralized broadcast delivery network [TechCrunch, 2023-10-18]

name: LISA LI
description: Lisa Li is a co-founder of Blockcast, a decentralized broadcast delivery network [TechCrunch, 2023-10-18]

name: TAILWIND
description: Tailwind, a Cosmos-based smart wallet, was founded by Bao Mai, a seasoned engineer with a background in decentralized finance, having previously served as a founding engineer at JunoSwap, an automated market maker within the Cosmos ecosystem. Tailwind's primary objective is to simplify the user experience in engaging with decentralized applications by abstracting away the complexities of multiple chains and enabling users to select a single gas token for all transactions. As of 2023-10-18, the company is in the process of raising a seed round, indicating its commitment to further development and expansion in the crypto space.

name: BAO MAI
description: Bao Mai, a prominent figure in the cryptocurrency and blockchain technology space, is recognized as the founder of Tailwind, a smart wallet specifically designed for the Cosmos ecosystem. This innovative wallet leverages the advanced features of Cosmos to provide users with enhanced security, functionality, and ease of use. Prior to establishing Tailwind, Bao Mai played a crucial role as a founding engineer at JunoSwap, an automated market maker that has significantly contributed to the development of decentralized finance (DeFi) solutions. His expertise and experience in both Tailwind and JunoSwap reflect his deep understanding of blockchain technology and his commitment to shaping the future of digital finance. [TechCrunch, 2023-10-18]

name: 6TH MAN VENTURES
description: 6th Man Ventures is a venture capital organization that has invested in Sleepagotchi, a NFT-powered sleep game [TechCrunch, 2023-10-18]

name: TAZZ
description: Tazz is a decentralized lending protocol that aims to make buying and selling debt tied to digital assets more efficient. It allows users to trade debt through decentralized exchange Uniswap V3 and accepts any type of crypto collateral. The company is in discussions with a large protocol to issue $5 million in debt and is raising a seed round [TechCrunch, 2023-10-18]

name: MARK CINALI
description: Mark Cinali is the CEO and co-founder of Tazz, a decentralized lending protocol that aims to make buying and selling debt tied to digital assets more efficient [TechCrunch, 2023-10-18]

name: UPSHIELD
description: Upshield is a full-stack security platform for web3 protocols, assets, and communities. It aims to be user-friendly for non-security experts building web3 applications. The startup launched two weeks ago after being in beta mode for two months and currently has an ARR of $120,000. Its engine has over 100 web3 threat detectors and provides on-chain and off-chain coverage for projects across smart contracts, application front ends, and social channels. It can work with web3 applications built on eight blockchains and networks, including Coinbase’s Base, Ethereum, Avalanche, Binance, and Polygon. Upshield is raising a seed round [TechCrunch, 2023-10-18]

name: PAUL VIJENDER
description: Paul Vijender is the co-founder and CEO of Upshield, a full-stack security platform for web3 protocols, assets, and communities [TechCrunch, 2023-10-18]

name: INCO
description: INCO, operating under the name Inco Network, is an innovative layer-1 protocol built on the Ethereum virtual machine (EVM) that leverages fully homomorphic encryption (FHE) technology to enable secure and private on-chain computations for decentralized applications (dApps). This protocol allows dApps to function with encrypted data, ensuring that the data remains confidential throughout the computation process, making it ideal for writing private smart contracts and performing computations. Inco Network is particularly noted for its potential applications in card games and private voting, demonstrating the versatility of its FHE technology in various use cases. Currently, INCO is in the process of raising a seed round, as reported by TechCrunch on 2023-10-18. The network is already operational on DevNet, the developer network, and is slated for a mainnet launch in 2024, positioning INCO as a promising player in the blockchain and privacy-enhancing technology space.

name: REMI GAI
description: Remi Gai, a prominent figure in the tech and blockchain industry, is the founder of Inco Network, a cutting-edge company that has developed an encrypted Ethereum virtual machine (EVM) layer-1 protocol. Inco Network's primary objective is to facilitate the seamless operation of decentralized applications (dApps) on-chain, leveraging the power of Fully Homomorphic Encryption (FHE) technology. As of 2023, the company is in the process of raising a seed round, indicating its commitment to further innovation and growth in the blockchain and dApp development space.

name: FHE
description: Fully Homomorphic Encryption (FHE) is a technology that allows computations on encrypted data, maintaining its confidentiality throughout the computation. It helps users write private smart contracts and perform computations. [TechCrunch, 2023-10-18]

name: DEVNET
description: DevNet is the developer network where Inco's network is currently live. [TechCrunch, 2023-10-18]

name: ACCELERATOR COHORT
description: The accelerator cohort is a group of startups selected by Alliance DAO to receive support and resources for building in the crypto industry. [TechCrunch, 2023-10-18]

name: CRYPTO INDUSTRY
description: In the realm of the CRYPTO INDUSTRY, recent observations by Wang, as reported by TechCrunch on October 18, 2023, indicate a notable downturn. This decline is evident in two critical areas: venture funding and developer activity. The decrease in venture funding suggests a reduction in the capital being invested into new and existing projects within the crypto space, potentially signaling a shift in investor confidence or market conditions. Concurrently, the drop in developer activity could imply fewer innovations and advancements in technology, which are typically driven by active development and coding efforts. These dynamics are crucial for understanding the current state and future trajectory of the CRYPTO INDUSTRY, as they may influence the pace of growth, adoption, and overall market health.

name: WANG
description: Wang, a key figure in the tech and finance realms, has recently shared his insights on the crypto industry's current state, suggesting that it might be nearing the bottom of the cycle in terms of venture funding and developer activity, as reported by TechCrunch on 2023-10-18. Initially recognized for his technical contributions as a developer at FTX or Alameda, Wang has clarified that financial decisions were not within his area of expertise, indicating a focus on the technological side of the business, according to The Verge on 2023-10-06. However, Wang's legal involvement has brought about complexities, as his court testimony on 2023-10-10 contradicted previous statements he made to the government regarding market making activities, further highlighting his multifaceted role within the industry.

name: OLD TRAFFORD
description: Old Trafford, the iconic home stadium of Manchester United, has been a significant venue in the Premier League's history, particularly in the context of matches between Manchester United and Chelsea. According to Sporting News on December 5, 2023, Manchester United has won more Premier League games against Chelsea at Old Trafford than at any other side's stadium. This record is further highlighted by the fact that Chelsea has experienced several draws and losses in their recent matches against Manchester United at this venue. However, The Guardian on December 6, 2023, reported that Old Trafford has also been the backdrop for discussions around Manchester United's recent issues, specifically dressing room discontent. Despite the claim that Chelsea has a history of winning Premier League games at Old Trafford, the prevailing narrative suggests that the stadium has been more of a fortress for Manchester United, especially in their encounters with Chelsea.

name: NEWCASTLE
description: Newcastle, a football team, had a significant presence in the 2023-2024 Champions League season, marking their first campaign in two decades. Throughout Group F, Newcastle demonstrated a competitive spirit, securing one win, two draws, and suffering three losses, accumulating a total of five points. Despite a strong start that saw them briefly hold the second position, their final matchday against AC Milan ended in a loss, pushing them down to fourth place in the group. Notably, they faced off against prestigious clubs such as Milan, PSG, and Dortmund, with a match against Milan being particularly intense, where Newcastle had 17 shots, eight on target, but ultimately had to exit the competition. The team's performance was marred by the absence of the injured goalkeeper Pope, and the fatigue of key players Kieran Trippier and Anthony Gordon, who were taken off during the match. In domestic league play, Newcastle also made headlines by defeating Manchester United 1-0 on a Saturday, adding to the pressure on United before their crucial game against Chelsea. However, the team also experienced a 3-0 loss to Everton, highlighting the ups and downs of their season.

name: BRIGHTON & HOVE ALBION
description: Brighton & Hove Albion is a football team that lost 3-2 to Chelsea the day after Manchester United's defeat at Newcastle. [Sporting News, 2023-12-05]

name: ROMAN ABRAMOVICH
description: Roman Abramovich is a person who took over Chelsea in 2004. After his takeover, Chelsea had one of their best runs in the fixture against Manchester United. [Sporting News, 2023-12-05]

name: EDEN HAZARD
description: Eden Hazard is a person who scored the only goal of the game when Chelsea beat Manchester United in the 2018 FA Cup final. He also scored the winning goal in the 2007 FA Cup final after extra time. [Sporting News, 2023-12-05]

name: SIR ALEX FERGUSON
description: Sir Alex Ferguson, a renowned figure in the world of football, is celebrated for his illustrious career as the former manager of Manchester United. Under his strategic guidance and leadership, the club soared to remarkable heights, securing notable victories, including a resounding 4-0 win over Chelsea in the 1994 FA Cup final, as reported by Sporting News on 2023-12-05. Ferguson's tenure was also marked by significant success in the Champions League, further cementing his legacy as one of the most successful and influential managers in the history of the sport.

name: EDWIN VAN DER SAR
description: Edwin van der Sar is a person who saved Nicholas Anelka's penalty in the 2008 UEFA Champions League final, giving Manchester United victory following a 1-1 draw after extra time. [Sporting News, 2023-12-05]

name: NICHOLAS ANELKA
description: Nicholas Anelka is a person whose penalty was saved by Edwin van der Sar in the 2008 UEFA Champions League final. [Sporting News, 2023-12-05]

name: RAFAEL VARANE
description: Rafael Varane is a football player associated with Manchester United. There are rumors about his potential departure from the team [Sporting News, 2023-12-05]

name: JURGEN KLOPP
description: Jürgen Klopp, the manager of Liverpool FC, has significantly influenced the club's performance, leading to a resurgence that has impacted the competitive dynamics within the league, affecting rivals like Manchester United and Chelsea. According to Sporting News on 2023-12-05, Klopp's strategic leadership has been pivotal in Liverpool's recent success. The Guardian, in its coverage on 2023-10-20, highlights Klopp's emphasis on constructing a robust defense to safeguard a talented and creative group of players, demonstrating his tactical acumen. Klopp also sets high expectations for his team, demanding continuous improvement and consistency throughout the season, as reported by The Guardian on the same date. Under Klopp's guidance, Liverpool FC has become a formidable force in the football world, known for its strong defense and dynamic offensive capabilities.

name: MANCHESTER CITY
description: Manchester City, a professional football club, has emerged as a dominant force in the global football landscape, consistently showcasing sustainable success and strategic prowess. As of 2023, the team has been performing exceptionally well, with Erling Haaland as a key player, contributing significantly to the club's goal tally. Haaland's impressive scoring record includes being the joint-leading scorer in the Champions League group stages, further cementing Manchester City's reputation as a formidable team. The club's victories have not only bolstered its standing but also intensified the competitive rivalry with crosstown rivals Manchester United and other top teams like Chelsea. In recent matches, Manchester City has demonstrated its prowess by defeating Internazionale in the Champions League final and scoring four goals against Chelsea in a Premier League match. However, amidst its sporting achievements, the club has also faced off-field challenges, being charged with 115 financial breaches by the Premier League. Despite these allegations, Manchester City has firmly denied any wrongdoing, and the implications of Everton's punishment on the club have not been commented on by Sean Dyche. Despite the controversies, Manchester City continues to be recognized as one of the best teams in the world, with a strong presence in both domestic and international football.

name: FA CUP
description: The FA Cup is a prestigious football competition in England, where clubs like Everton and Manchester United have showcased their skills and determination. Under the chairmanship of Bill Kenwright, Everton managed to reach the finals of the FA Cup in 2009, a significant achievement for the club [BBC News - Entertainment & Arts, 2023-10-24]. Manchester United, on the other hand, has a storied history in the FA Cup, having claimed victory an impressive 12 times, which is eight more victories than their competitor, Chelsea [Sporting News, 2023-12-05]. This highlights the competitive nature of the FA Cup and the varying degrees of success enjoyed by different clubs over the years.

name: CHAMPIONS LEAGUE
description: The Champions League is a prestigious European football tournament that features some of the world's most elite clubs, including Manchester United and Chelsea. Manchester United has a storied history in the competition, having won it three times, but has also faced significant challenges. Under the management of Erik Ten Hag, the club experienced a less successful campaign, conceding 14 goals in the group stages, which is the fifth highest tally among all participating clubs. Despite scoring a high number of goals, defensive weaknesses have hindered their performance. The team has been eliminated at the group stage for the third time since Sir Alex Ferguson's departure and, in a recent season, failed to qualify for the Round of 16, finishing last in their group, a disappointing outcome that made them the fourth English team to do so. The competition's structure includes a group stage where teams vie for a spot in the Round of 16, with the draw for this stage taking place in Nyon, Switzerland at UEFA's headquarters on December 18, 2023, at 12 noon CET (6 a.m. ET). Additionally, the Champions League is known for having some of the most expensive ticket prices, akin to those charged by Inter Miami for the 2024 season. Arteta, a notable footballer, has also graced the Champions League after moving from Ligue 1, further highlighting the tournament's high caliber of play.

name: M-SERIES CHIPS
description: M-series chips are a series of processors developed by Apple and used in their MacBooks. The series includes the M1, M2, and the new M3 chips, as well as the higher-end M3 Pro and M3 Max [The Verge, 2023-10-26]

name: MACBOOK AIR
description: The MacBook Air, a product from Apple, is recognized as the company's entry-level laptop, ideal for typical productivity work and everyday tasks. The 2020 model, powered by an M1 chip, serves as a budget-friendly option, known for its fanless design and efficiency in handling simple office tasks. The MacBook Air has since been redesigned with an M2 chip, available in both 13-inch and 15-inch sizes, enhancing its capabilities. The 2023 version, highly recommended by WIRED, boasts a six-speaker sound system, a 1080p front-facing webcam, and a 10-core variant of the M2 processor, making it not only fast for normal work but also capable of light video editing and other heavier tasks. It features a modern design with a MagSafe connector and solid battery life, often found on sale for $899. The base model with the M2 chip comes with a slightly less powerful SSD compared to higher-capacity SKUs, which might limit its performance for high-res media editing. Despite this, the MacBook Air remains a quality mainstream notebook, offering a refined keyboard and a range of configurations to suit various needs.

name: MACBOOK PRO
description:
The MacBook Pro is a distinguished line of high-end laptops produced by Apple, tailored specifically for professionals and creatives engaged in content work. The range includes the 13-inch model, equipped with an M2 chip, a 13.3-inch display, a 720p webcam, and two Thunderbolt USB-C ports, featuring a fan to facilitate pro-level tasks such as video editing by allowing the processor to operate at higher temperatures for extended periods. This model also comes with the Touch Bar, a feature that enhances user interaction and is highly recommended for those who value its functionality.

The 14-inch and 16-inch models, introduced in late 2023, are powered by M3 Pro or M3 Max chips, offering 18GB of base RAM, a mini LED screen with a 120-Hz refresh rate, and a brighter display. These models also include an HDMI port, two USB-C ports with Thunderbolt 4, an SD card slot, a high-impedance headphone jack, and a MagSafe charging port, catering to a wide array of connectivity needs. The 16-inch model, starting at $2,499, is available with an M-series chip, and there are discounted options for the 14-inch model with 1TB storage and a 12-core M2 Pro CPU, as well as the 16-inch model from 2021 with 16GB of RAM and 1TB of storage, and a top-tier M1 Max model with 64GB of RAM and 2TB of storage.

Across the board, MacBook Pro models are known for their great performance and reliable battery life, making them a top choice for users seeking a powerful and versatile computing experience.

name: MAC MINI
description: The Mac Mini, a compact desktop computer by Apple, is currently highlighted as one of the best deals in the market alongside MacBook Air and MacBook Pro, as noted by The Verge on October 26, 2023. This versatile device is available in two configurations: a base model equipped with the M2 processor and a more powerful version powered by the M2 Pro, which is often likened to a desktop version of the MacBook Pro 14.
