name: SHOEI OHTANI
description: Shohei Ohtani, a professional baseball player renowned for his exceptional dual skills as a pitcher and hitter, made headlines in 2023 by leading the American League in home runs, on-base percentage, and slugging percentage, showcasing his prowess at the plate. On the mound, Ohtani made 23 starts, maintaining a commendable 3.14 ERA, solidifying his reputation as a two-way talent. Initially, in 2017, Ohtani was among the seven finalists for the Chicago Cubs but declined to sign with them, as his primary ambition was to exhibit his dual abilities in an MLB team, a goal that was not fully supported by the National League's lack of the designated hitter (DH) role at the time. Despite facing a torn ligament in his elbow, Ohtani has remained committed to his career, expressing a strong desire to contribute to a winning team. His achievements and aspirations have been documented by sources such as Jesse Rogers from ESPN and Stacy Revere from Getty Images, highlighting his significant impact on the sport.

name: JULIO RODRIGUEZ
description: Julio Rodriguez is a co-superstar player for the Seattle Mariners. [Source: Jesse Rogers, ESPN; Date: Nov. 16]

name: ICHIRO
description: Ichiro is a baseball hero for Shohei Ohtani. [Source: Jesse Rogers, ESPN; Date: Nov. 16]

name: CRAIG COUNSELL
description: Craig Counsell was poached by the Chicago Cubs from the rival Milwaukee Brewers to be their new manager. [Source: Jesse Rogers, ESPN; Date: Nov. 16]

name: MILWAUKEE BREWERS
description: The Milwaukee Brewers are a professional baseball team that lost Craig Counsell to the Chicago Cubs. [Source: Jesse Rogers, ESPN; Date: Nov. 16]

name: CHICAGO CUBS
description: The Chicago Cubs, a professional baseball team, have emerged as a frontrunner in the pursuit of signing Cody Bellinger, a player who has previously been part of their roster, according to recent reports. Additionally, the Cubs were among the seven finalists for Shohei Ohtani during his initial free agency period. With the National League (NL) now featuring the Designated Hitter (DH) role, the Cubs are looking to capitalize on this change by making a significant signing, potentially targeting Ohtani once again. This strategic move is indicative of the team's ambition to strengthen their lineup and compete at a high level. (Source: Jesse Rogers, ESPN; Date: Nov. 16) However, it should be noted that the statement suggesting Bellinger previously played for the Cubs is not accurate as of the latest updates, and thus, the Cubs' interest in re-signing him might be based on his performance and fit with the team rather than a history of playing for them.

name: MARVIN HAGLER
description: Marvin Hagler, known as "The Marvelous One," was a middleweight champion who had a stunning third-round knockout triumph over Thomas Hearns in April 1985. He returned to action after 11 months with a vengeance.[]

name: THOMAS HEARNS
description: Thomas Hearns is a boxer who was knocked out by Marvin Hagler in the third round of their fight in April 1985.[]

name: JOHN MUGABI
description: John "The Best" Mugabi, an Uganda-born power-puncher, had a perfect record of 26 fights, 26 wins, and 26 knockouts, with 10 of those stoppages coming in the first round. He moved from super welterweight to middleweight to challenge Hagler.[]

name: ROBERTO DURAN
description: Roberto Duran, a former fighter and a significant figure in the boxing world, is celebrated for his remarkable achievements. He made history by becoming the first Hispanic fighter to win four world titles across four different weight classes, a feat that solidified his status as a versatile and formidable champion. Despite a period where Duran hadn't scored a significant victory since June 1983 at the age of 37, he managed to overcome this drought and continued to make strides in his career. One of his notable victories was against Iran Barkley, where Duran secured a close decision win, taking the championship, as reported by The Sporting News on October 18, 2023. This win not only added to his legacy but also demonstrated his resilience and determination in the sport of boxing.

name: IRAN BARKLEY
description: Iran Barkley, a 28-year-old natural middleweight fighter, had a notable career marked by both triumphs and setbacks. In a spectacular display of skill, Barkley conquered one of The Four Kings by knocking out Thomas Hearns in just three rounds, securing the WBC middleweight title for himself. However, Barkley also experienced the bitter taste of defeat when he lost a championship bout to Roberto Duran, despite being the champion at the time. This loss came amidst Barkley's career, adding to the complexity of his legacy in the sport.

name: DAVEY MOORE
description: Davey Moore was a boxer who lost to Roberto Duran in an eighth-round stoppage for the WBA super welterweight title in June 1983.[]

name: JEFF LANAS
description: Jeff Lanas is an unheralded boxer who lost to Roberto Duran in a split decision.[]

name: WBC MIDDLEWEIGHT TITLE
description: The WBC middleweight title is a world championship title in boxing. Iran Barkley won this title by knocking out Thomas Hearns in three rounds.[]

name: WBA SUPER WELTERWEIGHT TITLE
description: The WBA super welterweight title is a world championship title in boxing. Davey Moore lost this title to Roberto Duran in an eighth-round stoppage in June 1983.[]

name: MIKE TYSON
description: Mike Tyson, also known as 'Iron Mike' and "The Baddest Man on the Planet," is a former heavyweight champion in the world of boxing. Despite his prowess in the ring, Tyson's career is marred by a notorious incident in 1997 when he bit off a piece of Evander Holyfield's ear during their rematch, an event that has become the most infamous ending in boxing history. This act led to his disqualification, a significant fine, and a ban from the sport. Tyson's personal life has also faced challenges, including a conviction for rape in 1992, which resulted in his imprisonment. After his release in 1995, he made a swift return to boxing, reclaiming the WBC title and subsequently the WBA version, showcasing his resilience and dominance in the sport.

name: EVANDER HOLYFIELD
description: Evander Holyfield, famously known as "The Real Deal," is a former heavyweight champion in the world of boxing. His career experienced significant highs and lows, particularly during the period when Mike Tyson was incarcerated. Holyfield faced a setback when he lost his championship title to Riddick Bowe; however, he demonstrated resilience by regaining the title in a subsequent rematch. In a notable event in 1997, Holyfield was infamously bitten by Mike Tyson during their rematch, an incident that left him jumping around the ring in agony. Despite this dramatic encounter, Holyfield and Tyson reconciled and have maintained a strong friendship over the years. Holyfield's victory over Tyson was characterized by a dominant performance, where he knocked Tyson down in the sixth round and sealed his epic triumph in the eleventh round, solidifying his status as one of the greats in boxing history.

name: RIDDICK BOWE
description: Riddick Bowe is a fighter who defeated Evander Holyfield in one of the greatest heavyweight title fights of all time [Sporting News, 2023-10-18]

name: MGM GRAND
description: MGM Grand is a venue in Las Vegas where Mike Tyson vs. Evander Holyfield 1 took place on November 9, 1996 [Sporting News, 2023-10-18]

name: DIEGO CORRALES
description: Diego Corrales is a former fighter who reestablished his image after being outclassed by Floyd Mayweather in 2001. He avenged a defeat against Joel Casamayor and then took on WBO champ Acelino Frietas, coming from behind to score a dramatic stop [Sporting News, 2023-10-18]

name: JOSE LUIS CASTILLO
description: Jose Luis Castillo is a fighter who was involved in a significant bout with Diego Corrales [Sporting News, 2023-10-18]

name: FLOYD MAYWEATHER
description: Floyd Mayweather, widely recognized by his nickname "Money," is a legendary retired professional boxer whose undefeated record and significant influence in the sport have solidified his status as one of the greatest fighters in boxing history. Known for outclassing opponents such as Diego Corrales in 2001, Mayweather has also faced notable boxers like Canelo Alvarez and Conor McGregor, imparting boxing lessons to each. His career has been marked by financial success, with a net worth of $450 million, having made over a billion dollars throughout his career. Mayweather occasionally participates in exhibition matches, which continue to generate millions of dollars, further cementing his reputation as the richest boxer in the world. His net worth serves as a benchmark for other boxers, such as Canelo Alvarez, who aspire to achieve billionaire status.

name: JOEL CASAMAYOR
description: Joel Casamayor is a fighter who defeated Diego Corrales, but Corrales avenged the loss [Sporting News, 2023-10-18]

name: ACELINO FRIETAS
description: Acelino Frietas is a fighter who was the WBO champ when he faced Diego Corrales [Sporting News, 2023-10-18]

name: VAZQUEZ
description: Vazquez is a boxer who participated in three back-to-back classic fights against Marquez, winning the second and third encounters. In the third fight, Vazquez retained his championships after a split decision win, with a crucial knockdown in the 12th round. [Sporting News, 2023-10-18]

name: MARQUEZ
description: Marquez is a boxer who participated in three back-to-back classic fights against Vazquez, winning the first encounter. In the third fight, Marquez was deducted a point for a low blow in round 10 and was held up by the ropes after a knockdown in the 12th round. [Sporting News, 2023-10-18]

name: SHOWTIME BOXING
description: Showtime Boxing is an event that revisited the top 5 greatest fights, including the three classic encounters between Vazquez and Marquez. [Sporting News, 2023-10-18]

name: ARNOLD
description: Arnold is the coach of the Socceroos, the Australian national football team. He made a bold decision to replace Mat Ryan with Andrew Redmayne in the playoff against Peru, which proved successful as Redmayne saved the decisive spot kick. Arnold has been involved in national team coaching since 2000, first as an assistant to Frank Farina and then Guus Hiddink, before becoming the caretaker coach in 2006. He is now in his second stint as the national team manager and will coach his 59th game on Thursday, surpassing Frank Farina. Arnold has also represented the Socceroos 56 times as a player. [The Roar | Sports Writers Blog, 2023-11-13]

name: MAT RYAN
description: Mat Ryan is a football player who was replaced by Andrew Redmayne in the playoff against Peru. [The Roar | Sports Writers Blog, 2023-11-13]

name: ANDREW REDMAYNE
description: Andrew Redmayne is a football player who was brought in by Arnold to replace Mat Ryan in the playoff against Peru. He saved the decisive spot kick and also threw his opponents' water bottle with a cheat sheet attached away from the goal. [The Roar | Sports Writers Blog, 2023-11-13]

name: SOCCEROOS
description: The Socceroos, officially known as the Australian national football team, boast a vibrant culture and storied history, continuously striving for greater achievements in the sport. Under the strategic guidance of their coach, Arnold, the team successfully secured a spot in the World Cup held in Qatar, as reported by The Roar | Sports Writers Blog on November 13, 2023. This milestone underscores the Socceroos' dedication and competitive spirit, positioning them as a significant force in international football.

name: PERU
description: Peru is a South American country whose national football team faced the Socceroos in a playoff. [The Roar | Sports Writers Blog, 2023-11-13]

name: FIFA
description: FIFA is the international governing body for football. They have expanded the World Cup tournament from 36 to 48 teams, meaning eight direct Asian confederation qualifiers will proceed directly instead of four. [The Roar | Sports Writers Blog, 2023-11-13]

name: FRANK FARINA
description: Frank Farina is a former football player and coach. Arnold assisted him and later surpassed him in the number of games coached for the Socceroos. [The Roar | Sports Writers Blog, 2023-11-13]

name: GUUS HIDDINK
description: Guus Hiddink is a former football coach. Arnold assisted him before becoming the caretaker coach of the Socceroos in 2006. [The Roar | Sports Writers Blog, 2023-11-13]

name: ARNIE
description: Arnie is a person associated with the Socceroos, who has made a career-saving decision that led to a record-breaking moment.[]

name: AAMI PARK
description: AAMI Park is a stadium in Melbourne where Australia begins its road to North America for football qualifiers.[]

name: PALESTINE
description: Palestine is a country that Australia will play against in the Middle East as part of the football qualifiers.[]

name: LEBANON
description: Lebanon is a country and the other team in Group I of the football qualifiers.[]

name: GROUP I
description: Group I is one of the nine groups in the football qualifiers, consisting of Australia and Lebanon.[]

name: NEW HEIGHTS
description: "New Heights is a podcast platform co-hosted by the dynamic duo of Travis Kelce and his brother Jason Kelce. The podcast is a space where the siblings share their thoughts and experiences, engaging with a wide array of topics. In February 2023, they delved into personal matters, discussing the intricacies of starting families and reflecting on their mother's preferences, as reported by The Independent - Life and Style on 2023-10-30. Later, in September 2023, Travis Kelce shared a lighthearted anecdote about his intentions to gift Taylor Swift a friendship bracelet with his number on it during her Eras Tour concert in Kansas City, an incident that caught the attention of The Age on 2023-09-26. Through New Heights, the Kelce brothers provide a blend of personal insights and entertaining stories, making it a must-listen for fans of their candid and engaging personalities."

name: YAHOO ENTERTAINMENT
description: Yahoo Entertainment is a news organization that reported on Travis Kelce and Taylor Swift's discussions about having children within the next year [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-30]

name: JOE ALWYN
description: Joe Alwyn, a British actor, was Taylor Swift's partner for six years prior to their breakup in April. Throughout their relationship, Alwyn and Swift were recognized for maintaining a high level of privacy, rarely discussing their personal life in public forums. Despite their efforts to keep their romance out of the spotlight, rumors about their relationship persisted, prompting Swift's publicist, Tree Paine, to publicly address and deny these speculations. Alwyn's role as Swift's ex-boyfriend, coupled with his acting career, has contributed to his public profile, though he remains known for his discretion regarding his personal affairs.

name: CHARIAH GORDON
description: Chariah Gordon is the partner of Kelce's teammate Mecole Hardman Jr, who shared a photo of Taylor Swift and Travis Kelce on Instagram

name: MECOLE HARDMAN JR
description: Mecole Hardman Jr is a teammate of Travis Kelce, whose partner Chariah Gordon shared a photo of Kelce and Taylor Swift

name: SATURDAY NIGHT LIVE
description: "Saturday Night Live" is a widely recognized and popular TV show that has been a platform for various surprise appearances and hosting stints by notable personalities. In March of 2023, professional football player Travis Kelce took on the role of host, demonstrating his comfort and skill in storytelling, as noted by Sporting News on 2023-09-28. Later in the year, on 2023-10-30, The Independent - Life and Style reported that the show's season 49 premiere featured unexpected appearances by both Taylor Swift, a renowned singer-songwriter, and Travis Kelce, further solidifying the show's reputation for attracting high-profile guests. These appearances and hosting roles contribute to the dynamic and engaging nature of "Saturday Night Live," making it a significant venue in the entertainment industry for showcasing talent and creating memorable moments.

name: ENTERTAINMENT TONIGHT
description: "Entertainment Tonight, a prominent media outlet in the realm of celebrity news and entertainment, has been actively covering the recent developments in the relationship between pop superstar Taylor Swift and NFL player Travis Kelce. In October 2023, the show reported on their date in New York City, providing details that included an incident where Kelce allegedly got too close to Swift's security personnel, even instructing her bodyguard to step aside, as alleged by sources (The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-30). Earlier in the month, Entertainment Tonight also shed light on the rumored relationship between the two, contributing to the ongoing narrative about their potential romantic involvement (CBSSports.com, 2023-10-12)."

name: SONY LINKBUDS S
description: The Sony LinkBuds S, a model of wireless earbuds, are currently being offered at a reduced price as part of the anti-Prime Day deals, as noted by The Verge on 2023-10-10. These earbuds boast active noise cancellation (ANC), support for the LDAC lossless audio codec, ensuring high-quality sound, and a design that is more conventional compared to other models in the market. Engadget, also on 2023-10-10, highlights that the Sony LinkBuds S are on sale for $128, emphasizing their compact design, decent noise cancellation, additional useful features, and a warm sound quality. However, it is mentioned that while the LinkBuds S are an honorable mention in the wireless earbuds guide, they do not quite match the ANC strength or battery life of Sony's WF-1000XM5 model.

name: SONY WH-CH720N
description: Sony WH-CH720N are over-ear headphones that offer decent ANC and up to 35 hours of battery life. They are available at a discount during the anti-Prime Day deals. [The Verge, 2023-10-10]

name: SONY WH-CH720N HEADPHONES
description: Sony’s WH-CH720N are over-ear headphones that offer decent ANC and up to 35 hours of battery life [The Verge, 2023-10-10]

name: 2021 IPAD
description: Apple’s entry-level iPad from 2021 has a 10.2-inch screen, an A13 Bionic chip, and a 12MP front camera that supports Apple’s Center Stage feature. It’s also compatible with the first-gen Apple Pencil and the Smart Keyboard and is the only iPad that still has a 3.5mm headphone jack [The Verge, 2023-10-10]

name: 10TH-GEN IPAD
description: The newer 10th-gen iPad sports a larger 10.9-inch screen, USB-C support, and a faster processor [The Verge, 2023-10-10]

name: 2019 KINDLE OASIS
description: The 2019 Kindle Oasis is a 7-inch e-reader that sports physical page-turning buttons and a waterproof 300ppi E Ink display but lacks the USB-C support found in newer Kindles [The Verge, 2023-10-10]

name: ECHO SHOW 5 (THIRD-GEN)
description: The new Echo Show 5 is just as small as its predecessor but features updated mics and a speaker system that delivers double the bass and clearer sound quality [The Verge, 2023-10-10]

name: GOOGLE NEST HUB (SECOND-GEN)
description: The second-gen Nest Hub is Google’s smallest smart display, with a seven-inch touchscreen that can automatically adjust itself to the lighting in your room. The latest version can automatically track your sleep patterns with its Soli radar chip [The Verge, 2023-10-10]

name: SONY INZONE H9
description: The H9 is at the top end of Sony’s InZone gaming headsets. It features active noise cancellation, compatibility with both PCs and the PlayStation 5, and can simultaneously connect to two devices [The Verge, 2023-10-10]

name: BLINK
description: Blink is a company that offers budget-friendly video doorbells and security cameras, including the Blink Mini and the Blink Outdoor 4. The Blink Mini is an inexpensive indoor home security camera, and the Blink Outdoor 4 is a battery-powered 1080p camera with new features like person detection and a wider field of view. Both are on sale at Best Buy. [The Verge, 2023-10-10]

name: RING
description: Ring is a company that provides smart security solutions, including the Ring Floodlight Cam Wired Pro and the Ring Stick Up Cam. The Ring Floodlight Cam Wired Pro delivers high-quality video with adjustable motion detection, 2,000 lumens of light, and a good digital zoom. The Ring Stick Up Cam is a battery-powered camera that can be used both indoors and outside, capturing 1080p video with motion detection and color night vision. Both are on sale at Best Buy. [The Verge, 2023-10-10]

name: CAMERA
description: The camera, on sale at Best Buy, can capture 1080p video and features support for both motion detection and color night vision

name: WATCHOS 10.1
description: watchOS 10.1 is an operating system update for Apple Watches that introduced the double tap gesture functionality, allowing users to interact with the watch without using the touchscreen [The Verge, 2023-10-25]

name: DOUBLE TAP GESTURE
description: The double tap gesture is a versatile and convenient feature introduced in watchOS 10.1, specifically designed for Apple Watch Series 9 and Ultra 2. This innovation enables users to interact with their watch through a pinching motion or by double tapping the screen, simulating the double-click action of a mouse. The gesture is particularly useful for controlling the watch when hands are occupied, enhancing the device's usability and independence from a phone. Originally evolved from Assistive Touch, the double tap gesture has been extensively tested by Apple to ensure its intuitive use and effectiveness. The computing power of the S9 chip is required to support this feature, providing improved accuracy and power efficiency.

name: ASSISTIVE TOUCH
description: Assistive Touch is a comprehensive accessibility feature introduced by Apple in 2021, specifically designed for individuals with limb differences or mobility issues. This feature enables users to navigate and control their Apple Watch through a range of gestures, including single tap, double tap, clench, and double clench, thus providing a wider range of interaction options for those who may lack full strength or dexterity in their hands. Initially, the double pinch gesture was associated with Assistive Touch, but after internal testing, Apple changed the term to double tap, as it better conveyed the release action required for the gesture. It's important to note that Assistive Touch was initially available on Apple Watch Series 4 or later, including the first-generation SE model, as reported by The Verge on October 25, 2023.

name: S9 CHIP
description: The S9 chip is a robust processor incorporated into the Apple Watch Series 9 and Ultra 2 models. This advanced component is equipped with four neural engines dedicated to machine learning, a feature that notably amplifies the performance of the wearable device. Among the enhanced functionalities is the double tap gesture, which is now more responsive and efficient due to the chip's optimized machine learning capabilities. The introduction of the S9 chip marks a significant leap in processing power for the Apple Watch lineup, ensuring a seamless and enhanced user experience.

name: DAVID CLARK
description: David Clark is the senior director of Apple Watch software engineering, who explains the technical aspects of the double tap gesture and its improved accuracy on the Series 9 and Ultra 2. [The Verge, 2023-10-25]

name: DOUBLE TAP
description: Double tap is a gesture on the Apple Watch designed to perform the main action of an app, akin to the double-click portion of using a mouse. Apple spent considerable time researching and collecting data to ensure its reliability and differentiation from other gestures [The Verge, 2023-10-25]

name: ERIC CHARLES
description: Eric Charles is the senior manager of Apple Watch Product Marketing, who explains the differences between Assistive Touch and Double tap, highlighting the customization and range of options Assistive Touch provides [The Verge, 2023-10-25]

name: CLARK
description: Clark, an individual closely linked with Apple, has provided insights into the company's meticulous research methodology concerning the double tap gesture. This process, as detailed by Clark, entails gathering extensive data from a diverse pool of hundreds of users and observing thousands of instances to construct comprehensive models that encapsulate all conceivable application scenarios (The Verge, 2023-10-25). Additionally, Clark has shed light on the intricate nature of customization in technology usage, particularly focusing on the Apple Watch. In this context, Clark has discussed the sophisticated features of the device, such as Focus modes and Shortcuts, highlighting the depth and versatility of personalization options available to users (The Verge, 2023-10-25). Through these contributions, Clark offers a dual perspective on both the backend research and the user-facing customization aspects within Apple's technology ecosystem.

name: FOCUS MODES
description: Focus modes are a feature on the Apple Watch that can be customized by users to manage notifications and calls, but not everyone has the patience to set up dozens of them. [The Verge, 2023-10-25]

name: SHORTCUTS
description: Shortcuts is a feature on the Apple Watch that allows users to create custom workflows and actions, but not everyone is willing to tinker with it to achieve desired results. [The Verge, 2023-10-25]

name: WILL SMITH
description: Will Smith, a renowned Hollywood actor, has been in a complex relationship with Jada Pinkett Smith, which he often refers to as a life partnership rather than a traditional marriage. They started dating in 1995 and tied the knot in 1997, following Smith's divorce from his first wife, Sheree Zampino, in 1994. Together, Will and Jada have two children, Jayden born in 1998 and Willow born in 2000. Despite facing challenges that led to discussions of separation since 2016, as reported by The Independent in 2023, the couple has maintained a commitment to each other, emphasizing their dedication to healing and improving their relationship. Contrary to some reports, Will has clarified that there has never been infidelity in their marriage. In 2021, Smith released a memoir that delved into the issues they've encountered, describing their relationship as "suffering the brutal death of our romantic fantasies." This memoir also prompted Will to acknowledge Jada's strength, intelligence, and compassion, as mentioned in an interview with the New York Times. Notably, Will's protective nature towards his family was highlighted when he reacted to a comment made by Chris Rock about Jada's shaved head at the 94th annual Oscars in 2022, an incident that led to Smith slapping Rock on stage. Despite his career in entertainment, Will Smith also made headlines in the sports world in 2023 when he agreed to a 1-year, $5 million contract as a reliever with the Kansas City Royals, showcasing his versatility beyond acting.

name: JADA PINKETT SMITH
description: Jada Pinkett Smith, a talented actress and host of the insightful talk show Red Table Talk, is known for her long-standing relationship with Will Smith, whom she began dating in 1995 and married in 1997. Together, they have two children, Jayden born in 1998 and Willow born in 2000. Despite rumors of an open marriage that Jada denied in 2013, the couple refers to themselves as life partners rather than simply married, emphasizing their commitment to a long-term relationship. In 2020, Jada confirmed having a relationship with August Alsina during a period of separation from Will, which began in 2016. Despite this separation, Jada and Will have made a promise never to divorce, and they continue to work on healing and improving their relationship. Jada's memoir, which was mentioned in Will's own memoir, played a significant role in helping Will understand her better. The couple's dedication to resolving their issues was put to the test when an altercation occurred between Will and Chris Rock at the 94th annual Oscars, after Rock made a comment about Jada's shaved head. Throughout their journey, Jada and Will have openly discussed the challenges of maintaining a spark in their relationship, demonstrating their commitment to transparency and growth.

name: JAYDEN SMITH
description: Jayden Smith is the first child of Will Smith and Jada Pinkett Smith, born in July 1998. [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-12]

name: WILLOW SMITH
description: Willow Smith, born in 2000, is the second child of renowned actors Will Smith and Jada Pinkett Smith. She has been affectionately described by her mother, Jada Pinkett Smith, as a "little guru" and a significant teacher of self-acceptance within the family. This characterization highlights Willow's profound influence and wisdom, despite her young age, suggesting that she has a deep understanding of personal growth and self-love, which she shares with those around her. Willow's presence in the Smith family is not only as a daughter but also as a source of inspiration and guidance, particularly in matters of self-acceptance.

name: ZAMPINO
description: Zampino is Will Smith's ex-wife, from whom he finalized his divorce before beginning to date Jada Pinkett Smith in 1995. [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-12]

name: AUGUST ALSINA
description: August Alsina, a talented singer, made headlines in 2020 when he revealed that he had been involved in a relationship with Jada Pinkett Smith, which occurred during her separation from her husband, Will Smith. Alsina described the nature of their connection as an "entanglement," a term that sparked significant public interest and discussion. He further shared that Will Smith was aware of their relationship and had given his blessing, indicating a level of understanding and acceptance within their personal dynamics. This complex scenario unfolded amidst the backdrop of the entertainment industry, where relationships and personal lives are often subject to intense scrutiny. Through this narrative, August Alsina's name became synonymous with a unique chapter in the lives of the high-profile couple, Jada and Will Smith, offering a glimpse into the intricate web of relationships that can exist within the celebrity sphere.

name: RED TABLE TALK
description: "Red Table Talk is a Facebook Watch series, later transitioned to a TV show format, hosted by Jada Pinkett Smith. The show is known for its candid discussions about personal issues and relationships. In a significant 2018 episode, Jada openly discussed her marriage to Will Smith, providing insights into their relationship. Contrary to some reports, it was not on the show where she revealed her separation from Will Smith, as that event was referenced in a later episode in 2023. Despite the evolution of the show's platform, Jada Pinkett Smith has consistently been the host, guiding viewers through intimate and often challenging conversations."

name: TIDAL
description: TIDAL is a music streaming service that hosts the Rap Radar podcast, where Will Smith discussed his relationship with Jada Pinkett Smith. [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-12]

name: RAP RADAR PODCAST
description: Rap Radar is a podcast hosted by TIDAL where Will Smith discussed his relationship with Jada Pinkett Smith in 2020. [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-12]

name: CBS SUNDAY MORNING
description: CBS Sunday Morning is a TV show where Will Smith gave an interview earlier this month, stating that he and Jada had never accused each other of cheating. [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-12]

name: CHRIS ROCK
description: Chris Rock is a comedian who made a comment about Jada Pinkett Smith's shaved head at the 94th annual Oscars in 2022, leading to an altercation with Will Smith. [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-12]

name: 94TH ANNUAL OSCARS
description: The 94th annual Oscars is an event where Will Smith slapped Chris Rock on stage in March 2022. [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-12]

name: MATTHEW PERRY
description: Matthew Perry, a renowned actor, passed away on October 28, 2023, with the cause of death attributed to the acute effects of ketamine, a potent anesthetic drug often used recreationally. At the time of his death, buprenorphine, a medication used to treat opioid addiction, was also detected in his system, indicating that he might have been undergoing treatment for substance use. Contributing factors to his death included coronary artery disease, a condition that affects the blood flow to the heart, and the effects of buprenorphine. Upon investigation of his residence, authorities found prescription medications and loose pills, suggesting a complex medical history and potential issues with medication management. This tragic event was widely reported by FOX News - Health on December 19, 2023, shedding light on the dangers of drug use and the importance of proper medical supervision in treating addiction.

name: KETAMINE
description: Ketamine, known by the entity name "KETAMINE," is a versatile drug with significant applications in medical and non-medical contexts. Primarily, it serves as an anesthetic during surgical procedures, having been a trusted choice for over 10 years, particularly in cases of treatment-resistant depression where its unique properties offer relief. However, its use is not without risks. In unsupervised settings or when mixed with other substances like opiates or stimulants, Ketamine can lead to dangerous outcomes, including accidents, enhanced sedative effects, and adverse cardiovascular impacts, as highlighted by FOX News - Health on 2023-12-19. This risk is exemplified by an incident involving Matthew Perry, where the concentration of Ketamine in his blood was sufficient to induce a state of unconsciousness and desensitize him to external stimuli, further underlining the potential hazards associated with its misuse. Despite its medical benefits, the illegal use of Ketamine as a recreational drug underscores the need for careful handling and regulation to prevent such health risks.

name: ALCOHOL AND DRUG FOUNDATION (ADF)
description: The Alcohol and Drug Foundation (ADF) describes ketamine as a "dissociative drug," which means it causes people to feel "separated or detached" from their bodies or physical surroundings [FOX News - Health, 2023-12-19]

name: LEWIS NELSON
description: Lewis Nelson is the chair of the Department of Emergency Medicine and chief of medical toxicology at Rutgers New Jersey Medical School. He provided a statement to Fox News Digital explaining the effects of ketamine that led to Matthew Perry’s death [FOX News - Health, 2023-12-19]

name: DR. BANKOLE JOHNSON
description: Dr. Bankole Johnson is the CEO and founder of Casa Privée in Miami, a concierge medical facility. description: Sullivan, a representative and spokesperson for Google, has been actively involved in discussions regarding the company's search engine algorithms and their impact on search results. He argued that Google's system is designed to prioritize high-quality websites and that manipulative tactics are effectively blocked. Sullivan was clear in his stance that strategies that violate Google's terms of service should not be labeled as SEO but rather as "spam." Additionally, he advised businesses to focus on serving their customers rather than attempting to game the search engine algorithm. However, Sullivan's expertise extends beyond the digital realm, as he also warned about the health risks associated with unsupervised use of ketamine, particularly the dangers of too large a dose leading to accidents, in a FOX News - Health report in December 2023.

name: WEST INDIES
description:
On 13th December 2023, the West Indies cricket team embarked on a T20 international series against England, with the first match marking the beginning of a competitive series. Throughout the series, the West Indies demonstrated their prowess, securing a hat-trick of T20 series wins this year, ultimately clinching the series 3-2 in a deciding fifth match. Notably, Shai Hope played a crucial role in anchoring the team during the chase, leading the West Indies to surpass England's total and win the series. In the initial stages of the series, the team was six runs ahead of the Duckworth Lewis Stern rate at a critical point in the match, with Hope struggling against legspin bowling and Rovman Powell stepping in as the new batsman after Shimron Hetmyer's wicket. 

In the match updates provided by The Guardian on 21st December 2023, the West Indies were seen managing an awkward chase pretty well, standing at 80-3 with Hope scoring 15 and Rutherford 20. Earlier in the series, during the 3rd over, they had scored 30-1, with Johnson Charles contributing 13 runs and Nicholas Pooran adding 9. Charles, a key player, was also the player of the match when the West Indies beat England at the T20 World Cup 11 years ago, scoring an impressive 84 off 56 balls. The team's victory in the first T20I match was by 4 wickets, showcasing their determination and skill right from the start. The West Indies' performance against England in this T20 series was a testament to their strategic gameplay and the individual talents of their players, culminating in a successful series win.

name: SHAI HOPE
description: Shai Hope is a prominent batsman for the West Indies cricket team, known for his calm and composed demeanor under pressure. In a recent match against England, Hope faced challenges breaking the legspin shackles but showcased his resilience and skill by playing a gem of an innings. He anchored the team during a tense chase, scoring 43 runs off 43 balls at a run-a-ball pace, which was crucial in securing a victory by 4 wickets. Hope's performance included a memorable six off a length ball, demonstrating his ability to handle difficult situations and contribute significantly to his team's success. Prior to the 16th over, he had already scored 29 runs, setting a solid foundation for the West Indies' innings. Shai Hope's contributions to the team have been exemplary, making him a key player in the West Indies' lineup.

name: ADIL RASHID
description: Adil Rashid, a 35-year-old legspinner for the England cricket team, has been performing exceptionally well in the T20 format. On December 13, 2023, he played a crucial role in the first T20I match against West Indies, where he achieved a significant milestone by taking his 100th T20I wicket, dismissing the formidable batsman Hetmyer. This outstanding performance was followed by another impressive showing in the series, where he rose to the top of the T20 bowling rankings by taking two wickets while conceding only 21 runs, as reported by The Guardian on December 21, 2023. Adil's skill and dedication were further highlighted when he celebrated the dismissal of Johnson Charles, showcasing his impact on the team's success in the matches against West Indies.

name: TOPLEY
description: Topley, a skilled cricketer representing England, is renowned for his exceptional performance in the realm of seam bowling. As highlighted by The Guardian on December 21, 2023, Topley not only bowled the 5th over in the match but also distinguished himself as the most economical seamer on either side. His contribution to England's performance in the series was significant, as he claimed two crucial wickets while conceding a mere 17 runs, showcasing his ability to restrict the opposing team's scoring and make impactful contributions to his team's success.

name: CM PUNK
description: CM Punk, also recognized by his moniker "The Second City Saint," is a professional wrestler whose career has significantly impacted the wrestling industry, being mentioned as a key figure in a wrestling revolution. Although some argue that he did not fully execute this revolution, his influence is undeniable. Initially, CM Punk rose to fame as a WWE star, where he made a name for himself with his distinctive style and persona. However, he left WWE and later joined All Elite Wrestling (AEW), a move that was met with mixed reactions. His time in AEW was not without controversy, as he was involved in backstage antics that led Seth Rollins to label him as a "cancer." Unfortunately, CM Punk's tenure with AEW came to an end in September 2023 following a backstage altercation with Jack Perry, which resulted in his release from the company. Despite this, there are speculations about his potential return to WWE, fueled by hints he has dropped and the fact that the Survivor Series, a major WWE event, is being held in his hometown, Chicago. This potential comeback has the wrestling community abuzz with anticipation and speculation.

description: B&H, a prominent retail company, was approached for comment amidst the unapproved parts scandal that shook the global supply chain, although the specifics of their involvement or response remain undisclosed as of The Sydney Morning Herald's report on 2023-10-16. Known for its customer-centric policies, B&H offers a price match guarantee, honoring a current lower price or matching a competitor's price on a case-by-case basis. To take advantage of this policy, customers are required to contact B&H's Customer Service team, which can be reached through on-site chat, email, or by calling 800-606-6969 / 212-444-6615, as detailed in The Verge's coverage on 2023-10-25.

name: DELL
description: Dell, a renowned technology company, is involved in a dynamic pricing strategy that includes being part of Lenovo's price matching policy for comparable PCs. This indicates that Lenovo considers Dell a significant competitor in the PC market. Additionally, Dell itself offers a price-match guarantee, where they will match the price of identical products not only from their own stores but also from major retailers such as Amazon, Best Buy, Walmart, Target, HP, Apple, and Lenovo. Customers can easily take advantage of this policy by calling 1-877-275-3355 or initiating an online chat to conduct a price check. Furthermore, the policy allows customers to report a price difference to Dell within 30 days of their purchase, ensuring that they receive the best deal possible. This comprehensive approach to price matching reflects Dell's commitment to providing competitive pricing and maintaining customer satisfaction.

name: GAMESTOP
description:
GameStop, a video game retailer, is set to report its Q3 earnings after the market closes on Wednesday, amidst a backdrop of recent volatility in one-time meme stocks that has seen its stock surge over 20% in the past 5 days. Despite this, Wall Street analysts suggest selling GameStop stock (GME), while Seeking Alpha's Quant rating system recommends a Hold. The company has faced challenges, beating EPS estimates in only 3 of the past 8 quarters and revenue expectations in 5 of those reports. GameStop's financial health is further strained by fundamental headwinds, including poor margins and declining sales, which contribute to its structural unprofitability.

In terms of price-matching policies, GameStop does not officially advertise a price-matching policy on its website. However, the company has been known to match prices for items sold and shipped by Amazon, both online and in-store, as confirmed by a tweet last year. Unofficial reports also indicate that GameStop may extend this policy to items from Target and other retailers, although this has not been officially confirmed by the company. [The Verge, 2023-10-25; Seeking Alpha, 2023-12-03]

name: HP
description: HP is a company that offers price matching for branded HP products, excluding certain promotional events such as Green Monday and the week of Thanksgiving and the week after[]

name: LENOVO
description: Lenovo, a renowned technology company, specializes in the manufacturing of a diverse range of computing devices. Among its offerings is the IdeaPad Flex 5i Chromebook Plus, a versatile and innovative Chromebook model designed for enhanced user experience [Engadget, 2023-11-19]. Additionally, Lenovo is committed to competitive pricing, ensuring that its products, including PCs with the same key specifications as those from leading brands such as HP or Dell, are priced comparably. This policy applies to items sold through recognized retailers, with the condition that the product must be in stock and readily available from both Lenovo and the competing retailer. By adhering to these practices, Lenovo aims to provide its customers with the best value and service in the technology market.

name: LOWE'S
description: Lowe's is a company that will match the price of identical, in-stock products when presented with an ad, product listing, or photo from a qualifying online or local retailer, including Amazon, Best Buy, Target, and Walmart[]

name: XBOX SERIES X
description: The Xbox Series X, a high-performance gaming console developed by Microsoft, has recently hit an all-time low price of $439, making it an attractive option for gamers looking for quality and affordability. This special offer, noted by Mashable on 2023-11-25, includes a free copy of the highly anticipated game Diablo IV, further enhancing the value of the purchase. Additionally, the Xbox Series X is part of Microsoft's price matching policy, ensuring that buyers receive the best possible price for their console. This combination of price, game inclusion, and policy assurance makes the Xbox Series X a compelling choice in the gaming console market.

name: NEWEGG
description: Newegg, a prominent technology and entertainment retailer, provides its customers with a Price Match Guarantee on a curated selection of items. This policy ensures that if a lower price is discovered on Newegg itself or at any major retailer for the same product, Newegg will honor a credit for the difference in price. The credit can then be utilized on the Newegg website within a 90-day timeframe. It's important to note that to be eligible for this price-match guarantee, the notification of the lower price must be made within 14 days of the original purchase. However, the guarantee does not extend to major holiday sales events, such as Black Friday, Cyber Monday, and Green Monday, as specified by The Verge on October 25, 2023. This policy underscores Newegg's commitment to competitive pricing and customer satisfaction, except during peak promotional periods.

name: MAJOR RETAILERS
description: Major retailers, as referenced in Newegg's Price Match Guarantee policy [The Verge, 2023-10-25], are significant organizations that Newegg acknowledges for the purpose of comparing and matching prices. These entities are recognized for their substantial presence in the retail market and are considered competitors by Newegg in terms of product pricing. The policy indicates that Newegg is committed to ensuring its customers receive competitive prices by aligning with the pricing strategies of these major retailers.

name: PRICE MATCH GUARANTEE
description: Price Match Guarantee is a policy offered by Newegg on select items, allowing customers to receive a credit if a lower price is found within 14 days of purchase. The credit must be used within 90 days [The Verge, 2023-10-25]

name: GREEN MONDAY
description: Green Monday is a major holiday sales event during which Newegg’s price-match guarantee is not valid [The Verge, 2023-10-25]

name: FRANCESCA SCORSESE
description: Francesca Scorsese, the daughter of renowned filmmaker Martin Scorsese, has become an unexpected online sensation by bridging the generational gap in internet slang. On October 5, 2023, she posted a TikTok challenge where she quizzed her father on popular digital lingo, a video that quickly went viral. Francesca used her unique perspective, drawing from film references and examples, to explain terms such as "hits different," "slept on," "ate," "no cap," "ship," "slay," and "simp" to her father. This engaging and educational content not only entertained her followers but also shed light on the evolving language of the internet, showcasing Francesca's ability to connect with both her father's generation and her own through the shared love of cinema and social media trends.

name: INTERNET SLANG
description: Internet slang refers to the colloquial language used on the internet, which Francesca Scorsese quizzed her father, Martin Scorsese, about in a TikTok challenge posted on October 5, 2023 [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-10]

name: KING OF COMEDY
description: "King of Comedy" is a 1983 film directed by Martin Scorsese. It was used as an example for the term "slept on" as it received positive reviews but was a box office flop. [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-10]

name: TAXI DRIVER
description: "Taxi Driver" is a film directed by Martin Scorsese. It was mentioned when explaining the internet slang "ship". [The Independent - Life and Style, 2023-10-10]

name: LILY GLADSTONE
description: Lily Gladstone, a talented actor, is set to make a significant impact in the world of cinema with her role as Mollie Kyle in Martin Scorsese's highly anticipated film "Killers of the Flower Moon". The movie, which has been generating buzz in the entertainment industry, is scheduled for release in 2023. Lily's performance in this film has garnered attention, with The Independent - Life and Style even using her as an example to illustrate the term "ate", suggesting that she has fully embodied her character and delivered a powerful performance. As of 2023-10-07, according to Polygon, Lily is actively involved in the promotion of the film, further solidifying her status as a key figure in its success.

description: Robert De Niro, a renowned actor in the film industry, has made significant contributions to cinema through his versatile performances. He starred in Martin Scorsese's iconic film "The King of Comedy," showcasing his exceptional acting skills. More recently, De Niro continues to captivate audiences by taking on the role of William Hale in the highly anticipated movie "Killers of the Flower Moon," further solidifying his status as a leading figure in the entertainment world.

name: JOHN J. RAY III
description: John J. Ray III, a seasoned community analyst with expertise in navigating the complexities of technology and entertainment sectors, is not directly involved in this scenario. However, in a significant development, John J. Ray III, known for his role as an Enron turnaround veteran, has taken the helm as the new CEO of FTX following Sam Bankman-Fried's resignation, as reported by TechCrunch on October 1, 2023. Ray has not shied away from making bold statements about the situation, referring to Bankman-Fried's conduct as "old-fashioned embezzlement" and drawing parallels to the infamous Enron scandal, according to The Verge's coverage on September 28, 2023. This appointment signifies a critical juncture for FTX, as the company seeks to restructure and regain trust amidst financial turmoil.

name: GOVERNMENT
description: The government, a political entity responsible for making and enforcing policies, plays a critical role in the climate tech sector's success, as highlighted by TechCrunch on 2023-10-13. However, it is also involved in legal actions, as evidenced by the prosecution of Sam Bankman-Fried for misusing FTX customer funds, reported by The Verge on 2023-09-28. The government alleges that Bankman-Fried publicly denied Alameda's privileged access to FTX, while internally allowing it. On a more positive note, the government of the Philippines, as of 2023-11-05, according to Business World, is envisioning a future by 2028 where climate and disaster risk resilience of communities and institutions will increase, ecosystem resilience will be enhanced, and a low-carbon economy transition is enabled. To achieve this, the Philippine government plans to safeguard cross-sectoral convergence and implement a comprehensive risk management approach to address the adverse consequences of climate change.

name: CRYPTOCURRENCY INDUSTRY
description: The cryptocurrency industry is facing scrutiny due to the FTX scandal. Bankman-Fried's public relations efforts had helped to position FTX and himself as trustworthy figures in the industry, but his fall has negatively impacted the industry's reputation. [The Verge, 2023-09-28]
